','','2017-02-15'),(428,32,131,'Episode 131','','2017-02-16'),(429,32,132,'Episode 132','','2017-02-17'),(430,32,133,'Episode 133','','2017-02-20'),(431,32,134,'Episode 134','','2017-02-21'),(432,32,135,'Episode 135','','2017-02-22'),(433,32,136,'Episode 136','','2017-02-23'),(434,32,137,'Episode 137','','2017-02-24'),(435,32,138,'Episode 138','','2017-02-27'),(436,32,139,'Episode 139','','2017-02-28'),(437,32,140,'Episode 140','','2017-03-01'),(438,32,141,'Episode 141','','2017-03-02'),(439,32,142,'Episode 142','','2017-03-03'),(440,32,143,'Episode 143','','2017-03-06'),(441,32,144,'Episode 144','','2017-03-07'),(442,32,145,'Episode 145','','2017-03-08'),(443,32,146,'Episode 146','','2017-03-09'),(444,32,147,'Episode 147','','2017-03-10'),(445,32,148,'Episode 148','','2017-03-13'),(446,32,149,'Episode 149','','2017-03-14'),(447,33,1,'The Family Man','Srikant Tiwari, a member of TASC, a discreet intelligence agency, is assigned to interrogate suspected ISIS recruits. Balancing his personal life with work becomes a challenge for this family man, and things get out of hand on both fronts.','2019-09-20'),(448,33,2,'Sleepers','A scooter bomb goes off at Kala Ghoda. Srikant learns about a mission called Zulfiqar. Suspects in the blast case tell him about a drop box near Victoria College. He arranges for round-the-clock surveillance at the drop box location.','2019-09-20'),(449,33,3,'Anti-National','When he finds out that one of the hospitalised prisoners is part of Mission Zulfiqar, Srikant interrogates the prisoner’s friend, Moosa, about it. Someone called Kareem has used the dropbox. TASC monitors Kareem’s hostel room, but Kareem gives them the slip.','2019-09-20'),(450,33,4,'Patriots','TASC is in a quandary. They fear Kareem and his men have a devious plan. They get to Kareem’s car, only to realise that things are not what they seem.','2019-09-20'),(451,33,5,'Pariah','ISI agent Sameer sends the Kala Ghoda bomber to Kashmir to execute Mission Zulfiqar. Srikant is ‘punished’ and sent to Kashmir, but when his boss, Kulkarni, tells him it was planned, Srikant starts digging into Zulfiqar.','2019-09-20'),(452,33,6,'Dance of Death','Srikant discovers that he’s been after the wrong suspect all this time.','2019-09-20'),(453,33,7,'Paradise','Srikant searches for Sajid at a wedding in Baramulla. Pakistan’s PM finds out about Zulfiqar and tries to stop it.','2019-09-20'),(454,33,8,'Act of War','Srikant helps CIA locate Faizan, a wanted man hiding in Balochistan. Srikant slips into Pakistan to interrogate Faizan.','2019-09-20'),(455,33,9,'Fighting Dirty','Srikant tries to thwart a plan to smuggle nerve gas canisters from Kashmir into Delhi.','2019-09-20'),(456,33,10,'The Bomb','TASC realises that Mission Zulfiqar is not over. There is a Plan B. And it has already been put to action.','2019-09-20'),(457,34,1,'Exile','Srikant Tiwari has started a new life as an IT employee, but he can’t stay away from adventure when JK is sent to Chennai to nab a former foreign insurgent. Chennai TASC agent, Muthu and JK are faced with a hostage situation in Chennai. And Dhriti may have a boyfriend.','2021-06-04'),(458,34,2,'Weapon','Suchitra wants Srikant to go for couple counselling. Prime Minister Basu wants to make up for India’s recent foreign policy faux pas. Bhaskaran activates an elite unit with Major Sameer’s help. A creep harasses Raji.','2021-06-04'),(459,34,3,'Angel of Death','Suchitra’s birthday dinner triggers a showdown between Srikant and Suchitra. Srikant quits his IT job and joins back TASC. Raji’s boss is onto her secret life and blackmails her.','2021-06-04'),(460,34,4,'Eagle','Srikant starts investigating in Chennai. Sajid teams up with Selva and Raji. Wonder who they are targeting! Inspector Umayal starts investigating Nanda’s disappearance.','2021-06-04'),(461,34,5,'Homecoming','Inspector Umayal wants to join the TASC team in their mission. All roads lead to the old base.','2021-06-04'),(462,34,6,'Martyrs','Srikant and team manage to nab Raji. But they find out the hard way that they are way in over their heads. TASC suffers a tragic loss.','2021-06-04'),(463,34,7,'Collateral Damage','Raji is injured days before the D-Day and needs treatment. Simmering tensions between Suchitra and Dhriti hit a crescendo. Sajid bids adieu to Raji, for he has another, personal mission to accomplish in Mumbai. Meanwhile, Srikant is hit by another debilitating personal crisis.','2021-06-04'),(464,34,8,'Vendetta','The hunt is on for Dhriti. Meanwhile, JK and Muthu decide to check out Tigris Aviation, and walk into a trap. Dhriti’s loss of innocence is gruesome.','2021-06-04'),(465,34,9,'The Final Act','News about JK forces Srikant to rush back to Chennai. Raji hears about Sajid\'s fate. Dhriti finds out the true nature of Srikant\'s job. Prime Minister Basu reaches Chennai for bilateral talks with the Lankan President, Rupatunga. Srikant and team race against time to prevent a deadly attack on the two premiers.','2021-06-04'),(466,35,1,'Episode 1','','2025-11-21'),(467,36,1,'Episode 1','','2015-07-13'),(468,36,2,'Episode 2','','2015-07-14'),(469,36,3,'Episode 3','','2015-07-15'),(470,36,4,'Episode 4','','2015-07-16'),(471,36,5,'Episode 5','','2015-07-17'),(472,36,6,'Episode 6','','2015-07-20'),(473,36,7,'Episode 7','','2015-07-21'),(474,36,8,'Episode 8','','2015-07-22'),(475,36,9,'Episode 9','','2015-07-23'),(476,36,10,'Episode 10','','2015-07-24'),(477,37,1,'Episode 1','','2016-05-02'),(478,37,2,'Episode 2','','2016-05-03'),(479,37,3,'Episode 3','','2016-05-04'),(480,37,4,'Episode 4','','2016-05-05'),(481,37,5,'Episode 5','','2016-05-06'),(482,37,6,'Episode 6','','2016-05-09'),(483,37,7,'Episode 7','','2016-05-10'),(484,37,8,'Episode 8','','2016-05-11'),(485,37,9,'Episode 9','','2016-05-12'),(486,37,10,'Episode 10','','2016-05-13'),(487,38,1,'Episode 1','','2015-09-05'),(488,39,1,'The Only Mages in the World','The night of the crimson full moon. The full moon of Konichi, who had been living a normal high school life, is caught up in the battle to become the only magician in the world at the school where he returned to get his forgotten. It is explained that this world was overflowing with magic from the girl and the new moon which met there, and it is a full moon which runs away puzzled.','2019-07-06'),(489,39,2,'Why I\'m Here','As dawn breaks, Mangetsu awakens in Shingetsu\'s apartment. On her way back home, Shingetsu tells her more about mages and GRANBELM. Determining that Mangetsu has no intention of fighting, Shingetsu prepares to erase her memories, but her technique is unsuccessful. When Shingetsu is about to give up, Mangetsu asks her for more information about GRANBELM.','2019-07-13'),(490,39,3,'The Bell Tolls at the Full Moon','Mangetsu meets Anna at school in a chance encounter, and Anna tells her that Shingetsu ruined her family. During lunch the next day, Mangetsu tells Shingetsu that she wants to participate in GRANBELM. Shingetsu offers to help her, but at that moment, a car carrying Anna and some of her family passes by','2019-07-20'),(491,39,4,'Feng Shui Master Lin Fen Fen','Mangetsu experiences her second GRANBELM. As the battle grows more intense with all the girls\' emotions running high, Mangetsu and Shingetsu struggle against Nene\'s ARMANOX, JI GUAN LONG. But all along, another mech is approaching them','2019-07-27'),(492,39,5,'A Small Girl\'s Small Wish','Nene reveals her identity to Mangetsu and Shingetsu, vowing to fight them fair and square. Then, on the next full moon, Mangetsu and Kuon face off against JI GUAN LONG together according to a plan they devised before the battle, while Shingetsu draws Anna away from them. As shots are exchanged, Mangetsu finally figures out where JI GUAN LONG is','2019-08-03'),(493,39,6,'Magic Stones','After getting a glimpse of Nene\'s past, Mangetsu realizes what it means to fight in GRANBELM, but at the same time finds herself with even more questions about it. Still, now she knows that every participant has her own reasons for fighting. Meanwhile, Anna attempts to steal the Fugo family\'s powerful magic stone, which leads Suishou to give up on her and leave the Fugo household.','2019-08-10'),(494,39,7,'Miss Ressentiment','Shingetsu learns that Anna\'s mother was attacked and hurries to visit her at the hospital. She then makes up her mind to find Anna, who has gone missing, and defeat her once and for all. When the full moon rises, the next GRANBELM battle begins, and Shingetsu is faced with a much more powerful Anna... thanks to the power of the Fugo family\'s magic stone.','2019-08-17'),(495,39,8,'What It Means to Become a Mage','Mangetsu and Kuon are overwhelmed by Suishou\'s unsettling aura as they fight her, barely managing to hold out until the end of the battle. Mangetsu awakens back at Shingetsu\'s house, then sets out to visit Nene after receiving a message from her. They discuss the events of last night\'s battle, but Nene has no recollection of Anna whatsoever. Perturbed, Mangetsu and Shingetsu hurry to the Fugo household, but what they find isn\'t what they expected...','2019-08-24'),(496,39,9,'NOCTURNE Changes Colors','While Nene is investigating abnormal magic signals, she realizes that Mangetsu lies at the center of the astronomically high readings. Meanwhile, as Kuon is thinking about her older sister Shisui, who has long been asleep due to a curse, she somehow receives a message from her. She heads toward the location indicated in it and finds none other than the one responsible for the curse: Suishou.','2019-08-31'),(497,39,10,'The Pensive Doll','Mangetsu and Shingetsu have been expertly played by Suishou, leaving them unable to fight her effectively. Kuon tries to get them to leave the area and sets up a powerful attack aimed at Suishou, but a moment\'s inattention leaves her open to a vicious counterattack...','2019-09-07'),(498,39,11,'Even If My Goodbye Doesn\'t Reach You','Mangetsu, who has become uncertain of her own existence, runs into Kuon\'s older sister, Shisui. As she talks with Shisui, Mangetsu feels moved to send a message to Shingetsu. Meanwhile, Shingetsu is convinced that Mangetsu is suffering because of the wish she made, and her guilt brings her to tears. As she\'s talking with Mangetsu, she becomes unable to bear it any longer and runs from the house...','2019-09-14'),(499,39,12,'Magiaconatus','Shingetsu heads into the final battle with Mangetsu\'s feelings held within her heart. Suishou is fighting to prove that no human is worthy of becoming the one true mage, while Shingetsu and Mangetsu are fighting to rid the world of magical power for good. As the battle intensifies, Shingetsu becomes caught within Suishou\'s grasp. Mangetsu tries desperately to save her, but Shingetsu takes the full force of the beam Suishou fires...','2019-09-21'),(500,39,13,'For the Only Two of Their Kind in the World','GRANBELM is finally down to two participants. Their mechs surpass their own limits, but eventually they can no longer withstand the impact sustained during the battle, and their functions begin to fail. When Shingetsu\'s situation grows dire, she\'s surprised by the appearance of Mangetsu, who was supposed to have disappeared...','2019-09-28'),(501,40,1,'Chapter One: The Vanishing of Will Byers','On his way home from a friend\'s house, young Will sees something terrifying. Nearby, a sinister secret lurks in the depths of a government lab.','2016-07-15'),(502,40,2,'Chapter Two: The Weirdo on Maple Street','Lucas, Mike and Dustin try to talk to the girl they found in the woods. Hopper questions an anxious Joyce about an unsettling phone call.','2016-07-15'),(503,40,3,'Chapter Three: Holly, Jolly','An increasingly concerned Nancy looks for Barb and finds out what Jonathan\'s been up to. Joyce is convinced Will is trying to talk to her.','2016-07-15'),(504,40,4,'Chapter Four: The Body','Refusing to believe Will is dead, Joyce tries to connect with her son. The boys give Eleven a makeover. Nancy and Jonathan form an unlikely alliance.','2016-07-15'),(505,40,5,'Chapter Five: The Flea and the Acrobat','Hopper breaks into the lab while Nancy and Jonathan confront the force that took Will. The boys ask Mr. Clarke how to travel to another dimension.','2016-07-15'),(506,40,6,'Chapter Six: The Monster','A frantic Jonathan looks for Nancy in the darkness, but Steve\'s looking for her, too. Hopper and Joyce uncover the truth about the lab\'s experiments.','2016-07-15'),(507,40,7,'Chapter Seven: The Bathtub','Eleven struggles to reach Will, while Lucas warns that \"the bad men are coming.\" Nancy and Jonathan show the police what Jonathan caught on camera.','2016-07-15'),(508,40,8,'Chapter Eight: The Upside Down','Dr. Brenner holds Hopper and Joyce for questioning while the boys wait with Eleven in the gym. Back at Will\'s, Nancy and Jonathan prepare for battle.','2016-07-15'),(509,41,1,'Chapter One: MADMAX','As the town preps for Halloween, a high-scoring rival shakes things up at the arcade, and a skeptical Hopper inspects a field of rotting pumpkins.','2017-10-27'),(510,41,2,'Chapter Two: Trick or Treat, Freak','After Will sees something terrible on trick-or-treat night, Mike wonders whether Eleven\'s still out there. Nancy wrestles with the truth about Barb.','2017-10-27'),(511,41,3,'Chapter Three: The Pollywog','Dustin adopts a strange new pet, and Eleven grows increasingly impatient. A well-meaning Bob urges Will to stand up to his fears.','2017-10-27'),(512,41,4,'Chapter Four: Will the Wise','An ailing Will opens up to Joyce -- with disturbing results. While Hopper digs for the truth, Eleven unearths a surprising discovery.','2017-10-27'),(513,41,5,'Chapter Five: Dig Dug','Nancy and Jonathan swap conspiracy theories with a new ally as Eleven searches for someone from her past. “Bob the Brain” tackles a difficult problem.','2017-10-27'),(514,41,6,'Chapter Six: The Spy','Will\'s connection to a shadowy evil grows stronger, but no one\'s quite sure how to stop it. Elsewhere, Dustin and Steve forge an unlikely bond.','2017-10-27'),(515,41,7,'Chapter Seven: The Lost Sister','Psychic visions draw Eleven to a band of violent outcasts and an angry girl with a shadowy past.','2017-10-27'),(516,41,8,'Chapter Eight: The Mind Flayer','An unlikely hero steps forward when a deadly development puts the Hawkins Lab on lockdown, trapping Will and several others inside.','2017-10-27'),(517,41,9,'Chapter Nine: The Gate','Eleven makes plans to finish what she started while the survivors turn up the heat on the monstrous force that\'s holding Will hostage.','2017-10-27'),(518,42,1,'Chapter One: Suzie, Do You Copy?','Summer brings new jobs and budding romance. But the mood shifts when Dustin\'s radio picks up a Russian broadcast, and Will senses something is wrong.','2019-07-04'),(519,42,2,'Chapter Two: The Mall Rats','Nancy and Jonathan follow a lead, Steve and Robin sign on to a secret mission, and Max and Eleven go shopping. A rattled Billy has troubling visions.','2019-07-04'),(520,42,3,'Chapter Three: The Case of the Missing Lifeguard','With El and Max looking for Billy, Will declares a day without girls. Steve and Dustin go on a stakeout, and Joyce and Hopper return to Hawkins Lab.','2019-07-04'),(521,42,4,'Chapter Four: The Sauna Test','A code red brings the gang back together to face a frighteningly familiar evil. Karen urges Nancy to keep digging, and Robin finds a useful map.','2019-07-04'),(522,42,5,'Chapter Five: The Flayed','Strange surprises lurk inside an old farmhouse and deep beneath the Starcourt Mall. Meanwhile, the Mind Flayer is gathering strength.','2019-07-04'),(523,42,6,'Chapter Six: E Pluribus Unum','Dr. Alexei reveals what the Russians have been building, and Eleven sees where Billy has been. Dustin and Erica stage a daring rescue.','2019-07-04'),(524,42,7,'Chapter Seven: The Bite','With time running out -- and an assassin close behind -- Hopper\'s crew races back to Hawkins, where El and the kids are preparing for war.','2019-07-04'),(525,42,8,'Chapter Eight: The Battle of Starcourt','Terror reigns in the food court when the Mind Flayer comes to collect. But down below, in the dark, the future of the world is at stake.','2019-07-04'),(526,43,1,'Chapter One: The Hellfire Club','El is bullied at school. Joyce opens a mysterious package. A scrappy player shakes up D&D night.','2022-05-27'),(527,43,2,'Chapter Two: Vecna\'s Curse','A plane brings Mike to California — and a dead body brings Hawkins to a halt. Nancy goes looking for leads. A shaken Eddie tells the gang what he saw.','2022-05-27'),(528,43,3,'Chapter Three: The Monster and the Superhero','Murray and Joyce fly to Alaska, and El faces serious consequences. Robin and Nancy dig up dirt on Hawkins\' demons. Dr. Owens delivers sobering news.','2022-05-27'),(529,43,4,'Chapter Four: Dear Billy','Max is in grave danger... and running out of time. A patient at Pennhurst asylum has visitors. Elsewhere, in Russia, Hopper is hard at work.','2022-05-27'),(530,43,5,'Chapter Five: The Nina Project','Owens takes El to Nevada, where she\'s forced to confront her past, while the Hawkins kids comb a crumbling house for clues. Vecna claims another victim.','2022-05-27'),(531,43,6,'Chapter Six: The Dive','Behind the Iron Curtain, a risky rescue mission gets underway. The California crew seeks help from a hacker. Steve takes one for the team.','2022-05-27'),(532,43,7,'Chapter Seven: The Massacre at Hawkins Lab','As Hopper braces to battle a monster, Dustin dissects Vecna\'s motives — and decodes a message from beyond. El finds strength in a distant memory.','2022-05-27'),(533,43,8,'Chapter Eight: Papa','Nancy has sobering visions, and El passes an important test. Back in Hawkins, the gang gathers supplies and prepares for battle.','2022-07-01'),(534,43,9,'Chapter Nine: The Piggyback','With selfless hearts and a clash of metal, heroes fight from every corner of the battlefield to save Hawkins — and the world itself.','2022-07-01'),(535,44,1,'Chapter One: The Crawl','','2025-11-26'),(536,44,2,'Chapter Two: The Vanishing of ...','','2025-11-26'),(537,44,3,'Chapter Three: The Turnbow Trap','','2025-11-26'),(538,44,4,'Chapter Four: Sorcerer','','2025-11-26'),(539,44,5,'Chapter Five: Shock Jock','','2025-12-25'),(540,44,6,'Chapter Six: Escape from Camazotz','','2025-12-25'),(541,44,7,'Chapter Seven: The Bridge','','2025-12-25'),(542,44,8,'Chapter Eight: The Rightside Up','','2025-12-31'),(543,45,1,'Good Cop / Bad Cop','Season 1 Minisode 1: Hank and Marie celebrate Valentine\'s Day.','2009-02-17'),(544,45,2,'Wedding Day','Season 1 Minisode 2: Hank and Walt have a discussion on Hank and Marie\'s wedding day.','2009-02-17'),(545,45,3,'TwaüghtHammër','Season 1 Minisode 3: Jesse explains the origins of his band, TwaüghtHammër.','2009-02-17'),(546,45,4,'Marie\'s Confession','Season 1 Minisode 4: Marie confesses about her shop-lifting.','2009-02-17'),(547,45,5,'The Break-In','Season 1 Minisode 5: Walt asks for help from Badger to break into an old woman\'s house and get his vacuum cleaner back.','2009-02-24'),(548,45,6,'Jesse Pinkman Evidence Tape','Jesse goes on record and describes on camera everything he remembers about Walt\'s business dealings and criminal activity.',NULL),(549,45,7,'Walt\'s Confession','The video confession recorded by Walt.',NULL),(550,45,8,'Pizza of Destiny: Cranston\'s Greatest Shot','A detailed bonus feature about a particular scene in which Bryan Cranston tosses a pizza on the roof for the DVD/Blu-ray of \'Breaking Bad Season 3.','2011-06-07'),(551,45,9,'Alternate Ending','Special to the 2013 DVD and Blu-Ray release of Breaking Bad. The series ends with Hal from Malcolm in the Middle (also played by Bryan Cranston) wakes up, to reveal that the series had been a dream.','2013-11-26'),(552,46,1,'Pilot','When an unassuming high school chemistry teacher discovers he has a rare form of lung cancer, he decides to team up with a former student and create a top of the line crystal meth in a used RV, to provide for his family once he is gone.','2008-01-20'),(553,46,2,'Cat\'s in the Bag...','Walt and Jesse attempt to tie up loose ends. The desperate situation gets more complicated with the flip of a coin. Walt\'s wife, Skyler, becomes suspicious of Walt\'s strange behavior.','2008-01-27'),(554,46,3,'...And the Bag\'s in the River','Walter fights with Jesse over his drug use, causing him to leave Walter alone with their captive, Krazy-8. Meanwhile, Hank has a scared straight moment with Walter Jr. after his aunt discovers he has been smoking pot. Also, Skylar is upset when Walter stays away from home.','2008-02-10'),(555,46,4,'Cancer Man','Walter finally tells his family that he has been stricken with cancer. Meanwhile, the DEA believes Albuquerque has a new, big time player to worry about. Meanwhile, a worthy recipient is the target of a depressed Walter\'s anger, and Jesse makes a surprise visit to his parents home.','2008-02-17'),(556,46,5,'Gray Matter','Walter and Skyler attend a former colleague\'s party. Jesse tries to free himself from the drugs, while Skyler organizes an intervention.','2008-02-24'),(557,46,6,'Crazy Handful of Nothin\'','The side effects of chemo begin to plague Walt. Meanwhile, the DEA rounds up suspected dealers.','2008-03-02'),(558,46,7,'A No Rough Stuff Type Deal','Walter accepts his new identity as a drug dealer after a PTA meeting. Elsewhere, Jesse decides to put his aunt\'s house on the market and Skyler is the recipient of a baby shower.','2008-03-09'),(559,47,1,'Seven Thirty-Seven','Walt and Jesse are vividly reminded of Tuco’s volatile nature, and try to figure a way out of their business partnership. Hank attempts to mend fences between the estranged Marie and Skyler.','2009-03-08'),(560,47,2,'Grilled','Walt and Jesse find themselves in close quarters with an unhinged Tuco. Marie and Hank comfort Skyler, who is distraught over Walt’s disappearance. Hank pays a visit to Mrs. Pinkman on some not-so-official business.','2009-03-15'),(561,47,3,'Bit by a Dead Bee','Walt and Jesse become short on cash when they try to cover their tracks. Meanwhile, the DEA has a lead that could them straight to Walt and Jesse.','2009-03-22'),(562,47,4,'Down','Walt attempts to reconnect with his family, while Jesse struggles to rebuild his life.','2009-03-29'),(563,47,5,'Breakage','Hank suffers from the aftermath of his encounter with Tuco. Meanwhile, Jesse hires a crew to get their product out on the streets.','2009-04-05'),(564,47,6,'Peekaboo','Walt\'s secret is in jeopardy when Skyler thanks Gretchen for paying for his treatment.','2009-04-12'),(565,47,7,'Negro y Azul','Jesse and Walt discuss expanding into new territories; Hank struggles to fit in; Skyler pursues a new job opportunity; Jesse gets to know his landlord.','2009-04-19'),(566,47,8,'Better Call Saul','Walt and Jesse seek advice from a shady attorney when Badger gets in trouble with the law; the DEA believes they have caught up with \"Heisenberg\" ; Hank returns.','2009-04-26'),(567,47,9,'4 Days Out','Walt and his family wait for news after he undergoes a PET-CT scan. Walt follows Saul\'s advice; Jesse\'s relationship with Jane is put on hold when he and Walt head to the desert for a marathon of cooking.','2009-05-03'),(568,47,10,'Over','Walt and Hank get into a heated argument at a party. Skyler opens up to her boss. Jane hides her relationship with Jesse from her father.','2009-05-10'),(569,47,11,'Mandala','As the end of her pregnancy finds Skyler conflicted about her feelings, a dealer\'s death forces Walt to look for somewhere to unload a load of meth.','2009-05-17'),(570,47,12,'Phoenix','As Walt explores money laundering options, he and Jesse spar over the profits from their latest deal. Jesse and Jane clash with her father. Walt makes a fatal decision.','2009-05-24'),(571,47,13,'ABQ','Skyler confronts Walt about his secrecy; Jesse falls apart; and Jane\'s grief-stricken father takes action that results in further tragedy.','2009-05-31'),(572,48,1,'No Más','Walt faces a new threat, on a new front and deals with an increasingly angry Skyler, who must consider what to do next with her life and the kids. Meanwhile, Jesse comes face-to-face with some startling self-revelations.','2010-03-21'),(573,48,2,'Caballo sin Nombre','Despite ever-increasing tension between Walt and Skyler, he pulls out all the stops in an effort to reconcile with the family. Elsewhere, Saul is instrumental in getting Jesse involved in a most-unusual investment opportunity.','2010-03-28'),(574,48,3,'I.F.T.','Walt ignores Skyler\'s demands, furthering the rift between them and pushing her to break bad. Still suffering from panic and anxiety attacks, Hank crosses a line at work.','2010-04-04'),(575,48,4,'Green Light','Walt loses control as he reacts to Skyler\'s news, endangering his job and relationships with Saul and Jesse. Hank throws himself into his blue meth investigation. Jesse enacts a new plan.','2010-04-11'),(576,48,5,'Más','Gus increases his efforts to lure Walt back into business, forcing a rift between Walt and Jesse. Skyler doubts her new relationship. Marie confides in Skyler about her concern for Hank\'s well-being.','2010-04-18'),(577,48,6,'Sunset','Walt settles into his new surroundings; Walt, Jr. wants answers about his parents\' relationship; Hank\'s investigation causes problems for Walt and Jesse.','2010-04-25'),(578,48,7,'One Minute','Hank\'s increasing volatility forces a confrontation with Jesse and trouble at work. Skyler pressures Walt to make a deal. Gus\' actions have severe consequences.','2010-05-02'),(579,48,8,'I See You','The family waits for news about Hank. While Jesse covers at the lab, Walt attempts to placate Gus. After witnessing a disturbing outburst, Walt worries he and his family are in danger.','2010-05-09'),(580,48,9,'Kafkaesque','As Hank\'s hospital bills stack up, Skyler hatches a plan. Walt and Gus come to a better understanding. Jesse, looking for more independence, pursues a new opportunity.','2010-05-16'),(581,48,10,'Fly','Walt becomes obsessed with a contaminant in the lab and refuses to finish the cook until it is eliminated. A frustrated Jesse attempts to get Walt back on track.','2010-05-23'),(582,48,11,'Abiquiu','Skyler gets involved with Walt\'s business. Hank struggles with his recovery. Jesse makes a startling discovery after meeting a girl at group therapy.','2010-05-30'),(583,48,12,'Half Measures','Against Walt\'s advice, Jesse lashes out. Fearing for Jesse\'s safety, Walt takes drastic action to intervene and tragic event leads to a shocking confrontation.','2010-06-06'),(584,48,13,'Full Measure','With Jesse on the run and Mike in hot pursuit, Walt negotiates a bargain with Gus and concocts a disturbing plan to provide for his and Jesse\'s safety.','2010-06-13'),(585,49,1,'Box Cutter','Walt and Jesse face the deadly consequences of their actions. Skyler deals with a puzzling disappearance, as Marie struggles to help Hank with his recovery.','2011-07-17'),(586,49,2,'Thirty-Eight Snub','Walt attempts to form a new alliance as he plans his next move. Skyler pushes Walt towards a business opportunity, in hopes of protecting the family.','2011-07-24'),(587,49,3,'Open House','Events spiral out of control at Jesse\'s place. Skyler reluctantly asks for Saul\'s help. Marie returns to an old pastime and a friend asks Hank for help.','2011-07-31'),(588,49,4,'Bullet Points','The Cartel takes steps to gain the upper hand. Walt and Skyler share an embarrassing secret with the rest of the family. Jesse\'s activities draw unwanted attention.','2011-08-07'),(589,49,5,'Shotgun','When Jesse goes missing, Walt fears the worst. Skyler has an unlikely reunion. Hank shares some bad news with Detective Tim Roberts.','2011-08-14'),(590,49,6,'Cornered','Skyler makes an unsettling discovery. Walter, Jr. pushes his dad into a questionable purchase. Jesse offers Mike some unexpected help.','2011-08-21'),(591,49,7,'Problem Dog','A frustrated Walt gambles on a risky new plan. Skyler\'s business venture hits a snag. Hank recruits Walter, Jr. for an unusual outing.','2011-08-28'),(592,49,8,'Hermanos','Skyler develops an unusual solution to her money troubles. Hank enlists Walt to investigate a theory. Walt\'s impatience with Jesse grows.','2011-09-04'),(593,49,9,'Bug','Skyler\'s past mistakes come back to haunt her. Gus takes action to thwart his rivals. Jesse seeks Walt\'s help, with mixed results.','2011-09-11'),(594,49,10,'Salud','Walt\'s family worries when he doesn\'t turn up for Walter, Jr.\'s 16th birthday. Jesse is forced to put his lab skills to the test without Mr. White\'s help.','2011-09-18'),(595,49,11,'Crawl Space','Walt takes drastic action to protect his secret and Gus. Skyler\'s efforts to solve Ted\'s financial problems hit a wall.','2011-09-25'),(596,49,12,'End Times','Hank pushes Gomez to pursue one last lead, while Walt struggles to protect the family. Jesse gets alarming news and rushes to meet with Mr. White.','2011-10-02'),(597,49,13,'Face Off','Walt and Jesse team up to take on Gus. With Saul\'s help, Walt finds an unexpected ally.','2011-10-09'),(598,50,1,'Live Free or Die','As Walt deals with the aftermath of the Casa Tranquila explosion, Hank works to wrap up his investigation of Gus\' empire.','2012-07-15'),(599,50,2,'Madrigal','Walt and Jesse pursue an unlikely business partner. The DEA filters through various leads in hopes of finding something.','2012-07-22'),(600,50,3,'Hazard Pay','Walt and Jesse formulate a new business plan. Walt shares a secret with Marie.','2012-07-29'),(601,50,4,'Fifty-One','Walt celebrates another birthday. Skyler contemplates her options, and an associate puts a crimp in Walt and Jesse\'s business strategy.','2012-08-05'),(602,50,5,'Dead Freight','Walt\'s team gets creative to obtain the methylamine they need to continue their operation.','2012-08-12'),(603,50,6,'Buyout','Walt, Jesse, and Mike struggle over the future of their business, as occupational hazards weigh on Jesse.','2012-08-19'),(604,50,7,'Say My Name','Walt takes control of business matters; Mike deals with the consequences of his actions.','2012-08-26'),(605,50,8,'Gliding Over All','Walt takes care of loose ends; Walt makes a dangerous decision.','2012-09-02'),(606,50,9,'Blood Money','As Walt and Jesse adjust to life out of the business, Hank grapples with a troubling lead.','2013-08-11'),(607,50,10,'Buried','While Skyler\'s past catches up with her, Walt covers his tracks. Jesse continues to struggle with his guilt.','2013-08-18'),(608,50,11,'Confessions','Jesse decides to make a change, while Walt and Skyler try to deal with an unexpected demand.','2013-08-25'),(609,50,12,'Rabid Dog','An unusual strategy starts to bear fruit, while plans are set in motion that could change everything.','2013-09-01'),(610,50,13,'To\'hajiilee','Things heat up for Walt in unexpected ways.','2013-09-08'),(611,50,14,'Ozymandias','Everyone copes with radically changed circumstances.','2013-09-15'),(612,50,15,'Granite State','Events set in motion long ago move toward a conclusion.','2013-09-22'),(613,50,16,'Felina','All bad things must come to an end.','2013-09-29'),(614,51,1,'Butcher: A Short Film','Butcher relives the past, recalling violence and betrayal on the rough road towards finding his wife Becca.','2020-09-10'),(615,51,2,'Starlight - Never Truly Vanish (Official Music Video)','“Your presence truly blessed us from the start. You will never truly vanish from our hearts.” Rest in Peace Translucent, 1980-2020.','2021-06-04'),(616,51,3,'Vought News Network: Seven on 7 with Cameron Coleman (July 2021)','Today on Vought News Network: An update on America\'s favorite hero, Homelander. Meet the new man: Victoria Neuman announces FBSA hire. Where is Alastair?: Church of the Collective head missing amidst new allegations.','2021-07-07'),(617,51,4,'Vought News Network: Seven on 7 with Cameron Coleman (August 2021)','Today on Vought News Network: Is Starlight headed for a supernova? Making Waves: Deep’s bombshell allegations about Church of the Collective. Wall They’ve Got: Homelander fans stand up against super-terrorists.','2021-08-07'),(618,51,5,'A-Train - Faster (Official Music Video)','\"Faster than the speed of light, watching as your dreams take flight. I think I should stand and fight, then disappear into the night.”','2021-09-01'),(619,51,6,'Vought News Network: Seven on 7 with Cameron Coleman (September 2021)','Today on Vought News Network: Is the FBSA strong arming Vought? San Diego superhero sees popularity soar! A-Train\'s new single speeding up the charts.','2021-09-07'),(620,51,7,'Vought News Network: Seven on 7 with Cameron Coleman (October 2021)','Today on Vought News Network: Starlight Sells Out - Heroine’s costume is almost as popular as Homelander’s this halloween; Black Noir hunts serial killer to keep tri-state area safe; FBSA oversteps again as they target Ezekiel.','2021-10-07'),(621,51,8,'The Deep x Liquid Death','A Special Message from The Deep, Liquid Death Mountain Water’s new Chief Sustainability Associate.','2021-10-07'),(622,51,9,'Vought News Network: Seven on 7 with Cameron Coleman (November 2021)','Today on Vought News Network: Victoria Neuman Gives Herself a Virtual Victory Parade. A Train: “I Promise To Have A New Race As Fast As Possible.\" Payback’s Legendary Hero Gunpowder Teaches Kids About The 2nd Amendment.','2021-11-07'),(623,51,10,'Vought News Network: Seven on 7 with Cameron Coleman (December 2021)','Today on Vought News Network: Silent Knight Brings Bulletproof Cheer; Gecko On Vought’s Naughty List; and Starlight Awarded Top Honor at Holiday Benefit.','2021-12-07'),(624,51,11,'Vought News Network: Seven on 7 with Cameron Coleman (January 2022)','Today on Vought News Network: Anticipation High for Vought Hero Draft; Tiny Hero\'s Big Film Premiere; A Fair & Balanced Conversation with the FBSA.','2022-01-07'),(625,51,12,'Buster Beaver\'s Official TV Commercial','This #NationalPizzaDay, there’s no better place to be than Buster Beaver’s. Visit today and sign up for Buster’s Pizza Pals Club to get 7x the tokens. Come on in and Eat the Beav!','2022-02-09'),(626,51,13,'Dawn of the Seven | Official Trailer','Coming June 3. When darkness descends on the world, and it seems all hope is lost, seven heroes will rise. Seven who will stand. Seven who will fight. Seven who will restore light and hope, and see the sun rise on a new era. This is the true story of the greatest superhero team the world has ever known. This is the Dawn of The Seven.','2022-05-20'),(627,51,14,'Soldier Boy PSA | 1984','This Memorial Day, Vought International remembers America\'s first Superhero - Soldier Boy. In this classic PSA, he spoke up to help protect the youth of our great nation, reminding them that \"taking drugs is not cool, and anyone who does is a loser.\" Be sure to hit the subscribe button to honor his legacy.','2022-05-30'),(628,51,15,'American Hero | Behind the Scenes Mansion Tour','Tonight at 9/8C on Vought+, it’s the season finale of #AmericanHero! Three contestants remain, but only TWO will join #TheSeven! Will Starlight choose her old flame Supersonic? Or will someone else be moving into the Seven Tower? Tune in tonight for the SHOCKING final episode, brought to you by Lean Lady Frozen Dinners by Vought: Where slim tastes super! On this exclusive Behind the Scenes Mansion Tour, Vought\'s own Ashley Barrett takes you inside American Hero Mansion, to see contestants vie for a chance to be America\'s next top hero.','2022-06-04'),(629,51,16,'Soldier Boy | Guest Appearance on Solid Gold','Soldier Boy serenades the Solid Gold dancers with a super rendition of Blondie\'s \"Rapture\" in this classic clip recorded just before his heroic final mission. Shortly after this, he was posthumously awarded a Vrammy for Best Special Guest Performance!','2022-06-10'),(630,51,17,'The Deep | Not Without My Dolphin | Official Trailer','Based on the bestselling autobiography, Deeper: A Memoir, comes a thrilling story of Love, Loss, Redemption, Light, and Fresca. Only on Vought+.  Starring 3 time Vemmy Award Winner The Deep as Deep, and MTV Movie Award Nominee Billy Zane as Alastair Adana.','2022-06-14'),(631,51,18,'Crimson Countess | Chimps Don\'t Cry | Official Music Video','After a lifetime of using her super powers to protect America as part of legendary supe team Payback, Crimson Countess is using the power of music to help chimps live happier lives. Vought cares about simian well-being. So for the next seven hours, 1% of every Big Homie Burger sold will be donated to Crimson Countess\' Chimp Country Foundation to help troubled Chimps.','2022-06-17'),(632,51,19,'Supersonic | Super-Sweet - You Got Your License To Drive (Me Crazy) | Visualizer','Supersonic may be gone, but he\'ll live forever in our hearts - and our ears! Reminisce about summer nights cruising in the Jetta with “You Got Your License To Drive (Me Crazy),\" and all of SuperSweet’s catalogue, exclusively on Voughtify.','2022-06-23'),(633,51,20,'Deep Thoughts With The Deep','If you feel like #WisdomWednesday is surface-level, it\'s time for #DeepThoughtsWithTheDeep. Here\'s a collection of the Lord of the Seven Seas\' greatest wisdom that will shape our lives forever. Continue your journey of enlightenment with #DeeperAndDeeper, the most intimate superhero interview of all time, now available on Audible.','2022-07-27'),(634,51,21,'Soldier Boy | Red Thunder Scene','We saw your tweets, opened your emails, and read your one-star reviews. That’s why we’re making the brave choice to bring Soldier Boy back to Vought++. Films like Red Thunder will now have this content warning to properly prepare patriots before they press play!','2022-08-11'),(635,51,22,'A-Train | Turbo Rush Full Commercial','For months, you’ve asked to see the most inspirational commercial ever made again. Originally taken off air because the testing was too strong, this is “Taste The Movement,” the full-length spot for A-Train’s Turbo Rush. Look for a super back-to-school sale on 7-Packs now!','2022-09-06'),(636,51,23,'Super-Sweet | Rock My Kiss','On this day in 2008, one glance across study hall changed everything. Celebrate 14 years of Rock My Kiss, the chart-topping single from the boys of Super-Sweet. Upgrade to a Voughtify Premium Student subscription to listen to a Supersonic bonus tribute!','2022-09-10'),(637,51,24,'My Dad Works For Vought','This National Working Parents Day, we’re proud to support mothers and fathers like Homelander, who somehow manage to keep our country safe while raising the next generation of heroes. Work at Vought and get occasional access to our on-site Vought Tots Daycare!','2022-09-16'),(638,51,25,'VNN | Vought Partners with G Fuel','On this special edition of VNN\'s Seven on 7, Cameron has the details on a new energy drink Vought has partnered with G Fuel on. Inspired by Compound V, it sharpens focus, increases energy, and in select cases, turns you into a weapon of mass destruction.','2022-09-28'),(639,51,26,'The Deep | Kirei Shoyu Commercial','This Soy Sauce Day, enjoy a bottle of Kirei Shoyu, full of flavor and peak freshness. Now back in stock at your local store, thanks to the Deep personally escorting a cargo shipment across the ocean. Get 7% off with promo code GOODLUCK!','2022-10-01'),(640,51,27,'The Deep | World Octopus Day','This year, we lost one of Deep’s dear friends Timothy, who was sadly eaten by a predator. We can’t bring back Timothy, but we can try to make oceans safer for cephalopods on World Octopus Day. Vought is proud to offer continued support, thoughts and prayers for Timothy’s family!','2022-10-08'),(641,51,28,'2022 Voughtify Recapped | A-Train','Coming to you a week late so we could collect more of your data and iron out a few technical glitches, it\'s the 2022 Voughtify Recapped! Join A-Train as we celebrate the Top 5 songs of the year, and remember to separate art (Rapture) from the artist and traitor (Soldier Boy).','2022-12-07'),(642,51,29,'Ashley Barrett | Q1 Earnings Recap','Transparency has always been our core value at Vought. That’s why ahead of our Q1 earnings call, we’ve prepped this summary for all shareholders to enjoy. Here\'s CEO Ashley Barrett, who has the board’s full confidence and was just given a new seven-month contract!','2023-01-24'),(643,51,30,'Queen Maeve | In Memoriam','Tonight, we honor Queen Maeve with this emotional in memoriam at the Supie Awards. A hero on and off screen, her acting in Dawn of the Seven and Her Majesty will be studied by performing arts students at Godolkin University for years to come. Rest In Pride, Queen!','2023-03-12'),(644,51,31,'Show Me the Doll','Hello boys and girls. This is Mr. Butcher and he’s here today to teach you all about supes. Because supes, you see, ain’t always nice. Sometimes they are very, very not nice. So grab your dollies and sit down criss-cross-applesauce: story time is about to start.','2019-08-02'),(645,51,32,'Clean Face Clean Streets | Starlight\'s Skincare','You’re not crime-fighting ready, until you’re camera ready. To get the deepest clean for the most sensitive skin, try the new oil-free skincare line from the freshest face among The Seven: Wish by Starlight. A Vought International Company.','2019-05-01'),(646,51,33,'Newstand','Everyone loves superheroes. They swoop out of the sky and save the day. This city’s in thrall to them: we buy their toys, watch their movies, read their fawning headlines. But if you knew just half of what supes get up to, you’d think again. That’s where Butcher comes in. He’s here to spank those supes when they get out of line. And he won’t rest until he’s done with each and every one of them.','2019-06-05'),(647,51,34,'Vought Corporate Video','Welcome, New Employee, to the world’s most admired company: Vought International. You may know us as the home of your favorite heroes, but we’re much more than that. Learn more about your super colleagues and explore the various ways that Vought impacts our lives: from our customer service endeavors, to our new national security tactics. See how Vought International makes the world a safer place.','2020-10-07'),(648,51,35,'An Important Update on Homelander','It’s a dark day for America. But together, we can keep an innocent hero #HomeFree. Here’s CEO Ashley Barrett with more on Homelander.','2023-06-14'),(649,51,36,'Cameron\'s Promise to Homelander','If there’s one thing Americans can count on right now, it’s that Cameron is committed to debunking the lies surrounding this shameless facade of a “trial.” Join him every night as he brings you hard-hitting news, and teaches the woke mob basic vocabulary like “loving father”!','2023-06-15'),(650,51,37,'Black Noir Announces Call of Duty','BREAKING: Vought and VNN can exclusively confirm that Homelander, Black Noir and a hero who shall not be named are coming to Call of Duty. More insightful soundbites from Noir in this press conference for the ages!','2023-07-10'),(651,51,38,'A Love Letter to America','Today, Vought brings you a love letter to AMERICA, rated \"Too Patriotic\" for TV. Please enjoy with an ice cold Turbo Rush!','2024-02-11'),(652,51,39,'Vought and Homelander Support Singer-Neuman','Despite what the fake news might tell you, Vought and Homelander have ALWAYS been steadfast friends with Robert Singer and Victoria Neuman. This Tuesday, we\'re proud to stand with them, and work towards a new era for the SUPERhuman community!','2024-03-05'),(653,51,40,'Singer Neuman 2024 - A Stronger America','At Vought, our primary goal is to create a stronger, MORE SUPER America. That’s why we’re endorsing Robert Singer and Victoria Neuman, who have promised to give Superhumans more just than a seat at the table. We’ll be holding them accountable every step of the way!','2024-05-21'),(654,51,41,'Vought\'s American History','We’re tired of socialist teachers brainwashing your kids with their woke takes on the “Civil War” and “Women’s Rights.\" That’s why we’re launching Vought’s American History – designed to teach your lil’ patriots the God-honest truth about this nation’s history. Buy now and get a special edition copy with a foreword from Homelander himself!','2024-06-07'),(655,51,42,'Deep Thoughts With The Deep - The Deeper Version','This World Oceans Day, Vought is proud to present the triumphant return of Deep Thoughts With The Deep. This time, even Deeper! Listen as The Lord of the Seven Seas ponders provocative questions that no other mind in history has dared to tackle.','2024-06-08'),(656,51,43,'Training A-Train - First Look','From the studio that brought you Rising Tide and Dawn of the Seven comes TRAINING A-TRAIN. Now in production, directed by award-winning filmmaker Adam Bourke and starring The World’s Fastest Man. Here’s A-Train on why this is his most heart-wrenching role yet!','2024-06-10'),(657,51,44,'The Deep x Liquid Death - The Dangers of Sugar','Today, The Deep is proud to announce a renewed partnership with Liquid Death. Two years ago, he taught children to bring death to plastic, and now he is educating them on the dangers of sugar. He takes his job as role model and health & wellness ambassador Deep-ly serious!','2024-06-11'),(658,51,45,'Vought On Ice','This Thursday, we’re proud to present Vought on Ice! It’s the most festive, family-friendly show ever – converting non-believers into God-fearing, upstanding citizens in under three hours. Nothing says \"Merry Christmas\" like Homelander landing a triple axel!','2024-06-11'),(659,51,46,'Vought On Ice - \"Let\'s Put The Christ Back In Christmas\"','Critics, families and online trolls have all been raving about Vought On Ice! That’s why we’re bringing you an exclusive and extended look at the magic.  Once you’re done watching, stream “Let’s Put the Christ Back in Christmas” anytime on Voughtify!','2024-06-14'),(660,51,47,'Truth Con Recap with Firecracker','At Vought, we see the same spark in Firecracker as Homelander does: a fearless freedom fighter. Hear it for yourself today on this week\'s episode of Truthbomb as she recounts this weekend’s horrific events, and help ignite the resistance by sharing with #WhereWeGoOneWeGoVought!','2024-06-18'),(661,51,48,'Opera GX presents BROWSER by Vought','Vought is proud to usher in a new era of Internet privacy. Together with Opera GX, we’ve built BROWSER by Vought. What it lacks in branding creativity, it makes up for in speed and security. Download it today and you’ll be review bombing woke TV shows in no time!','2024-06-22'),(662,51,49,'Firecracker and Deep - Up Where We Belong','You saw it already on Firecracker’s recent six-hour VNN special, but for the first time ever online, it’s her full performance of “Up Where We Belong” featuring Deep. God Himself smiled down from heaven as they sang, and we bet He’ll be streaming on Voughtify too!','2024-06-24'),(663,51,50,'V52 Expo Recap with A-Train, Deep and Noir','If you missed #V52, we trust you had a completely invalid excuse or were trapped under something heavy. Here’s A-Train, Deep and Noir to recap the most important and influential day in entertainment history, destined to shape culture for at least the next seven decades!','2024-06-28'),(664,51,51,'Voughtality - For a Super You','Ever wonder how CEO Ashley Barrett looks so composed in every meeting or press conference? Her secret is simple – Voughtality! Featuring a line of products that will have you feeling fresh and moist on every level. Voughtality – For A Super You.','2024-07-01'),(665,51,52,'Vought Fresh Farms Ad with Firecracker','At Vought Fresh Farms, we’ll do anything to make sure you get the right amount of dairy. That’s why our milk is made from only the youngest and most God-fearing of cows, homegrown right here in America. Vought Fresh Farms, the only choice for true patriots like Homelander!','2024-07-05'),(666,51,53,'Ashley Barrett Addresses Fake News','At Vought, our top priority always has been transparency. That’s why CEO Ashley Barrett is here to debunk the woke conspiracy theories on the dark web. Remember, if you’re going to share misinformation, make sure you get it from reputable patriots like Firecracker!','2024-07-09'),(667,51,54,'Deep Thoughts With The Deep - Even Deeper','Back by popular demand, Vought proudly presents a new wave of Deep Thoughts with The Deep. Keep the waters of your mind still as you soak in these pearls of wisdom. Then when you’re done, be sure to share with a bro!','2024-07-10'),(668,51,55,'The Deep\'s Olympics Ad','This week, Olympics viewers will be delighted watching the events AND the ad breaks. Here\'s a first look at a new TV spot featuring The Deep, the greatest swimmer of all-time. He\'d easily be world champion if Supers were allowed to compete!','2024-07-22'),(669,51,56,'Soldier Boy World War II Found Footage','Our social media department on Floor 47 has seen lots of conversation about Soldier Boy the past few days. He’s still a traitor, but it’s footage like this that helps us remember his better days as a true hero. Share to tell someone you love GOD BLESS AMERICA!','2024-07-29'),(670,51,57,'See Something, Say Something - Official Music Video','It’s more than a festive tune – it’s a cry of freedom from patriots everywhere! SEE SOMETHING, SAY SOMETHING. Performed by puppets, adored by everyone. Sing along, then call the hotline to report those groomers. Remember - T is for TRAITOR!','2024-11-01'),(671,51,58,'Get it Done','There’s a new supe in The Seven, and she’s really shaking things up. When Stormfront arrives on the scene, she threatens Homelander’s leadership and creates a whole new level of problems for the Boys. Plus, she throws some pretty freaky plasma bolts.','2020-09-10'),(672,51,59,'Bad Guy','Homelander is America’s hero: he’s practically a perfect being in every way. Except that he’s a maniacal, super-powered killing machine who just unleashed a bunch of super terrorists on the world. But in every other way, he’s pretty perfect.','2020-09-10'),(673,52,1,'The Name of the Game','When a Supe kills the love of his life, A/V salesman Hughie Campbell teams up with Billy Butcher, a vigilante hell-bent on punishing corrupt Supes — and Hughie’s life will never be the same again.','2019-07-25'),(674,52,2,'Cherry','The Boys get themselves a Superhero, Starlight gets payback, Homelander gets naughty, and a Senator gets naughtier.','2019-07-25'),(675,52,3,'Get Some','It’s the race of the century. A-Train versus Shockwave, vying for the title of World’s Fastest Man. Meanwhile, the Boys are reunited and it feels so good.','2019-07-25'),(676,52,4,'The Female of the Species','On a very special episode of The Boys… an hour of guts, gutterballs, airplane hijackings, madness, ghosts, and one very intriguing Female. Oh, and lots of heart — both in the sentimental sense, and in the gory literal sense.','2019-07-25'),(677,52,5,'Good for the Soul','The Boys head to the “Believe” Expo to follow a promising lead in their ongoing war against the Supes. There might — MIGHT — be a homicidal infant, but you’ll have to see for yourself.','2019-07-25'),(678,52,6,'The Innocents','SUPER IN AMERICA (2019). Vought Studios. Genre: Reality. Starring: Homelander, Queen Maeve, Black Noir, The Deep, A-Train, Starlight, Tara Reid, Billy Zane.','2019-07-25'),(679,52,7,'The Self-Preservation Society','Never trust a washed-up Supe — the Boys learn this lesson the hard way. Meanwhile, Homelander digs into his past, Starlight discovers that love hurts, and if you’re ever in Sandusky, Ohio and a girl asks if she can touch your gills, say NO.','2019-07-25'),(680,52,8,'You Found Me','Season Finale Time! Questions answered! Secrets revealed! Conflicts… conflicted! Characters exploded! And so much more!','2019-07-25'),(681,53,1,'The Big Ride','Season 2! New and improved! Now with 50% more explosive decapitations, terrorists, S&M hookers, cults, and a new pine fresh scent! But wait, there’s more! 2X MORE blood, guts and gore than the other leading brands! This exclusive offer is available only on Amazon Prime Video! Don’t delay! Order now!','2020-09-03'),(682,53,2,'Proper Preparation and Planning','The Boys get themselves a Super Terrorist, Starlight gets evidence against Vought, The Deep gets in touch with his feelings, and Homelander gets himself a family (sort of).  All that, and a hard-hitting exposé on why Super Suits don’t have pockets.','2020-09-03'),(683,53,3,'Over the Hill with the Swords of a Thousand Men','Attention: If you or a loved one were exposed to Compound V, you may be entitled to financial compensation. Vought has given the drug to multiple victims, without their knowledge or consent. If you believe that you or a loved one were administered Compound V, call the law firm of Bremmer & Bremmer at 1-888-177-2774 for a free legal consultation. Know your rights!','2020-09-03'),(684,53,4,'Nothing Like It in the World','Road trip! The Boys head to North Carolina to follow a lead on a mysterious Supe named Liberty. And did you know a person’s choice of candy bars might tell you if they’re a serial killer? Watch and learn the warning signs! This episode could save your life!','2020-09-10'),(685,53,5,'We Gotta Go Now','VoughtStudios is pleased to announce that filming has begun on #DawnOfTheSeven. 12 years of VCU movies have led to this. If you like movies about One Hero, you’ll love a movie about Seven Heroes. Introducing newest member @RealStormfront! See how the legend began! In theaters Summer 2021!','2020-09-17'),(686,53,6,'The Bloody Doors Off','The Sage Grove Center® is dedicated to caring for those struggling with mental illness. Our compassionate doctors and counselors provide personalized services to help patients live their best lives. If you or a loved one need help, call the Sage Grove Center today at 1-800-122-8585. A proud subsidiary of Global Wellness Services®, which is a proud subsidiary of Vought International®','2020-09-24'),(687,53,7,'Butcher, Baker, Candlestick Maker','Congresswoman Victoria Neuman’s sham Congressional Hearing against Vought takes place in 3 DAYS. Are we going to let her criminalize Superheroes when we need them most? We have to stand up against such blatant partisan politics. Please join fellow Patriotic Americans and send $20 to VOUGHTPROMISE.COM to tell Neuman and her Kangaroo Court Cronies that they won’t win, “Not On Our Watch”™.','2020-10-01'),(688,53,8,'What I Know','***SUPER VILLAIN ALERT*** YOU ARE RECEIVING THIS NOTIFICATION FROM THE DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY. A SUPER VILLAIN ALERT HAS BEEN ISSUED FOR YOUR AREA. PLEASE BE VIGILANT AND REPORT ANY SUSPICIOUS PERSONS OR ACTIVITY. IF YOU BELIEVE YOU HAVE SEEN A SUPER VILLAIN, DO NOT APPROACH OR ATTEMPT TO APPREHEND THEM. CONTACT LAW ENFORCEMENT IMMEDIATELY','2020-10-08'),(689,54,1,'Payback','You and a guest are invited to the premiere of DAWN OF THE SEVEN this Tuesday at 7PM in Vought Tower’s Lamplighter Memorial Theater! Screening will be followed by a Q&A with director Adam Bourke and an after-party with Supe DJ Malchemical on the turntables! Join us for the greatest true origin story ever told about America’s number one Superhero team and see how the legend began!','2022-06-02'),(690,54,2,'The Only Man in the Sky','Homelander. America’s greatest Superhero. Defending our shores from sea to shining sea. Today, America honors him on his birthday. And the Vought Shopping Network is celebrating by offering the exclusive Homelander Limited Birthday Edition Gold Coin for only $99.95 (plus tax and shipping) while supplies last. Vought Gold Commemorative Coins: An investment that lasts a lifetime.','2022-06-02'),(691,54,3,'Barbary Coast','Tonight at 9/8C on Vought Plus, it’s the season finale of #AmericanHero! Three contestants remain, but only TWO will join #TheSeven! Will Starlight choose her old flame Supersonic? Or will someone else be moving into the Seven Tower? Tune in tonight for the SHOCKING final episode, brought to you by Lean Lady Frozen Dinners by Vought: Where slim tastes super!','2022-06-02'),(692,54,4,'Glorious Five Year Plan','Tonight, streaming live exclusively for Supeporn.com Super-Subscribers, it’s the #ClashOfTheDildos! Which of The Seven-inspired dildos will crush the competition in this tip-to-tip challenge? Will it be the reigning champion Homelander Star-Spangled Banger or Starlight’s electrified Star-Brator? Join us as we put these pleasure-pounding penetrators through their paces! Only on Supeporn.com!','2022-06-09'),(693,54,5,'The Last Time to Look on This World of Lies','Did you know chimpanzees are an endangered species largely because of human activity? But you can help by supporting construction costs for Crimson Countess’s Chimp Country! This beautiful refuge for chimpanzees will feature a banana plantation, four daily stunt shows, and a petting zoo! And when you donate, you’ll be entered to win a private video chat with Crimson Countess! Donate today!','2022-06-16'),(694,54,6,'Herogasm','You’re invited to the 70th Annual Herogasm! You must present this invitation in order to be admitted! Same rules as always: no cameras, no non-Supe guests unless they sign an NDA and they’re DTF, and no telling any news media! It’s BYOD, but food, alcohol and lube will be provided! And please remember to RSVP so we can get an accurate headcount for the caterer!','2022-06-23'),(695,54,7,'Here Comes a Candle to Light You to Bed','Did someone say birthday? Come celebrate at Buster Beaver’s with our new Deluxe VIP Birthday Package, with seating for up to 30 guests, ten large two-topping pizzas, and ten pitchers of your choice of soda! And of course, a special birthday play starring Buster Beaver and his cast of furry forest friends! All for only $199.99 + tax! Buster Beaver’s Pizza! Where Kids Make the Rules®!','2022-06-30'),(696,54,8,'The Instant White-Hot Wild','Calling all patriots! Let’s show Homelander we’ve got his back and we’re not going to let Starlight and her Starlight House of Horrors get away with trafficking children and drinking their adrenaline! It’s time for real Americans to fight back! Join the Hometeamers and Stormchasers tomorrow at Vought Square! Stand back and stand by!','2022-07-07'),(697,55,1,'Department of Dirty Tricks','CALLING ALL PATRIOTS. BE AT THE COURTHOUSE TOMORROW FOR HOMELANDER\'S #VERDICT AND BE READY. IF THE CORRUPT \"JUSTICE\" SYSTEM WANTS TO F**K AROUND, THEY\'RE GONNA FIND OUT. #HOMEFREE','2024-06-13'),(698,55,2,'Life Among the Septics','Did you know globalists put chemicals in food to make us gay, Dakota Bob is a demon from hell, and the Moon isn\'t real? Find out what they don\'t want you to know at #TruthCon!','2024-06-13'),(699,55,3,'We\'ll Keep the Red Flag Flying Here','This December at VoughtCoin Arena, experience the story of Christmas the way it was meant to be told... on ice! Vought Presents Vought on Ice! Tickets available now at VoughtOnIce.com!','2024-06-13'),(700,55,4,'Wisdom of the Ages','Vought News Network is proud to announce its new series #Truthbomb! Join host Firecracker and her celebrity guests for the live 6-hour premiere as they expose Starlight\'s Adrenochrome Parties!','2024-06-20'),(701,55,5,'Beware the Jabberwock, My Son','Attention #superfans! This year at #V52 see A-Train live and in person, as he presents an exclusive sneak peek at his powerful, true-life story: TRAINING A-TRAIN! V52: Powered by fans, for fans!','2024-06-27'),(702,55,6,'Dirty Business','Vernon Correctional Services provides compassionate rehabilitation to those in our care to prepare them for successful community reentry. At Vernon, it\'s not about custody. It\'s about family.','2024-07-04'),(703,55,7,'The Insider','Hey kids! Did you know your neighbor, uncle, or even Mom and Dad might be trying to destroy America? Find out how to stop them on the Avenue V Christmas Special! If you see something, say something!','2024-07-11'),(704,55,8,'Season Four Finale','Calling all patriots! We will not allow this stolen election to be certified tomorrow! We must stop Bob Singer\'s woke anti-Supe agenda! PREPARE FOR WAR! #WhereWeGoOneWeGoVought','2024-07-18'),(705,56,1,'Fifteen Inches of Sheer Dynamite','',NULL),(706,57,1,'The End\'s Beginning','Hostile townsfolk and a cunning mage greet Geralt in the town of Blaviken. Ciri finds her royal world upended when Nilfgaard sets its sights on Cintra.','2019-12-20'),(707,57,2,'Four Marks','Bullied and neglected, Yennefer accidentally finds a means of escape. Geralt\'s hunt for a so-called devil goes to hell. Ciri seeks safety in numbers.','2019-12-20'),(708,57,3,'Betrayer Moon','Geralt takes on another Witcher\'s unfinished business in a kingdom stalked by a ferocious beast. At a brutal cost, Yennefer forges a magical new future.','2019-12-20'),(709,57,4,'Of Banquets, Bastards and Burials','Against his better judgment, Geralt accompanies Jaskier to a royal ball. Ciri wanders into an enchanted forest. Yennefer tries to protect her charges.','2019-12-20'),(710,57,5,'Bottled Appetites','Heedless of warnings, Yennefer looks for a cure to restore what she\'s lost. Geralt inadvertently puts Jaskier in peril. The search for Ciri intensifies.','2019-12-20'),(711,57,6,'Rare Species','A mysterious man tries to entice Geralt to join a hunt for a rampaging dragon, a quest that attracts a familiar face. Ciri questions who she can trust.','2019-12-20'),(712,57,7,'Before a Fall','With the Continent at risk from Nilfgaard\'s rising power, Yennefer revisits her past, while Geralt reconsiders his obligation to the Law of Surprise.','2019-12-20'),(713,57,8,'Much More','A terrifying pack of foes lays Geralt low. Yennefer and her fellow mages prepare to fight back. A shaken Ciri depends on the kindness of a stranger.','2019-12-20'),(714,58,1,'A Grain of Truth','Geralt sets off with Ciri on a journey that leads him to an old friend. After the Battle of Sodden, Tissaia shows no mercy in her search for information.','2021-12-17'),(715,58,2,'Kaer Morhen','Seeking a safe place for Ciri, Geralt heads for home, but danger lurks everywhere — even Kaer Morhen. Yennefer\'s dreams could be the key to her freedom.','2021-12-17'),(716,58,3,'What Is Lost','Impatient with Geralt\'s methods, Ciri braves major obstacles to prove her mettle. Scheming and suspicion amongst the Brotherhood make Yennefer a target.','2021-12-17'),(717,58,4,'Redanian Intelligence','A guest at Kaer Morhen extends a guiding hand to Ciri — and an invitation to Geralt. On the run in Redania, Yennefer seeks safety below ground.','2021-12-17'),(718,58,5,'Turn Your Back','As a powerful mage joins the hunt for Ciri, she cuts a deal with Vesemir over his extraordinary discovery. Geralt explores the mystery of the monoliths.','2021-12-17'),(719,58,6,'Dear Friend...','A close friend is lost — and another found — as Geralt helps Ciri learn more about her power. Cahir warns Fringilla to focus on their primary mission.','2021-12-17'),(720,58,7,'Voleth Meir','Geralt turns to the bard Jaskier for help, Yennefer realizes just how special Ciri is, and tensions rise on the eve of Emperor Emhyr\'s visit to Cintra.','2021-12-17'),(721,58,8,'Family','Geralt faces off with a demon targeting his nearest and dearest while the most powerful players on the Continent ramp up their pursuit of Ciri.','2021-12-17'),(722,59,1,'Shaerrawedd','Geralt, Yennefer and Ciri journey to the far reaches of the Continent in search of a safe haven. King Vizimir puts his charming younger brother to use.','2023-06-29'),(723,59,2,'Unbound','A shocking discovery awaits Geralt after he obtains information on Rience. Ciri\'s sense of justice causes problems. Jaskier performs for a royal fan.','2023-06-29'),(724,59,3,'Reunion','Geralt seeks magical help from a family friend as Ciri and Yennefer clash over plans for the future. Philippa and Dijkstra scheme to get Vizimir in line.','2023-06-29'),(725,59,4,'The Invitation','Yennefer pitches a bold idea to the Brotherhood, Geralt strikes a dangerous deal with a ferryman, and Triss digs into the mystery of the missing novices.','2023-06-29'),(726,59,5,'The Art of the Illusion','Yennefer and Geralt step out arm in arm and dressed to kill at a lavish ball, but all is not as it seems during a night of revelry and revelations.','2023-06-29'),(727,59,6,'Everybody Has a Plan \'til They Get Punched in the Face','Betrayal and bloodshed rock the conclave when the hunt for Ciri comes to a head. As sides are chosen and enemies unmasked, nothing will ever be the same.','2023-07-27'),(728,59,7,'Out of the Fire, Into the Frying Pan','Haunted by faces from the past, Ciri endures the ultimate test of survival on a desperate journey under the harshest of conditions.','2023-07-27'),(729,59,8,'The Cost of Chaos','After the fateful events at Aretuza, Geralt and Yennefer struggle to pick up the pieces and reunite their family as war comes to the Continent.','2023-07-27'),(730,60,1,'What Doesn\'t Kill You Makes You Stronger','Geralt sets out to save Ciri from the claws of Emhyr, unaware of her true fate. Beset by Vilgefortz, Yennefer attempts to uncover his plan.','2025-10-30'),(731,60,2,'Dream of a Wish Fulfilled','Ciri gets a chance to prove herself during a robbery. Geralt gains an unlikely ally, as does Yennefer when she visits Montecalvo to look for sanctuary.','2025-10-30'),(732,60,3,'Trial by Ordeal','A witch trial pulls Geralt away from his quest. Ciri taps further into the darkness of her new life. Yennefer brings more recruits to her cause.','2025-10-30'),(733,60,4,'A Sermon of Survival','Yennefer\'s conviction starts to waver. Ciri opens up to Mistle about her true identity. Geralt finds himself at the mercy of Dijkstra.','2025-10-30'),(734,60,5,'The Joy of Cooking','Catching their breath before attempting a river crossing, Geralt and his party regale each other with stories and song, revealing a shocking truth.','2025-10-30'),(735,60,6,'Twilight of the Wolf','Out of options, Yennefer rallies her novices in a deadly battle against the army of Vilgefortz. A dangerous foe catches Ciri\'s scent.','2025-10-30'),(736,60,7,'What I love I do not carry','A trek through treacherous swamplands confronts Geralt with troubling visions. Emhyr discovers what he must do in order to claim absolute power.','2025-10-30'),(737,60,8,'Baptism of Fire','As the Continent sinks deeper into war, Geralt, Yennefer and Ciri each meet their fate on the roads they took to avoid it.','2025-10-30'),(738,61,1,'Inside Game of Thrones','A short look into the film-making process for the production Game of Thrones','2010-12-05'),(739,61,2,'15-Minute Preview','An approximately 15-minute preview of the first episode of Game of Thrones.','2011-04-03'),(740,61,3,'Making Game of Thrones','An exclusive 30-minute feature including never-before-seen footage from the set and interviews from the cast and crew.','2011-04-07'),(741,61,4,'El Juego Comienza','A spanish \"Canal +`\" production with interviews to some famous spanish movie directors like Alex de La Iglesia and extracts from last special \"Making Game Of Thrones\"','2011-04-10'),(742,61,5,'2011 Comic Con Panel','','2011-07-21'),(743,61,6,'You Win or You Die','A prequel to Game of Thrones Season 2 which recaps on the first season and gives insight into what\'s to come.','2012-03-24'),(744,61,9,'Ice and Fire: A Foreshadowing','Take a look back and a look forward to the fourth season of the hit HBO series, the show features clips from upcoming episodes, behind the scenes footage, interviews with talent, and cast members\' answers to questions posed by fans.','2014-02-09'),(745,61,10,'The Politics of Power: A Look Back at Season 3','Relive every thrilling, dramatic and tragic highlight from Season 3 of \"Game of Thrones\" in this comprehensive featurette. From Daenerys building a slave army to the infamous Red Wedding, not a detail is missed as recalled by the stars of the hit HBO series.','2014-03-12'),(746,61,11,'A Day in the Life','The 30-minute special documents one epic day of production as tackled by hundreds of crew members across three countries. In addition to a behind-the-scenes look at the action in Dubrovnik, Croatia, Belfast, Northern Ireland and Seville, Spain, the preview includes several never-before-seen features.','2015-02-08'),(747,61,12,'The Story So Far (2015)','Ahead of the eagerly-anticipated fifth season, we bring you up tp speed with the events of the epic fantasy drama to date. And to help the uninitiated ease into the wild world of Westeros, here\'s a beginner\'s guide to the fantasy epic.','2015-03-16'),(748,61,13,'World Premiere','See the stars of Game of Thrones arrive at the Tower of London for the world premiere of the hit show\'s fifth season. Sue Perkins and Jamie East host.','2015-03-19'),(749,61,14,'Red Nose Day \'Game Of Thrones\' Musical','“George R.R. Martin meets Chris Martin – what could go wrong?” That’s Emilia Clarke in the epic, 12-minute video for Coldplay’s totally fake Game of Thrones musical, right before she rips into a song called “Rastafarian Targaryen.” Here’s a sample lyric: “Call me Daenerys Targaryen when you want to reach me, and if you feel the love then you can call me Khalessi.” The sketch, part of Red Nose Day, includes cast members Kit Harington, Peter Dinklage, John Bradley, Rose Leslie, Charlotte Pope, Thomas Brodie-Sangster, Alfie Allen and Nikolaj Coster-Waldau, who performs a piano ballad called “Closer to Home” to a photo of Lena Headey as Cersei. (“Are you thinking about Joffrey? Such a spirited lad. I was his uncle, I was also his dad.”)','2015-05-22'),(750,61,15,'The Story So Far (2016)','Ahead of Season 6 of the epic saga, this special will bring viewers up to speed on the gripping storylines and compelling characters from the first five seasons. Writers and stars of the show give viewers an insight into key events of each season and explain the intrigues and power struggles at work in the lands of Westeros and beyond.','2016-04-20'),(751,61,16,'The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 1 & 2','The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 1 & 2','2016-08-01'),(752,61,17,'The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 3 & 4','The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 3 & 4','2016-08-01'),(753,61,18,'The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 5 & 6','The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 5 & 6','2016-08-01'),(754,61,19,'The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 7 & 8','The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 7 & 8','2016-08-01'),(755,61,20,'The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 9 & 10','The Game Revealed: Season 6 Episode 9 & 10','2016-08-01'),(756,61,21,'Anatomy of A Scene: The Battle of Winterfell','Anatomy of A Scene: The Battle of Winterfell','2016-06-19'),(757,61,22,'2016 Comic Con Panel','2016 Comic Con Panel','2016-07-22'),(758,61,23,'18 Hours at the Paint Hall','Take an inside look at an action-packed day inside the main production complex for ‘Game of Thrones’ in Belfast, Northern Ireland.','2016-07-03'),(759,61,24,'The Story So Far (2017)','Ahead of the season seven premiere, get up to speed on all the action in Game of Thrones with this re-cap of the story so far.','2017-07-13'),(760,61,25,'2017 Comic Con Panel','2017 Comic Con Panel','2017-07-21'),(761,61,26,'Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 1','Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 1','2017-08-01'),(762,61,27,'Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 2','Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 2','2017-08-01'),(763,61,28,'Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 3','Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 3','2017-08-01'),(764,61,29,'Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 4','Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 4','2017-08-06'),(765,61,30,'Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 5','Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 5','2017-08-13'),(766,61,31,'Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 6','Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 6','2017-08-20'),(767,61,32,'Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 7','Inside the Episode: Season 7 Episode 7','2017-08-28'),(768,61,33,'The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 1','The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 1','2017-08-28'),(769,61,34,'The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 2','Go inside the brutal battle between Greyjoy fleets with this clip from the latest episode of the 7-part behind-the-scenes series, The Game Revealed.','2017-09-07'),(770,61,35,'The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 3','The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 3','2017-09-11'),(771,61,36,'Conquest & Rebellion: An Animated History of the Seven Kingdoms','The story of the Targaryen Conquest which first unified the Seven Kingdoms, nearly 300 years before the War of the Five Kings, including the founding of King\'s Landing and creation of the Iron Throne.','2017-12-12'),(772,61,37,'The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 4','The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 4','2017-09-18'),(773,61,38,'The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 5','The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 5','2017-09-25'),(774,61,39,'The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 6','The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 6','2017-10-02'),(775,61,40,'The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 7','The Game Revealed: Season 7 Episode 7','2017-10-09'),(776,61,42,'60 Minutes Profile','60 Minutes Profile','2019-04-14'),(777,61,43,'The Story So Far (2018)','Catch up on all seven seasons of the global phenomenon that is Game of Thrones as fans and cast members take you through the story so far.','2019-04-13'),(778,61,44,'The Cast Remembers','First days on set, favorite costumes and scenes they\'ll never forget: the actors look back on filming eight seasons of Game of Thrones.','2019-04-08'),(779,61,45,'The Game Revealed: Season 8 Episode 1','\"This is the last time we\'re ever going to be doing this.\"','2019-04-15'),(780,61,46,'Inside the Episode: Season 8 Episode 1','The producers and writers of Game of Thrones give behind-the-scenes insight into the first episode from the final season of the fantasy epic. (S8, ep 1)','2019-04-14'),(781,61,47,'The Game Revealed: Season 8 Episode 2','The Game Revealed: Season 8 Episode 2','2019-04-22'),(782,61,48,'Inside the Episode: Season 8 Episode 2','Inside the Episode: Season 8 Episode 2','2019-04-21'),(783,61,49,'The Game Revealed: Season 8 Episode 3','The cast and crew sheds light on the extraordinary 11-week night shoot that culminated in the longest Game of Thrones episode to date.','2019-04-29'),(784,61,50,'Inside the Episode: Season 8 Episode 3','Series creators David Benioff and D.B. Weiss examine the episode\'s wins and losses.','2019-04-28'),(785,61,51,'The Game Revealed: Season 8 Episode 4','The Game Revealed: Season 8 Episode 4','2019-05-05'),(786,61,52,'Inside the Episode: Season 8 Episode 4','Inside the Episode: Season 8 Episode 4','2019-05-05'),(787,61,53,'The Game Revealed: Season 8 Episode 5','The Game Revealed: Season 8 Episode 5','2019-05-13'),(788,61,54,'Inside the Episode: Season 8 Episode 5','Inside the Episode: Season 8 Episode 5','2019-05-13'),(789,61,55,'Game of Thrones: The Last Watch','A documentary chronicling the fantasy drama’s eighth and final season. British documentarian Jeanie Finlay was embedded on the series’ set during production of the final six episodes, and the footage she captured during that time delves deep into the mud and blood to reveal the tears and triumphs involved in the challenge of bringing the fantasy world of Westeros to life in the very real studios, fields and car-parks of Northern Ireland.','2019-05-26'),(790,61,56,'Histories & Lore: The Children of the Forest, the First Men, and the Andals','Bran Stark recounts the legends surrounding the mysterious Children of the Forest and their wars against the First Men and the Andals.','2012-03-05'),(791,61,57,'Histories & Lore: The Age of Heroes','Bran Stark recounts the stories of legendary figures of several of the seven independent kingdoms that existed prior to the War of Conquest.','2012-03-05'),(792,61,58,'Histories & Lore: The Old Gods and the New','Catelyn and Bran Stark discuss the worship of the Old Gods of the Forest and the Seven in Westeros.','2012-03-05'),(793,61,59,'Histories & Lore: The History of the Night\'s Watch (Jeor Mormont)','Jeor Mormont discusses the earliest days, structure and duty of the Night\'s Watch.','2012-03-05'),(794,61,60,'Histories & Lore: The History of the Night\'s Watch (Maester Luwin)','Maester Luwin details the steady decline that the Night\'s Watch has suffered with the passage of time.','2012-03-05'),(795,61,61,'Histories & Lore: The History of the Night\'s Watch (Tywin Lannister)','Tywin Lannister mocks the faded glory of the Night\'s Watch and questions the need for the order.','2012-03-05'),(796,61,62,'Histories & Lore: The Order of the Maesters','Maester Luwin explains the role and function of the Order of Maesters in the Seven Kingdoms as well as studies aspiring Maesters undergo.','2012-03-05'),(797,61,63,'Histories & Lore: Valyria and the Dragons','Viserys Targaryen recounts the history of Valyria from its rise to becoming the greatest civilization the world has ever seen to its destruction in the Doom.','2012-03-05'),(798,61,64,'Histories & Lore: The Field of Fire (Viserys Targaryen)','Viserys Targaryen reflects on the victory which secured Aegon I Targaryen\'s domination of the Seven Kingdoms.','2012-03-05'),(799,61,65,'Histories & Lore: The Field of Fire (Robb Stark)','Robb Stark recalls how Aegon the Conqueror forced the lords of Westeros into submission with his brutal victory on the Field of Fire.','2012-03-05'),(800,61,66,'Histories & Lore: Mad King Aerys (Robert Baratheon)','Robert Baratheon reflects on the actions of King Aerys II Targaryen and his son Rhaegar leading to his rebellion.','2012-03-05'),(801,61,67,'Histories & Lore: Mad King Aerys (Maester Luwin)','Maester Luwin looks back on Prince Rhaegar\'s capture of Lyanna Stark and the horrific injustice inflicted on House Stark by the Mad King Aerys.','2012-03-05'),(802,61,68,'Histories & Lore: Mad King Aerys (Tywin Lannister)','Tywin Lannister reminisces on the collapse of his alliance with Aerys as the latter descended further and further into madness.','2012-03-05'),(803,61,69,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Robert Baratheon)','Robert Baratheon reminisces on his glorious victories against the supporters of the Mad King Aerys II Targaryen.','2012-03-05'),(804,61,70,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Viserys Targaryen)','Viserys Targaryen bitterly recalls the treachery of the Usurper Robert Baratheon putting an end to the Targaryen dynasty.','2012-03-05'),(805,61,71,'Histories & Lore: The Sack of King\'s Landing (Viserys Targaryen)','Viserys Targaryen bitterly recounts Tywin Lannister\'s treachery bringing down the Targaryen dynasty.','2012-03-05'),(806,61,72,'Histories & Lore: The Sack of King\'s Landing (Robert Baratheon)','Robert Baratheon reflects on his victory over the Targaryen dynasty and the necessity for the death of Rhaegar Targaryen\'s children.','2012-03-05'),(807,61,73,'Histories & Lore: The Sack of King\'s Landing (Maester Luwin)','Maester Luwin details the downfall of the Mad King and the death of the royal family, as well as how it impacted those who won the war.','2012-03-05'),(808,61,74,'Histories & Lore: The Sack of King\'s Landing (Tywin Lannister)','Tywin Lannister reminisces on the part he played in defeating the Targaryens and the rewards his family reaped for it.','2012-03-05'),(809,61,75,'Histories & Lore: House Stark','Bran and Robb Stark discuss House Stark\'s reign as the Kings of Winter before kneeling to Aegon the Conqueror.','2012-03-05'),(810,61,76,'Histories & Lore: House Lannister','Tywin Lannister recalls how House Lannister survived and rose to prominence through cunning.','2012-03-05'),(811,61,77,'Histories & Lore: House Targaryen','Viserys Targaryen recounts the conquest of House Targaryen and its ruling of the Seven Kingdoms before being brought down by the treacherous Usurper Robert Baratheon.','2012-03-05'),(812,61,78,'Histories & Lore: House Baratheon','Robert Baratheon recalls the victories that led to House Baratheon cementing themselves as one of the greatest houses in Westeros.','2012-03-05'),(813,61,79,'Histories & Lore: House Arryn','Catelyn Stark speaks of the origins of House Arryn and the conquest of the Vale during the Andal Invasion and its role in Robert\'s Rebellion.','2012-03-05'),(814,61,80,'Histories & Lore: The Greyjoy Rebellion (Robb Stark)','Robb Stark reminisces about his father going to war to put an end to Balon Greyjoy\'s rebellion and the impact it had on his family.','2013-02-19'),(815,61,81,'Histories & Lore: The Greyjoy Rebellion (Theon Greyjoy)','Theon Greyjoy reflects on his father\'s failed rebellion and the penalties his family suffered as a result of it.','2013-02-19'),(816,61,82,'Histories & Lore: The Greyjoy Rebellion (Stannis Baratheon)','Stannis Baratheon recounts serving under his brother Robert when Balon Greyjoy rebelled against the Iron Throne, as well as how he would have done things differently had he been king.','2013-02-19'),(817,61,83,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Stannis Baratheon)','Stannis Baratheon reflects on his brother Robert\'s rebellion against the Mad King Aerys II Targaryen and his own part in it, as well as his bitterness for not being justly rewarded.','2013-02-19'),(818,61,84,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Davos Seaworth)','Davos Seaworth recounts his lowly beginnings and days as a smuggler as well as the event that brought him into the service of Stannis Baratheon.','2013-02-19'),(819,61,85,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Margaery Tyrell)','Margaery Tyrell details House Tyrell\'s loyalty to House Targaryen before the rebellion and to House Baratheon afterwards.','2013-02-19'),(820,61,86,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Catelyn Stark)','Catelyn Stark reminisces on the rebellion and how it affected the family she was born into as well as the one she married into.','2013-02-19'),(821,61,87,'Histories & Lore: House Tyrell','Margaery Tyrell details House Tyrell\'s history serving under House Gardener before the War of Conquest and House Targaryen afterwards, before surrendering to Robert Baratheon after he defeated the Targaryen dynasty.','2013-02-19'),(822,61,88,'Histories & Lore: House Greyjoy','Theon and Yara Greyjoy divulge the history of the ironborn and how House Greyjoy became the dominant family of the Iron Islands.','2013-02-19'),(823,61,89,'Histories & Lore: House Clegane','Sandor Clegane recounts House Clegane\'s humble beginnings, as well as how he and his brother Gregor became two of the most infamous killers in Westeros.','2013-02-19'),(824,61,90,'Histories & Lore: The Free Folk','Ygritte discusses the history and culture of the Free Folk in comparison to that of the inhabitants of the Seven Kingdoms.','2013-02-19'),(825,61,91,'Histories & Lore: The Night\'s Watch','Ygritte recites the history of the Night\'s Watch and their oppression of the Free Folk.','2013-02-19'),(826,61,92,'Histories & Lore: Dragonstone','Stannis Baratheon recounts the history of the island Dragonstone, from the landing of the Targaryens to his own unwanted ruling of it.','2013-02-19'),(827,61,93,'Histories & Lore: Harrenhal','Catelyn Stark details the rise and fall of the supposedly impenetrable fortress Harrenhal and the terrifying legends that have plagued its ruins ever since.','2013-02-19'),(828,61,94,'Histories & Lore: The Free Cities','Jorah Mormont explains the rise of the “Free Cities” of Essos in the wake of Valyria’s Doom, detailing how the cities differ and what one can expect to find in each one.','2013-02-19'),(829,61,95,'Histories & Lore: Qarth','Xaro Xhoan Daxos explains Qarth’s role in Essos’ commerce, and how the merchant council known as the Thirteen rules the city to ensure it remains the greatest city that was or ever will be.','2013-02-19'),(830,61,96,'Histories & Lore: The Drowned God','Yara Greyjoy explains the worship of the Drowned God, His importance in the Iron Islands, and the legends of His halls beneath the waves.','2013-02-19'),(831,61,97,'Histories & Lore: The Alchemists\' Guild','Wisdom Hallyne provides an account of the Alchemist Guild (or Pyromancers), detailing their knowledge of wildfire and how their once great influence in Westeros has faded over the years.','2013-02-19'),(832,61,98,'Histories & Lore: The Warlocks','Xaro Xhoan Daxos explains the mysterious order of the warlocks and their relationship with the House of the Undying, their center of power.','2013-02-19'),(833,61,99,'Histories & Lore: Old Ghis & Slaver\'s Bay','Jorah Mormont charts the rise and fall of the Ghiscari Empire, including its battles with the Valyrian Freehold and the slaver cities that carry on in the wake of its destruction.','2014-02-18'),(834,61,100,'Histories & Lore: The Unsullied','Jorah Mormont recounts the legendary Battle of Qohor, in which three thousand Unsullied slave-warriors held off an entire Dothraki horde outside the gates of Qohor.','2014-02-18'),(835,61,101,'Histories & Lore: House Reed','Meera Reed discusses the history and modern perceptions of House Reed, leaders of the crannogmen, the mysterious swamp-dwelling gatekeepers of the North.','2014-02-18'),(836,61,102,'Histories & Lore: House Bolton','Roose Bolton discusses the history of House Bolton, one of the great houses of the North, despite their often unsavory reputation.','2014-02-18'),(837,61,103,'Histories & Lore: House Frey','Catelyn Stark tracks the House Frey’s quick rise to wealth and power through control of the Crossing, as well as their current reputation under the prickly and resentful Lord Walder Frey.','2014-02-18'),(838,61,104,'Histories & Lore: House Tully','Brynden Tully details the history of House Tully, the noble and diplomatic Lords Paramount of the Riverlands.','2014-02-18'),(839,61,105,'Histories & Lore: The Lord of Light','Thoros of Myr details his personal history as a follower of the Lord of Light, from his skeptical youth in Myr, to his visions in the flames that have made him a believer.','2014-02-18'),(840,61,106,'Histories & Lore: Wargs and the Sight','Bran Stark explains the legendary abilities of warging and the Sight, skills that, although innate to the mythical Children of the Forest, only present themselves in modern men on rare occasion.','2014-02-18'),(841,61,107,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Petyr Baelish and Varys)','Petyr Baelish and Varys debate the ramifications of Robert Baratheon’s rebellion against the Mad King Aerys II Targaryen, and its impact on the realm.','2014-02-18'),(842,61,108,'Histories & Lore: The Red Keep','Joffrey Baratheon reveals the history and structure of the Red Keep, the main fortress of King’s Landing, from its construction by the Targaryens, to its hidden lower dungeons.','2014-02-18'),(843,61,109,'Histories & Lore: The North','Jon Snow describes the vast, cold and unforgiving North, which stretches from the Neck to the Wall, and has served as the barrier between the Seven Kingdoms and the horrors beyond the Wall for thousands of years.','2014-02-18'),(844,61,110,'Histories & Lore: The Reach','Margaery Tyrell discusses the history, customs, and noble houses of the Reach, the fertile region known for chivalry, knightly tournaments, farms, and vineyards.','2014-02-18'),(845,61,111,'Histories & Lore: The Riverlands','Brynden Tully recounts the history of the Riverlands, one of the most desirable-and most fought over-regions in the Seven Kingdoms.','2014-02-18'),(846,61,112,'Histories & Lore: The Stormlands','Brienne of Tarth recounts the tumultuous history of the Stormlands, from the constant battles waged by the Storm Kings, to the relative peace under Targaryen rule, to Robert’s Rebellion.','2014-02-18'),(847,61,113,'Histories & Lore: The Westerlands','Tywin Lannister reveals the history of the Westerlands, and the true strength behind the richest region of the Seven Kingdoms; House Lannister.','2014-02-18'),(848,61,114,'Histories & Lore: The Vale','Petyr Baelish delves into the history of the Vale, from its mythical beginnings to the impregnable Eyrie, the noble House Arryn, and the unpredictable Hill Tribes.','2014-02-18'),(849,61,115,'Histories & Lore: House Martell','Oberyn Martell discusses the history and reputation of House Martell, the strong-willed ruling family of Dorne that refused to join the Seven Kingdoms for centuries.','2015-02-17'),(850,61,116,'Histories & Lore: House Baelish','Petyr Baelish explains how, despite humble beginnings, House Baelish has rapidly risen to power, thanks mostly to his own wit and ambition.','2015-02-17'),(851,61,117,'Histories & Lore: Dragons','Grand Maester Pycelle recounts the mysterious origins, magical powers, and inexplicable downfall of history\'s last generation of dragons.','2015-02-17'),(852,61,118,'Histories & Lore: Poisons','Oberyn Martell explains the sources, surreptitious uses, and lethal effects of the many poisons circulating throughout Westeros and Essos.','2015-02-17'),(853,61,119,'Histories & Lore: The Bastards of Westeros','Ellaria Sand explains the shame cast upon bastards throughout much of Westeros, and how these unwanted children can tear families and kingdoms apart.','2015-02-17'),(854,61,120,'Histories & Lore: The Iron Bank of Braavos','Tycho Nestoris reveals the history behind the legendary Iron Bank of Braavos, an institution renowned for its economic power and formidable reputation.','2015-02-17'),(855,61,121,'Histories & Lore: Sellswords & Hedge Knights','Bronn describes the unique profession and skill of the sellsword, as well as the debatable merits of the hedge knight.','2015-02-17'),(856,61,122,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Oberyn Martell)','Oberyn Martell reveals the Dornish perspective of Robert\'s Rebellion - or the War of the Usurper as they call it - including the murder of his sister, Elia Martell, during the sack of King\'s Landing.','2015-02-17'),(857,61,123,'Histories & Lore: The Wall','Samwell Tarly explains the impressive construction and function of the Wall, including its natural defenses against wildling attempts to scale, breach, and circumnavigate it.','2015-02-17'),(858,61,124,'Histories & Lore: The Nations of the North','Tormund Giantsbane describes the varied clans of Free Folk living beyond the Wall, from Thenns to the Hornfoots to the Giants, all of whom Mance Rayder has rallied to his cause.','2015-02-17'),(859,61,125,'Histories & Lore: The Kingsguard (Jaime Lannister)','Jaime Lannister details the heroes and storied triumphs of the Kingsguard believed to be the most honorable knights in the realm.','2015-02-17'),(860,61,126,'Histories & Lore: The Kingsguard (Bronn)','Bronn sheds some light on the unfavorable moments from the Kingsguard\'s history, including their blind loyalty for less-than-honorable kings.','2015-02-17'),(861,61,127,'Histories & Lore: The Maester\'s Chain','Qyburn explains the significance of the Maester\'s Chain, a symbolic ornament earned by students of The Citadel, with each link representing the mastery of a different subject.','2015-02-17'),(862,61,128,'Histories & Lore: The Death of Kings','Varys tracks the lives and all too common deaths of the Kings of Westeros over the years, proving that the Iron Throne is truly an uncomfortable seat to hold.','2015-02-17'),(863,61,129,'Histories & Lore: Valyrian Steel','Jorah Mormont details the mysterious properties of Valyrian Steel, a metal considered magical that was used to forge the blades of the great Houses of Westeros.','2015-02-17'),(864,61,130,'Histories & Lore: Justice of the Seven Kingdoms','Bronn offers his view on the Seven Kingdoms\' questionable methods of justice, including the dramatic trial by combat and the rarely invoked trial by Seven.','2015-02-17'),(865,61,131,'Histories & Lore: The Seven-Pointed Star','The High Sparrow details how \"The Seven-Pointed Star\" has influenced followers of the Faith of the Seven throughout the centuries.','2016-03-15'),(866,61,132,'Histories & Lore: The Faith Militant','The High Sparrow narrates the origins of the Faith Militant, its rebellion against House Targaryen that plunged the realm into war, and its ultimate decline and disbandment.','2016-03-15'),(867,61,133,'Histories & Lore: Volantis','Varys discusses the history of Volantis, the oldest of the Free Cities from its humble beginnings as the first colony of Valyria.','2016-03-15'),(868,61,134,'Histories & Lore: Braavos','Tycho Nestoris explains the history behind the beautiful city of Braavos, from the Titan who inhabits the harbor, to the world-renowned swordsmanship of the city\'s \"bravos.\"','2016-03-15'),(869,61,135,'Histories & Lore: The Faceless Men','Tycho Nestoris discusses the mysterious guild of assassins known as the Faceless Men.','2016-03-15'),(870,61,136,'Histories & Lore: Winterfell','Roose Bolton gives his views on Winterfell and how the House Bolton influenced its creation and expansion before seizing it.','2016-03-15'),(871,61,137,'Histories & Lore: The Lord Commanders','Acting Lord Commander Alliser Thorne talks about the purpose of the Lord Commander of the Night\'s Watch, how he is chosen, and recalls some of the more noteworthy Lord Commanders, who made history through their folly.','2016-03-15'),(872,61,138,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Barristan Selmy)','Barristan Selmy recounts how he was named to the Kingsguard, saw King Aerys descend into madness but revered Prince Rhaegar Targaryen. Barristan describes the fateful Tourney at Harrenhal, the ensuing War of the Five Kings, and how he fought beside Rhaegar at the Battle of the Trident where he was killed.','2016-03-15'),(873,61,139,'Histories & Lore: Dorne','Ellaria Sand narrates a brief history of Dorne from the migration of the First Men to the present day.','2016-03-15'),(874,61,140,'Histories & Lore: The Fighting Pits of Meereen','Daario Naharis describes the history of the fighting pits of Meereen, the different types of fights that occur there, and the lives that the more-skilled fighters lead.','2016-03-15'),(875,61,141,'Histories & Lore: The River Rhoyne','Varys talks about the Rhoyne, the largest river of Essos, and the people who originally inhabited it, the Rhoynar, and the war they fought against the Dragonlords.','2016-03-15'),(876,61,142,'Histories & Lore: The Many-Faced God','A man known as \"Jaqen H\'ghar\" discusses the Many-Faced God, the syncretic god of death worshiped by the cult of assassins known as the Faceless Men.','2016-03-15'),(877,61,143,'Histories & Lore: Greyscale and the Stone Men','Qyburn discusses the dreaded plague known as Greyscale, and its advanced victims known as \"Stone Men\".','2016-03-15'),(878,61,144,'Histories & Lore: The Great Masters of Meereen','Missandei of Naath discusses the self-styled \"Great Masters\", the powerful aristocratic slaver families that rule over Meereen, the largest city in Slaver\'s Bay.','2016-03-15'),(879,61,145,'The Dance of Dragons','The great Targaryen civil war known as the Dance of the Dragons is discussed by Shireen Baratheon, Viserys Targaryen, Oberyn Martell, Robert Baratheon, Catelyn Stark, and Joffrey Baratheon.','2016-03-15'),(880,61,146,'Histories & Lore: The Old Way','Euron Greyjoy remembers the origins of the Old Way of the Ironborn in their days of glory, and how a brutal and bloody leader tried to recover it during the Dance of the Dragons.','2016-11-15'),(881,61,147,'Histories & Lore: The Kingsmoot','Euron Greyjoy discusses the origins of the tradition of the Kingsmoot, and he names the most famous and bloodthirsty kings named under this tradition.','2016-11-15'),(882,61,148,'Histories & Lore: The Summer Sea','Euron Greyjoy outlines the cultures and peoples he has witnessed in his travels and incursions for the Summer Sea.','2016-11-15'),(883,61,149,'Histories & Lore: The War of the Ninepenny Kings','Brother Ray recounts the War of the Ninepenny Kings from the perspective of a peasant who was recruited by his Lord as a soldier, with all the sufferings and tragedies that this meant for his life.','2016-11-15'),(884,61,150,'Histories & Lore: The Great Tourney at Harrenhal','Meera Reed tells the story that her father told her during her childhood about the infamous tournament at Harrenhal, the biggest tournament in Westeros\' history, in which a mysterious knight tested the honor of the great Lords.','2016-11-15'),(885,61,151,'Histories & Lore: Robert\'s Rebellion (Jaime Lannister)','Jaime Lannister looks back on his appointment as a brother of the Kingsguard, with all the secret interests involved, and how it led to his infamous participation in the end of the Robert\'s Rebellion.','2016-11-15'),(886,61,152,'Histories & Lore: Vaes Dothrak','Jorah Mormont explains the structure and places of interest of Vaes Dothrak, the vast capital of Dothraki people, and mentions some of the rituals practiced there by the Dosh khaleen.','2016-11-15'),(887,61,153,'Histories & Lore: The Dothraki','Jorah Mormont details the history of the first major migration of the Dothraki after the Doom of Valyria towards Central Essos, and how the newly invaded invaders destroyed the civilizations of what would later become the Dothraki Sea.','2016-11-15'),(888,61,154,'Histories & Lore: Northern Allegiances to House Stark','Sansa Stark recounts the history of the North, of how it was once unified by the House Stark, of how its principal noble houses swore loyalty to them, and how they guaranteed its independence from the Andals, while she prepares herself from the Wall to confront those who now govern it.','2016-11-15'),(889,61,155,'Histories & Lore: Children of the Forest vs. the First Men','The Three-Eyed Raven recounts the wars between the Children of the Forest and the First Men, and how they led to the conflict now threatening Westeros.','2016-11-15'),(890,61,156,'Histories & Lore: The Brotherhood Without Banners','Thoros of Myr explains the origin that led to the conformation of the Brotherhood Without Banners, and how it assumed the mission of protecting the smallfolk.','2016-11-15'),(891,61,157,'Histories & Lore: Oldtown','Grand Maester Pycelle and Qyburn debate the records and theories about the history of Oldtown, the oldest city of Westeros, the noble house that governs it and the Citadel, the refuge and home of the noble order of the Maesters','2016-11-15'),(892,61,158,'Histories & Lore: House Dayne','The young Eddard Stark recounts the history of House Dayne, the former kings and lords of Starfall, and how they have been linked to their legendary sword Dawn, especially his last and greatest bearer, Arthur Dayne, the Sword of the Morning.','2016-11-15'),(893,61,159,'Histories & Lore: The Little Birds','Varys recounts his own origins, and how he created his network of spies he calls his little birds.','2016-11-15'),(894,61,160,'Histories & Lore: The Knights of the Vale','Petyr Baelish highlights on arrival at the first of the Andals invaders who went on to become the great knights of the Vale of Arryn.','2016-11-15'),(895,61,161,'Histories & Lore: House Tarly','Randyll Tarly reflects on the history of House Tarly, and his own story with his eldest son Samwell.','2016-11-15'),(896,61,162,'Histories & Lore: Riverrun','Brynden Tully details the history of Riverrun, the ancestral castle of the House Tully , and the strengths that have allowed it to resist millennia of wars.','2016-11-15'),(897,61,163,'Histories & Lore: The Great Sept of Baelor','The High Sparrow recounts the history of the Great Sept of Baelor, the largest Sept of the Faith of the Seven, and the pious King who built it, Baelor the Blessed.','2016-11-15'),(898,61,164,'Histories & Lore: The Dragonpit','Varys and Qyburn recall the era when Targaryen dragons were housed in King\'s Landing.','2017-12-12'),(899,61,165,'Histories & Lore: The Citadel','Samwell Tarly tells the history of the Citadel, the center of learning where maesters earn their chains.','2017-12-12'),(900,61,166,'Histories & Lore: Casterly Rock','Jaime Lannister recounts the founding of his ancestral home, Casterly Rock.','2017-12-12'),(901,61,167,'Histories & Lore: Highgarden','Randyll Tarly describes the battles, marriages, and alliances surrounding Highgarden, the seat of House Tyrell.','2017-12-12'),(902,61,168,'Histories & Lore: The Golden Company','Jorah Mormont explains the history of the Golden Company - a band of mercenaries who have built their reputation on never having lost a battle.','2017-12-12'),(903,61,169,'Histories & Lore: Prophecies of the Known World','Samwell Tarly enumerates on the roles prophecies play in Westeros and Essos alike.','2017-12-12'),(904,61,170,'Histories & Lore: The Hand of the King','Petyr Baelish details the successes and failures of past Hands of the King.','2017-12-12'),(905,61,171,'Histories & Lore: The Rains of Castamere','Jaime Lannister provides the gruesome backstory surrounding \"The Rains of Castamere.\"','2017-12-12'),(906,61,172,'Histories & Lore: King\'s Landing','Varys explains the origins and the workings of King\'s Landing.','2019-12-03'),(907,61,173,'Histories & Lore: The Greyjoy Rebellion (Jaime Lannister and Euron Greyjoy)','Jaime Lannister and Euron Greyjoy argue their perspectives of the Greyjoy Rebellion.','2019-12-03'),(908,61,174,'Histories & Lore: The Blackfyres','Varys explains the backstory of House Blackfyre.','2019-12-03'),(909,61,175,'Histories & Lore: The South','Tormund shares the Free Folks\' perspective of Westeros south of The Wall and its inhabitants.','2019-12-03'),(910,61,176,'Histories & Lore: The Defiance of Duskendale','Varys explains the details of the Defiance of Duskendale and how this event forever changed Aerys II Targaryen for the worse.','2019-12-03'),(911,61,177,'Histories & Lore: Maegor the Cruel','Varys recounts the terrifying history of Maegor Targaryen, also known as \"Maegor the Cruel\".','2019-12-03'),(912,61,178,'The Real History Behind Game of Thrones (Part 1)','Watch historians, along with George R. R. Martin, explore the interweaving inspirations of the actual players in the era known as \"The Wars of the Roses\" and other historical events in this two-part series.','2016-03-14'),(913,61,179,'The Real History Behind Game of Thrones (Part 2)','Watch historians, along with George R. R. Martin, explore the interweaving inspirations of the actual players in the era known as \"The Wars of the Roses\" and other historical events in this two-part series.','2016-03-14'),(914,61,180,'Creating the show open','Deep insights into the creation of the opening credits for Game of Thrones, which was awarded the Emmy.','2012-03-05'),(915,61,181,'From the book to the screen','Executive producers David Benioff & D.B. Weiss, as well as author George R.R. Martin talk about the great challenge of bringing Martin\'s epic fantasy books to life on HBO.','2012-03-05'),(916,61,182,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Arya Stark','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(917,61,183,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Bran Stark','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(918,61,184,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Catelyn Stark','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(919,61,185,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Cersei Lannister','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(920,61,186,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Daenerys Targaryen','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(921,61,187,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Jaime Lannister','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(922,61,188,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Jon Snow','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(923,61,189,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Khal Drogo','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(924,61,190,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Ned Stark','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(925,61,191,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Petyr Baelish','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(926,61,192,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Robb Stark','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(927,61,193,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Robert Baratheon','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(928,61,194,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Sansa Stark','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(929,61,195,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Tyrion Lannister','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(930,61,196,'Season 1 Character Profiles: Viserys Targaryen','Character profiles of the 15 main characters in the words of the respective actors.','2012-03-05'),(931,61,197,'The night\'s watch','A detailed look at the special troop of men dedicated to the protection and supervision of the wall, a 200 meter high construction that separates the seven kingdoms from the darkness behind.','2012-03-05'),(932,61,198,'Creating the Dothraki language','A deep look into the artificial language that was invented for the Dothraki people in Game of Thrones.','2012-03-05'),(933,61,199,'Season 2 Character Profiles: Jon Snow','7 new profiles including Renly and Stannis Baratheon, Robb Stark, Theon Greyjoy and others.','2013-02-19'),(934,61,200,'Season 2 Character Profiles: Daenerys Targaryen','7 new profiles including Renly and Stannis Baratheon, Robb Stark, Theon Greyjoy and others.','2013-02-19'),(935,61,201,'Season 2 Character Profiles: Robb Stark','7 new profiles including Renly and Stannis Baratheon, Robb Stark, Theon Greyjoy and others.','2013-02-19'),(936,61,202,'Season 2 Character Profiles: Joffrey Baratheon','7 new profiles including Renly and Stannis Baratheon, Robb Stark, Theon Greyjoy and others.','2013-02-19'),(937,61,203,'Season 2 Character Profiles: Renly Baratheon','7 new profiles including Renly and Stannis Baratheon, Robb Stark, Theon Greyjoy and others.','2013-02-19'),(938,61,204,'Season 2 Character Profiles: Stannis Baratheon','7 new profiles including Renly and Stannis Baratheon, Robb Stark, Theon Greyjoy and others.','2013-02-19'),(939,61,205,'Season 2 Character Profiles: Theon Greyjoy','7 new profiles including Renly and Stannis Baratheon, Robb Stark, Theon Greyjoy and others.','2013-02-19'),(940,61,206,'Creating The Battle Of Blackwater Bay','A deep look behind the scenes with the cast and crew shows how the epic battle in the Blackwater bay was brought to life.','2013-02-19'),(941,61,207,'Game of Thrones: The Inner Circle','Emilia Clarke, Kit Harington, Lena Headey, Michelle Fairley and Liam Cunningham talk in detail about their experiences filming the second season in a discussion led by David Benioff and D.B. Weiss.','2013-02-19'),(942,61,208,'Religions of Westeros','Author George R.R. Martin and the producers David Benioff and D.B. Weiss discuss about the various competing religions in Game of Thrones and how they affect the protagonists not only in Westeros but also further afield.','2013-02-19'),(943,61,209,'New Characters','The new faces from season 3: Olenna Tyrell, Missandei, Manke Rayder, Tormund Giantsbane, Orell, Jojen and Meera Reed, Blackfish and Edmure Tully, Thoros of Myr and Beric Dondarrion.','2014-02-18'),(944,61,210,'A Gathering Storm','A prequel to Game of Thrones Season 3 which recaps on the first and second season and gives insight into what\'s to come.','2014-02-18'),(945,61,211,'The Politics of Marriage','Love and marriage? They don\'t go together so well in \'Game of Thrones\' where the concept of matrimony is all about making power plays and political alliances. Cast and crew members along with author George R.R. Martin take a fascinating look at this ancient institution and its place in the hit HBO series.','2014-02-18'),(946,61,212,'Inside the Wildlings','With this introduction to the Wildlings, take a look into the land beyond the wall to better understand their history and origins.','2014-02-18'),(947,61,213,'Unused / extended scenes from season 3','Five unused and extended scenes.','2014-02-18'),(948,61,214,'The Fallen: A Roundtable','Writer Bryan Cogman sits down with a few main casts who face their deaths in season 4. The 30-minute feature shows what it\'s like to live - or die - in the world of Game of Thrones, from the first announcement of the impending end to the execution of the final scene.','2015-02-17'),(949,61,215,'Behind the battle for the wall','Follow the cast and crew into the most ambitious battle yet. The extensive documentation, including previously unpublished material, curbs the difficulties that arose in creating one of the strongest episodes in the entire series.','2015-02-17'),(950,61,217,'Bastards of Westeros','Series makers David Benioff & D.B. Weiss discuss with author George R.R. Martin on the role of the bastards in the Seven Kingdoms.','2015-02-17'),(951,61,218,'New characters and locations','Explore the new races, cultures and locations in Season 4.','2015-02-17'),(952,61,219,'2 unused scenes from Season 4','','2015-02-17'),(953,61,220,'Bloopers Season 4','','2015-02-17'),(954,61,221,'Anatomy of an episode: Mother\'s Mercy','We experience, how \"Mother\'s Mercy\" came about - an episode that fans will be discussing for years to come: from the script concepts to the final visual effects.','2016-03-15'),(955,61,223,'New characters and locations','Explore the new races, cultures and locations in Season 5.','2016-03-15'),(956,61,226,'4 unused scenes from Season 5','Season 5 Deleted Scenes','2016-03-15'),(957,61,227,'The battle of the bastards: An in-depth look','Here we learn how the greatest battle in Game of Thrones history came about: the story, the stunts used and a comprehensive analysis of the complete visual effects. Since the first season, the series creators have been waiting to translate this battle into pictures.','2016-11-15'),(958,61,228,'Recreating the Dothraki world','Here we learn how the production team brings the Dothraki world of the first season to new life: costumes, dialect trainers and the creation of the world\'s largest pyre. All aspects of the reconstruction of this world are analyzed.','2016-11-15'),(959,61,230,'3 deleted scenes from Season 6','3 deleted scenes from Season 6.','2016-11-15'),(960,61,231,'Anatomy of an Episode: A Golden Crown','A detailed feature about the production of Season 1 episode \"A Golden Crown\", complete with cast and crew interviews, behind-the-scene footage and plenty more.','2012-03-05'),(961,61,232,'Cast Auditions: Harry Lloyd (Viserys Targaryen)','Watch rarely-seen footage of the cast auditioning for Game of Thrones','2012-03-05'),(962,61,233,'Cast Auditions: Rory McCann (Sandor Clegane)','Watch rarely-seen footage of the cast auditioning for Game of Thrones','2012-03-05'),(963,61,234,'Cast Auditions: Jason Momoa (Khal Drogo)','Watch rarely-seen footage of the cast auditioning for Game of Thrones','2012-03-05'),(964,61,235,'Cast Auditions: Sophie Turner (Sansa Stark)','Watch rarely-seen footage of the cast auditioning for Game of Thrones','2012-03-05'),(965,61,236,'Cast Auditions: Maisie Williams (Arya Stark)','Watch rarely-seen footage of the cast auditioning for Game of Thrones','2012-03-05'),(966,61,237,'Cast Auditions: Miltos Yerolemou (Syrio Forel)','Watch rarely-seen footage of the cast auditioning for Game of Thrones','2012-03-05'),(967,61,238,'Deleted Scene: Dorreah and Irri','Deleted scene from Season 2','2013-02-19'),(968,61,239,'Deleted Scene: The Hound and the Little Bird','Deleted scene from Season 2','2013-02-19'),(969,61,240,'Deleted Scene: Varys congratulates Littlefinger','Deleted scene from Season 2','2013-02-19'),(970,61,241,'Deleted Scene: Margaery comforts Loras','Deleted scene from Season 2','2013-02-19'),(971,61,243,'Anatomy of a Scene: Planning a Royal Wedding','Likely on the Season 4 Blu-ray. Part of the Bonus Features on the Disc 1 on UHD sets','2015-02-17'),(972,61,244,'The Rains of Castamere Unveiled','An in-depth look into the third season\'s most crucial, most emotionally taxing and most jaw-dropping episode, \"The Rains of Castamere,\" in all its gory, gutsy glory. Includes cast and crew interviews, behind-the-scenes footage and other materials.','2014-02-18'),(973,61,248,'Blooper Reel 2 (Season 5)','','2013-02-19'),(974,61,249,'Deleted Scenes from Season 8','Alys Karstark (Episode 3), Davos & Fergus (Episode 2), Grey Worm & Missandei at the Feast (Episode 4), Play All (Season 8), Soup in the Trenches (Episode 1), and Tyrion & Sansa in the Crypts (Episode 3).','2019-05-26'),(975,61,250,'Arya\'s Transition','Describes the story of Arya\'s transformation from a little girl of noble blood to a tempered young woman.','2014-02-18'),(976,61,251,'Arya and the Hound','George R.R. Martin talks of the connection between Arya and the Hound.','2014-02-18'),(977,61,252,'Dany\'s Love Triangle','Emilia Clarke (Daenerys Targaryen) and Ian Glen (Jorah Mormont) discuss their complex relationship between their characters.','2014-02-18'),(978,61,253,'The Bedding Ceremony','Author George R.R. Martin and producer D.B. Weiss discuss the bedding ceremony depicted in the series as part of a medieval wedding.','2014-02-18'),(979,61,254,'Marriage in Westeros','Author George R.R. Martin talks about the medieval weddings featured in the series.','2014-02-18'),(980,61,255,'The Free Companies of Essos','Author George R.R. Martin talks about the free companions of Essos.','2014-02-18'),(981,61,256,'History of the Gift','Author George R.R. Martin talks about the history of the Gift of the Night\'s Watch.','2014-02-18'),(982,61,257,'The Ultimate Surprise','Author George R.R. Martin and the cast talk about how they experienced the surprise of the Red Wedding.','2014-02-18'),(983,61,258,'The temptation of Jon Snow','David Benioff, D.B. Weiss, Rose Leslie (Ygritte) and Kit Harington (Jon Show) discuss Ygritte and Jon Snow\'s relationship and his temptations between duty and love.','2014-02-18'),(984,61,259,'One must suffer for art','Rory McCann (Sandor Clegane) and Maisie Williams (Arya Stark) relate a scene in which the hound feasts on a pig\'s foot.','2014-02-18'),(985,61,260,'Guest Right','Author George R.R. Martin, producer David Benioff and Richard Madden (Robb Stark) discuss the medieval guest rights portrayed in the series.','2014-02-18'),(986,61,261,'History of the Nightfort','Author George R.R. Martin tells the history of the nightfort.','2014-02-18'),(987,61,262,'History of Slaver\'s Bay','Author George R.R. Martin tells the history of slaver\'s bay.','2014-02-18'),(988,61,263,'New Sound for \'The rains of Castamere\'','Author George R.R. Martin, producers David Benioff and D.B. Weiss and composer Ramin Djawadi talk about the new sound for the episode \"The rains of Castamere\"','2014-02-18'),(989,61,264,'Roose Bolton\'s motivation','Author George R.R. Martin, producers David Benioff and D.B. Weiss talk about Roose Bolton\'s motivation for betraying the Starks.','2014-02-18'),(990,61,265,'Sam the wizard','Producers David Benioff and D.B. Weiss talk about the character of Samwell Tarly.','2014-02-18'),(991,61,266,'Dany\'s motivation: Freeing the slaves','Producers David Benioff and D.B. Weiss and Emilia Clarke (Daenerys Targaryen) talk about Dany\'s motivations.','2014-02-18'),(992,61,267,'Wildling Raiders','Author George R.R. Martin, producers David Benioff and D.B. Weiss talk about wildling raiders or the free people.','2014-02-18'),(993,61,268,'The Stark state of mind','Author George R.R. Martin tells about the Stark\'s state of mind.','2014-02-18'),(994,61,269,'Fire & Steel: Creating the Invasion of Westeros','Revisit season 7\'s most pivotal moments with this behind-the-scenes featurette, including interviews with key cast and crew breaking down how fans\' favorite moments were created.','2017-12-12'),(995,61,270,'From Imagination to Reality: Inside the Art Department - Part 1','Part 1 of an extensive featurette detailing the astonishing work of Production Designer Deborah Riley and her art department, dissecting the process behind the creation of season 7\'s incredible new sets, including Dragonstone, Casterly Rock, Highgarden, the Dragon Pit, and more.','2017-12-12'),(996,61,271,'From Imagination to Reality: Inside the Art Department - Part 2','Part 2 of an extensive featurette detailing the astonishing work of Production Designer Deborah Riley and her art department, dissecting the process behind the creation of season 7\'s incredible sets, including Winterfell, Euron\'s ship Silence, the loot train and the frozen lake.','2017-12-12'),(997,61,272,'Jon\'s Inner Struggle','The show creators discuss Jon\'s changing sense of mission over time.','2014-02-18'),(998,61,273,'Jon\'s Tragic Flaw','The show creators discuss Jon\'s inability to kill an innocent man.','2014-02-18'),(999,61,274,'VFX: Creating the Twins','The visual effects team discuss how they visually created the Twins.','2014-02-18'),(1000,61,275,'VFX: Creating the Wall','The visual effects team discuss how they visually created the Wall.','2014-02-18'),(1001,61,276,'Red Wedding Option 1: Behind The Scenes','Show creators provide behind-the-scenes insight into the filming of the Red Wedding.','2014-02-18'),(1002,61,277,'Red Wedding Option 2: Interviews','Show creators provide additional insight into the Red Wedding.','2014-02-18'),(1003,61,278,'Red Wedding Option 3: Red Wedding Scene','Standalone clip of the Red Wedding.','2014-02-18'),(1004,61,279,'The Last Season: When Winter Falls','Join Game of Thrones show runners David Benioff and D.B. Weiss, along with many of the major stars and behind-the-scenes players, as they look back at the colossal filming that was the \"Battle of the Winterfell\".','2019-12-03'),(1005,61,280,'The Last Season: Duty is the Death of Love','Look at how the team behind Game of Thrones brought the Emmy-winning series to its conclusion in the series finale, \"The Iron Throne.\"  Interviews include show runners David Benioff and D.B. Weiss, along with all of the major stars, including Kit Harington, Peter Dinklage, Emilia Clarke and more.','2019-12-09'),(1006,61,281,'Anatomy of a Scene: The Massacre At Hardhome','A look at the Season 5 Scene - The Massacre At Hardhome.\n\nOn the UHD Box Set Bonus Disc 1','2020-11-03'),(1007,61,282,'Anatomy of a Scene: Inside the Fight for Meereen','A behind the scenes look at the making of Season 6 Scene - Inside the Fight for Meereen\n\nOn the UHD Box Set Bonus Disc 1','2020-11-03'),(1008,61,283,'Anatomy of a Scene: Ice, Fire and Dragons: Creating the Frozen Lake','A behind the scenes look at the making of Season 7 Scene - Ice, Fire and Dragons: Creating the Frozen Lake\n\nOn the UHD Box Set Bonus Disc 1','2020-11-03'),(1009,61,284,'Behind the Scenes: Houses of the Seven Kingdoms','Behind-the-scenes look at filming the season 1 \"Houses of the Seven Kingdoms\"\n\nUHD Box Set Bonus Disc 2','2020-11-03'),(1010,61,285,'Behind the Scenes: Westeros At War with George R.R. Martin','A Discussion on Season 2 with George R.R. Martin','2020-11-09'),(1011,61,286,'Behind the Scenes: Silk, Leather & Chain Mail','A Look at the Costumes of Season 4','2020-11-09'),(1012,61,287,'Behind the Scenes: The Final Step','Discussing the Season 5 post-production','2020-11-09'),(1013,61,288,'Creating the Visual Effects: Season 1','Creating the Visual Effects: Season 1','2020-11-10'),(1014,61,289,'Creating the Visual Effects: Season 2','Creating the Visual Effects: Season 2','2020-11-16'),(1015,61,290,'Creating the Visual Effects: Season 3','Creating the Visual Effects: Season 3','2020-11-17'),(1016,61,291,'Creating the Visual Effects: Season 4 (Shock and Awe)','Creating the Visual Effects for Season 4','2020-11-17'),(1017,61,292,'Creating the Visual Effects: Season 5','Creating the Visual Effects: Season 5','2020-11-23'),(1018,61,293,'Creating the Visual Effects: Season 6','Creating the Visual Effects: Season 6','2020-11-24'),(1019,61,294,'Creating the Visual Effects: Season 7','Creating the Visual Effects: Season 7','2020-11-30'),(1020,61,295,'Game of Thrones: The Last Watch','','2019-05-26'),(1021,61,296,'Extended Scene (Season 7): Sam & Gilly','An extended Scene between Sam and Gilly','2020-11-05'),(1022,61,297,'Deleted Scene (Season 7): Varys & Trella in King\'s Landing','Deleted Scene between Varys & Trella in King\'s Landing','2020-11-05'),(1023,61,298,'Deleted Scene (Season 7): Daenaerys & Tyrion corridor talk','A deleted scene between Daenerys and Tyrion','2020-11-05'),(1024,61,299,'Hidden Dragon Egg - Harry Lloyd Audition','','2020-11-10'),(1025,61,300,'Hidden Dragon Egg - Jason Momoa Audition','','2020-11-10'),(1026,61,301,'Hidden Dragon Egg - Maisie Williams Audition','','2020-11-10'),(1027,61,302,'Hidden Dragon Egg - Miltos Yerolemou Audition','','2020-11-10'),(1028,61,303,'Hidden Dragon Egg - Roy McCann Audition','','2020-11-10'),(1029,61,304,'Hidden Dragon Egg - Sophie Turner Audition','','2020-11-10'),(1030,61,305,'2015 Comic Con Panel','','2020-11-16'),(1031,61,306,'How the Storm was Born','Behind-the-scenes featurette about the making of Game of Thrones Season 8, specifically focusing on the penultimate episode  and the destruction of King\'s Landing.','2019-07-24'),(1032,61,307,'From Renderings to Reality: The Visual Effects of Season 8','Insights and techniques from the visual effects team on creating the show\'s final season effects, offering an in-depth look at the process behind the complex visuals.','2019-07-30'),(1033,62,1,'Winter Is Coming','Jon Arryn, the Hand of the King, is dead. King Robert Baratheon plans to ask his oldest friend, Eddard Stark, to take Jon\'s place. Across the sea, Viserys Targaryen plans to wed his sister to a nomadic warlord in exchange for an army.','2011-04-17'),(1034,62,2,'The Kingsroad','While Bran recovers from his fall, Ned takes only his daughters to Kings Landing. Jon Snow goes with his uncle Benjen to The Wall. Tyrion joins them.','2011-04-24'),(1035,62,3,'Lord Snow','Lord Stark and his daughters arrive at King\'s Landing to discover the intrigues of the king\'s realm.','2011-05-01'),(1036,62,4,'Cripples, Bastards, and Broken Things','Eddard investigates Jon Arryn\'s murder. Jon befriends Samwell Tarly, a coward who has come to join the Night\'s Watch.','2011-05-08'),(1037,62,5,'The Wolf and the Lion','Catelyn has captured Tyrion and plans to bring him to her sister, Lysa Arryn, at The Vale, to be tried for his, supposed, crimes against Bran. Robert plans to have Daenerys killed, but Eddard refuses to be a part of it and quits.','2011-05-15'),(1038,62,6,'A Golden Crown','While recovering from his battle with Jamie, Eddard is forced to run the kingdom while Robert goes hunting. Tyrion demands a trial by combat for his freedom. Viserys is losing his patience with Drogo.','2011-05-22'),(1039,62,7,'You Win or You Die','Robert has been injured while hunting and is dying. Jon and the others finally take their vows to the Night\'s Watch. A man, sent by Robert, is captured for trying to poison Daenerys. Furious, Drogo vows to attack the Seven Kingdoms.','2011-05-29'),(1040,62,8,'The Pointy End','Eddard and his men are betrayed and captured by the Lannisters. When word reaches Robb, he plans to go to war to rescue them. The White Walkers attack The Wall. Tyrion returns to his father with some new friends.','2011-06-05'),(1041,62,9,'Baelor','Robb goes to war against the Lannisters. Jon finds himself struggling on deciding if his place is with Robb or the Night\'s Watch. Drogo has fallen ill from a fresh battle wound. Daenerys is desperate to save him.','2011-06-12'),(1042,62,10,'Fire and Blood','With Ned dead, Robb vows to get revenge on the Lannisters. Jon must officially decide if his place is with Robb or the Night\'s Watch. Daenerys says her final goodbye to Drogo.','2011-06-19'),(1043,63,1,'The North Remembers','As Robb Stark and his northern army continue the war against the Lannisters, Tyrion arrives in King’s Landing to counsel Joffrey and temper the young king’s excesses.  On the island of Dragonstone, Stannis Baratheon plots an invasion to claim his late brother’s throne, allying himself with the fiery Melisandre, a strange priestess of a stranger god.  Across the sea, Daenerys, her three young dragons, and the khalasar trek through the Red Waste in search of allies, or water.  In the North, Bran presides over a threadbare Winterfell, while beyond the Wall, Jon Snow and the Night’s Watch must shelter with a devious wildling.','2012-04-01'),(1044,63,2,'The Night Lands','In the wake of a bloody purge in the capital, Tyrion chastens Cersei for alienating the king’s subjects.  On the road north, Arya shares a secret with Gendry, a Night’s Watch recruit.  With supplies dwindling, one of Dany’s scouts returns with news of their position.  After nine years as a Stark ward, Theon Greyjoy reunites with his father Balon, who wants to restore the ancient Kingdom of the Iron Islands.  Davos enlists Salladhor Saan, a pirate, to join forces with Stannis and Melisandre for a naval invasion of King’s Landing.','2012-04-08'),(1045,63,3,'What is Dead May Never Die','At the Red Keep, Tyrion plots three alliances through the promise of marriage.  Catelyn arrives in the Stormlands to forge an alliance of her own, but King Renly, his new wife Margaery, and her brother Loras Tyrell have other plans.  At Winterfell, Luwin tries to decipher Bran’s dreams.','2012-04-15'),(1046,63,4,'Garden of Bones','Joffrey punishes Sansa for Robb’s victories, and Tyrion scrambles to temper the king’s cruelty. Catelyn entreats Stannis and Renly to unite against the Lannisters. Dany and her khalasar arrive at the prosperous city of Qarth. Tyrion coerces a relative into being his eyes and ears. Arya and Gendry are taken to Harrenhal, where their lives are in the hands of Ser Gregor Clegane. Stannis orders Davos to smuggle Melisandre into a secret cove.','2012-04-22'),(1047,63,5,'The Ghost of Harrenhal','The Baratheon rivalry ends, driving Catelyn to flee and Littlefinger to act. At King’s Landing, Tyrion’s source alerts him to Joffrey’s defense plan - and a mysterious secret weapon. Theon sails to the Stony Shore to prove he’s worthy to be called Ironborn. At Harrenhal, Arya receives a promise from Jaqen H’ghar, one of the prisoners she saved from the Gold Cloaks. The Night’s Watch arrive at the Fist of the First Men, an ancient ringfort where they hope to stem the wildings\' advance.','2012-04-29'),(1048,63,6,'The Old Gods and the New','Theon seizes control of Winterfell. Jon captures a wildling, named Ygritte and is given a chance to prove himself. At King\'s Landing, after the Lannisters send Myrcella off to be married, the people begin to turn against King Joffrey. Arya comes face to face with a surprise visitor. Daenerys looks to buy ships to sail for the Seven Kingdoms.','2012-05-06'),(1049,63,7,'A Man Without Honor','Jamie meets a distant relative. Daenerys receives an invitation to the House of the Undying. Theon leads a search party. Jon loses his way in the wilderness. Cersei counsels Sansa.','2012-05-13'),(1050,63,8,'The Prince of Winterfell','Betrayal befalls Robb. Jon and Qhorin are taken prisoner by the wildlings. Theon receives a visitor at Winterfell and must make an important decision. Meanwhile, Stannis is just days away from reaching King\'s Landing and Tyrion prepares for his arrival. At Harrenhal, Arya, Gendry and Hot Pie plan their escape.','2012-05-20'),(1051,63,9,'Blackwater','Tyrion and the Lannisters fight for their lives as Stannis’ fleet assaults King’s Landing.','2012-05-27'),(1052,63,10,'Valar Morghulis','Tyrion awakens to a changed situation. King Joffrey doles out rewards to his subjects. As Theon stirs his men to action, Luwin offers some final advice. Brienne silences Jaime. Arya receives a gift from Jaqen. Dany goes to a strange place. Jon proves himself to Qhorin.','2012-06-03'),(1053,64,1,'Valar Dohaeris','Jon meets the King-Beyond-the-Wall while his Night Watch Brothers flee south. In King\'s Landing, Tyrion wants a reward, Margaery shows her charitable nature, Cersei arranges a dinner party, and Littlefinger offers to help Sansa. Across the Narrow Sea, Daenerys starts her journey west.','2013-03-31'),(1054,64,2,'Dark Wings, Dark Words','Sansa says too much. Shae asks Tyrion for a favor. Jaime finds a way to pass the time, while Arya encounters the Brotherhood Without Banners.','2013-04-07'),(1055,64,3,'Walk of Punishment','Tyrion shoulders new responsibilities. Jon is taken to the Fist of the First Men. Daenerys meets with the slavers. Jaime strikes a deal with his captors.','2013-04-14'),(1056,64,4,'And Now His Watch Is Ended','Trouble brews among the Night\'s Watch at Craster\'s. Margaery takes Joffrey out of his comfort zone. Arya meets the leader of the Brotherhood. Varys plots revenge on an old foe. Theon mournfully recalls his missteps. Daenerys deftly orchestrates her exit from Astapor.','2013-04-21'),(1057,64,5,'Kissed by Fire','The Hound is judged by the gods. Jaime is judged by men. Jon proves himself. Robb is betrayed. Tyrion learns the cost of weddings.','2013-04-28'),(1058,64,6,'The Climb','Tywin plans strategic unions for the Lannisters. Melisandre pays a visit to the Riverlands. Robb weighs a compromise to repair his alliance with House Frey. Roose Bolton decides what to do with Jaime Lannister. Jon, Ygritte, and the Wildlings face a daunting climb.','2013-05-05'),(1059,64,7,'The Bear and the Maiden Fair','Daenerys exchanges gifts with a slave lord outside of Yunkai. As Sansa frets about her prospects, Shae chafes at Tyrion’s new situation. Tywin counsels the king, and Melisandre reveals a secret to Gendry. Brienne faces a formidable foe in Harrenhal.','2013-05-12'),(1060,64,8,'Second Sons','King’s Landing hosts a wedding, and Tyrion and Sansa spend the night together. Daenerys tries to persuade the Second Sons to join her against Yunkai. Stannis releases Davos from the dungeons. Sam and Gilly meet an older gentleman.','2013-05-19'),(1061,64,9,'The Rains of Castamere','The Lannisters send their regards.','2013-06-02'),(1062,64,10,'Mhysa','Bran and company travel beyond the Wall. Sam returns to Castle Black. Jon says goodbye to Ygritte. Jaime returns to King\'s Landing. The Night\'s Watch asks for help from Stannis. Daenerys waits to see if she is a conqueror or a liberator.','2013-06-09'),(1063,65,1,'Two Swords','Tyrion welcomes a guest to King’s Landing. At Castle Black, Jon Snow finds himself unwelcome. Dany is pointed to Meereen, the mother of all slave cities. Arya runs into an old friend.','2014-04-06'),(1064,65,2,'The Lion and the Rose','Tyrion lends Jaime a hand. Joffrey and Margaery host a breakfast. At Dragonstone, Stannis loses patience with Davos. Ramsay finds a purpose for his pet. North of the Wall, Bran sees where they must go.','2014-04-13'),(1065,65,3,'Breaker of Chains','Tyrion ponders his options. Tywin extends an olive branch. Sam realizes Castle Black isn’t safe, and Jon proposes a bold plan. The Hound teaches Arya the way things are. Dany chooses her champion.','2014-04-20'),(1066,65,4,'Oathkeeper','Dany balances justice and mercy. Jaime tasks Brienne with his honor. Jon secures volunteers while Bran, Jojen, Meera and Hodor stumble on shelter.','2014-04-27'),(1067,65,5,'First of His Name','After Tommen is crowned the King of the Seven Kingdoms, Cersei and Tywin plan the Crown\'s next move. Meanwhile, Dany weighs her future plans regarding Westeros and Slaver\'s Bay. Sansa and Lord Baelish arrive at the Eyrie and Jon Snow along with men from the Night\'s Watch attacks Craster\'s Keep.','2014-05-04'),(1068,65,6,'The Laws of Gods and Men','Stannis makes a deal with the Iron Bank of Braavos. Yara and her troops storm the Dreadfort to free Theon. Meanwhile, Daenerys meets Hizdar zo Loraq and her other supplicants. And the day of Tyrion\'s trial has come where Tyrion faces his father.','2014-05-11'),(1069,65,7,'Mockingbird','Tyrion gains an unlikely ally; Daario asks Dany to allow him to do what he does best; Jon\'s warnings about the vulnerability of the Wall are ignored; Brienne follows a new lead. ','2014-05-18'),(1070,65,8,'The Mountain and the Viper','Unexpected visitors arrive in Mole\'s Town. With assistance from Theon, Ramsay proves himself to his father, Lord Bolton. Littlefinger\'s motives are questioned when Sansa reveals the fate of Lysa Arryn to other lords of the Vale. Daenerys finds out a secret about Jorah Mormont. Tyrion\'s fate is decided.','2014-06-01'),(1071,65,9,'The Watchers on the Wall','Night gathers, and now my watch begins.','2014-06-08'),(1072,65,10,'The Children','Circumstances change after an unexpected arrival from north of the Wall. Dany must face harsh realities. Bran learns more about his destiny. Tyrion sees the truth about his situation.','2014-06-15'),(1073,66,1,'The Wars to Come','Cersei and Jaime adjust to a world without Tywin. Varys reveals a conspiracy to Tyrion. Dany faces a new threat to her rule. Jon is caught between two kings.','2015-04-12'),(1074,66,2,'The House of Black and White','Arya arrives in Braavos. Podrick and Brienne run into trouble on the road. Cersei fears for her daughter\'s safety in Dorne as Ellaria Sand seeks revenge for Oberyn\'s death. Stannis tempts Jon. An adviser tempts Daenerys.','2015-04-19'),(1075,66,3,'High Sparrow','In Braavos, Arya sees the Many-Faced God. In King\'s Landing, Queen Margaery enjoys her new husband. Tyrion and Varys walk the Long Bridge of Volantis.','2015-04-26'),(1076,66,4,'Sons of the Harpy','The Faith Militant grow increasingly aggressive. Jaime and Bronn head south. Ellaria and the Sand Snakes vow vengeance.','2015-05-03'),(1077,66,5,'Kill the Boy','Dany makes a difficult decision in Meereen. Jon recruits the help of an unexpected ally. Brienne searches for Sansa. Theon remains under Ramsay\'s control.','2015-05-10'),(1078,66,6,'Unbowed, Unbent, Unbroken','Arya trains. Jorah and Tyrion run into slavers. Trystane and Myrcella make plans. Jaime and Bronn reach their destination. The Sand Snakes attack.','2015-05-17'),(1079,66,7,'The Gift','Jon prepares for conflict. Sansa tries to talk to Theon. Brienne waits for a sign. Stannis remains stubborn. Jaime attempts to reconnect with family.','2015-05-24'),(1080,66,8,'Hardhome','Arya makes progress in her training. Sansa confronts an old friend. Cersei struggles. Jon travels.','2015-05-31'),(1081,66,9,'The Dance of Dragons','Stannis confronts a troubling decision. Jon returns to The Wall. Mace visits the Iron Bank. Arya encounters someone from her past. Dany reluctantly oversees a traditional celebration of athleticism.','2015-06-07'),(1082,66,10,'Mother\'s Mercy','Stannis marches. Dany is surrounded by strangers. Cersei seeks forgiveness. Jon is challenged.','2015-06-14'),(1083,67,1,'The Red Woman','The fate of Jon Snow is revealed. Daenerys meets a strong man. Cersei sees her daughter once again.','2016-04-24'),(1084,67,2,'Home','Bran trains with the Three-Eyed Raven. In King’s Landing, Jaime advises Tommen. Tyrion demands good news, but has to make his own. At Castle Black, the Night’s Watch stands behind Thorne. Ramsay Bolton proposes a plan, and Balon Greyjoy entertains other proposals.','2016-05-01'),(1085,67,3,'Oathbreaker','Daenerys meets her future. Bran meets the past. Tommen confronts the High Sparrow. Arya trains to be No One. Varys finds an answer. Ramsay gets a gift.','2016-05-08'),(1086,67,4,'Book of the Stranger','Tyrion strikes a deal. Jorah and Daario undertake a difficult task. Jaime and Cersei try to improve their situation.','2016-05-15'),(1087,67,5,'The Door','Tyrion seeks a strange ally. Bran learns a great deal. Brienne goes on a mission. Arya is given a chance to prove herself.','2016-05-22'),(1088,67,6,'Blood of My Blood','An old foe co