ion','Tokyo\'s happiness turns bittersweet. Angel closes in on a quarreling Raquel and the Professor. Authorities offer a multimillion-dollar reward for tips.','2019-07-19'),(1162,74,8,'Astray','Tokyo attempts to drown her sorrows. Sierra uses personal tactics to target a vulnerable Nairobi, while Suarez continues to hunt down Raquel.','2019-07-19'),(1163,74,9,'Game Over','Anger and grief heighten tensions between the group. The Professor, while in mourning, attempts to make a daring and dangerous escape.','2020-04-03'),(1164,74,10,'Berlin\'s Wedding','Palermo shocks the group with his actions. Sierra pressures her subject to take a deal. The Professor remembers his brother\'s wedding.','2020-04-03'),(1165,74,11,'Anatomy Lesson','The Professor\'s mole attempts to pass along his message to the person inside the tent. Denver\'s jealousy toward Mónica and Rio\'s friendship heightens.','2020-04-03'),(1166,74,12,'Pasodoble','In the past, Berlin predicts that Gandía will cause problems for the operation. Sierra\'s interrogation of Lisboa leads to a personal revelation.','2020-04-03'),(1167,74,13,'5 Minutes Earlier','Denver turns to an undercover source for help. Nairobi attempts to motivate her team as the danger around them intensifies.','2020-04-03'),(1168,74,14,'TKO','With Nairobi held hostage, Gandía negotiates with the crew. The Professor desperately seeks a new plan to save his team.','2020-04-03'),(1169,74,15,'Strike the Tent','The group reels following the attack on one of their own. The Professor puts his adjusted plan in motion with the help of new recruits and Palermo.','2020-04-03'),(1170,74,16,'The Paris Plan','The Professor, Benjamin and the others attempt to free Lisboa. Tokyo\'s anger threatens her faith in the plan. Sierra takes matters into her own hands.','2020-04-03'),(1171,75,1,'The End of the Road','The Professor faces off with Sierra as Tamayo raises the stakes of the negotiations by calling the army. In the past, Berlin meets with a family member.'