urvivor in the medical facility as Paul\'s health deteriorates.','2013-10-01'),(2464,163,34,'The Oath: Bond','Karina and Paul are forced to make life and death choices.','2013-10-01'),(2465,163,35,'Inside the Walking Dead','Footage from the show; elements of production of \"The Walking Dead\"; bringing the series together.','2014-07-08'),(2466,163,36,'Inside The Walking Dead: Walker University','Greg Nicotero takes viewers on a behind-the-scenes look at the process of creating the shows \'walkers\'. Featuring interviews with actors, costume designers and special effects people at The Walking Dead\'s own Zombie School.','2014-07-15'),(2467,163,37,'A Look at Season 6','A look back at season 6.','2016-07-24'),(2468,163,38,'The Journey So Far','In this special episode the producers and cast of the show reflect on the events and characters throughout the first six seasons.','2016-10-16'),(2469,163,39,'Behind The Dead (100 Episodes Special)','Andrew Lincoln, Norman Reedus, and the rest of the cast and crew reflect on the history and celebrate reaching the 100th episode of The Walking Dead.','2017-10-19'),(2470,163,40,'Walker World','Greg Nicotero and KNB EFX Group bring their zombies to life and interview the cast and crew, including Andrew Lincoln and Norman Reedus.','2017-10-20'),(2471,163,41,'The Journey So Far (2017)','The cast and producers of The Walking Dead recount the epic journey that the characters have experienced through the first seven seasons of the show.','2017-10-21'),(2472,163,42,'The Walking Dead: Retrospective','An emotional look back celebrating the 99 episode journey that lead to Season 8.','2017-09-16'),(2473,163,43,'Season 9 Preview Special','Khary Payton, Tom Payne and Angela Kang discuss the upcoming ninth season of The Walking Dead. Hosted by Yvette Nicole Brown.','2018-08-06'),(2474,163,44,'Wrapping Up Season 8','','2018-09-30'),(2475,163,45,'The Walking Dead Holiday Special','Hosted by Chris Hardwick, the hour-long program will feature current and past cast members from The Walking Dead joining via video chat to talk about the holiday season and look back on a decade of the franchise series – from behind-the-scenes stories on set to what fans can look forward to next.','2020-12-13'),(2476,163,46,'The Walking Dead: Making the Extended 10th Season','In light of Covid-19, TWD Season 10 was extended. Crew and cast show planning, filming, and producing the 6 episodes. These stories bridge the epic final 11th TWD season and the making of them is almost as extraordinary as the show itself.','2021-02-14'),(2477,163,47,'The Walking Dead Extended Season 10 Preview Special','Talking Dead\'s Chris Hardwick hosts the one-hour virtual Walking Dead Extended Season 10 Preview Special, featuring Seth Gilliam (Father Gabriel), Paola Lázaro (Princess/Juanita Sanchez), TWD Universe Twitch host Clarke Wolfe, and executive producer and showrunner Angela Kang.','2021-02-21'),(2478,163,48,'The Making of The Walking Dead','','2010-10-11'),(2479,163,49,'The Making of the Final Season','','2022-11-13'),(2480,163,50,'Inside the Walking Dead: On Set with Andrew Lincoln','A day on set from the filming of Season 1 with Andrew Lincoln.','2010-10-31'),(2481,163,51,'Inside the Walking Dead: Inside Dale\'s RV','A look at the Dale RV set from Season 1 of The Walking Dead.','2010-11-01'),(2482,163,52,'Inside the Walking Dead: On Set with Robert Kirkman','A day on set from Season 1 with Robert Kirkman.','2010-11-02'),(2483,163,53,'Inside the Walking Dead: Bicycle Girl','Filming the first zombie encounter of the entire series from Season 1.','2010-11-07'),(2484,163,54,'Inside the Walking Dead: On Set with Steven Yeun','A day on set from Season 1 with Steven Yeun.','2010-11-08'),(2485,163,55,'Inside The Walking Dead: Zombie Make-Up Tips for Halloween','A Season 1 guide to replicating some of the show\'s zombie effects in practical ways.','2010-11-09'),(2486,163,56,'Inside The Walking Dead: Zombie School','A look at the instruction extras go through to learn how to be zombies for Season 4.','2013-05-08'),(2487,163,57,'Inside The Walking Dead: Comic-Con Panel Highlights','Clips from the San Diego Comic-Con The Walking Dead Panel from Season 1.','2011-06-05'),(2488,163,58,'All the Guts Inside','A behind the scenes look at the effects involved in a zombie autopsy scene from Season 2/','2011-11-16'),(2489,163,59,'Live or Let Die','How the show\'s writers decide which characters live or die that sometimes contrasts with the comic book in Season 2.','2011-11-21'),(2490,163,60,'Fire on Set','A big set piece of Season 2 goes up in flames for a pivotal part of the story.','2011-11-22'),(2491,163,61,'In the Dead Water','Filming a memorable well scene in Season 2 of The Walking Dead.','2011-11-27'),(2492,163,62,'She Will Fight','A look at Andrea\'s character in Season 2 of The Walking Dead.','2011-11-28'),(2493,163,63,'The Ink is Alive','A look at key moments from The Walking Dead comics brought to life in Season 2.','2011-11-29'),(2494,163,64,'The Meat of the Music','A look at the music composition of The Walking Dead in Season 2.','2011-12-04'),(2495,163,65,'The Sound of the Effects','Looking at the work of the Foley Artists behind the audio effects of The Walking Dead from Season 2.','2011-12-05'),(2496,163,66,'The Walking Dead Cast on Season 2','The cast of The Walking Dead  discuss their favorite moments and big set pieces of Season 2.','2011-12-06'),(2497,163,67,'Wardrobe of The Walking Dead','A look at the costume design from The Walking Dead\'s Season 2.','2011-12-11'),(2498,163,68,'You Could Make a Killing','The practical effects of creating kills and realistic viscera for The Walking Dead\'s Season 2.','2011-12-12'),(2499,163,69,'Greg Nicotero on Season 2\'s Zombie Effects','Greg Nicotero discusses the make-up and practical effects of zombies in Season 2.','2011-12-13'),(2500,163,70,'Rising Son','A look at Carl Grimes coming of age in a world full of zombies from Season 3.','2012-12-18'),(2501,163,71,'Evil Eye','A look at the Governor character of The Walking Dead from Season 3.','2012-12-23'),(2502,163,72,'Gone, but Not Forgotten','A look back at the character of Lori Grimes from Season 3.','2012-12-24'),(2503,163,73,'Heart of a Warrior','Michonne\'s evolution in Season 3.','2012-12-25'),(2504,163,74,'Michonne vs The Governor','Behind the scenes of a Michonne and Governor fight sequence in Season 3.','2012-12-30'),(2505,163,75,'Safety Behind Bars','A look at Season 3\'s prison set.','2012-12-31'),(2506,163,76,'Making the Dead','A look at make-up and effects for Season 3 zombies.','2013-01-01'),(2507,163,77,'Guts and Glory','A look at the character deaths of the first three seasons of The Walking Dead.','2013-01-06'),(2508,163,78,'Red Machete','The series starts all the way back to the beginning, when the red-handled machete was just one item on the shelf of a hardware store as the zombie apocalypse began. A young man pulled the machete off the shelf and used it to defend himself from a walker. Unfortunately for him, he didn\'t actually know how to kill a walker and ran the blade through his assailant\'s stomach rather than striking at the monster\'s head.','2017-10-22'),(2509,163,79,'Daryl\'s Story','','2021-07-16'),(2510,163,80,'Maggie\'s Story','','2021-07-23'),(2511,163,81,'Negan\'s Story','','2021-07-30'),(2512,163,82,'Carol\'s Story','','2021-08-06'),(2513,164,1,'Days Gone Bye','Rick searches for his family after emerging from a coma into a world terrorized by the walking dead. Morgan and Duane, whom he meets along the way, help teach Rick the new rules for survival.','2010-10-31'),(2514,164,2,'Guts','Rick unknowingly causes a group of survivors to be trapped by walkers. The group dynamic devolves from accusations to violence, as Rick must confront an enemy far more dangerous than the undead.','2010-11-07'),(2515,164,3,'Tell It to the Frogs','Rick makes a decision to go back to Atlanta to retrieve the bag of guns and save a man\'s life. Lori and Shane must deal with the surprising return of someone they thought was dead.','2010-11-14'),(2516,164,4,'Vatos','Rick\'s mission to Atlanta is jeopardized when things go awry. Jim becomes unhinged in camp.','2010-11-21'),(2517,164,5,'Wildfire','Rick leads the group to the CDC after the attack. Jim must make a terrible life and death decision.','2010-11-28'),(2518,164,6,'TS-19','Rick and the group are allowed into the CDC by a strange doctor, but all is not what it seems in their newfound haven.','2010-12-05'),(2519,165,1,'What Lies Ahead','Rick leads the group out of Atlanta. On the highway, they are stopped by a threat unlike anything they have seen before. The group searches for someone who has gone missing.','2011-10-16'),(2520,165,2,'Bloodletting','Coming to the aid of another, Rick discovers a possible safe haven. Shane must go on a dangerous mission to get badly-needed medical supplies.','2011-10-23'),(2521,165,3,'Save the Last One','The group desperately awaits Shane\'s return. Shane finds himself trapped in a school, surrounded by the undead. Daryl and Andrea search for someone in the woods.','2011-10-30'),(2522,165,4,'Cherokee Rose','Shane makes a deadly sacrifice which leads to unusual behavior and self-distancing. The rest of the group tries to hang on somewhere between living to die and dying to live.','2011-11-06'),(2523,165,5,'Chupacabra','Glenn, the only one breaking barriers between both groups, knows far too much for his comfort level. Daryl finds a sign of life and, in his delirium, tries to make it back to the farm alive.','2011-11-13'),(2524,165,6,'Secrets','Secrets are told and secrets are revealed. Hershel refuses to acknowledge the world’s new reality. Andrea comes out of her shell. Everyone is becoming more and more aware that “everything is food for something.”','2011-11-20'),(2525,165,7,'Pretty Much Dead Already','Hershel sets a deadline. All secrets are out in the open. Glenn stands up for himself and Shane takes charge.','2011-11-27'),(2526,165,8,'Nebraska','Rick and the others try to restore order in the aftermath of a terrible discovery. Hershel takes up an old habit and disappears, Rick and Glenn must follow him into town.','2012-02-12'),(2527,165,9,'Triggerfinger','Trapped, Rick, Hershel and Glenn fight to survive against new foes, both dead and alive. Shane finds Lori in danger on the road and makes it his mission to bring her back to the farm.','2012-02-19'),(2528,165,10,'18 Miles Out','Rick and Shane are in conflict over the fate of an outsider; Andrea helps Hershel\'s daughter face a crucial decision.','2012-02-26'),(2529,165,11,'Judge, Jury, Executioner','Rick sides with Shane on an important decision, causing Dale to worry that the group is losing its humanity. Carl\'s actions have unintended consequences on the group.','2012-03-04'),(2530,165,12,'Better Angels','The group learns that someone dangerous may be on the loose near the farm. As night falls, Rick, Shane, Daryl, and Glenn comb the woods to handle the situation and keep the group safe.','2012-03-11'),(2531,165,13,'Beside the Dying Fire','Rick and Carl return from the woods to find the farm in jeopardy. The group is split up in the ensuing chaos. With things looking grim, Rick\'s leadership is questioned.','2012-03-18'),(2532,166,1,'Seed','With the world growing increasingly more dangerous and Lori’s pregnancy advancing, Rick discovers a potentially safe haven. But first he must secure the premises, pushing his group to its limit.','2012-10-14'),(2533,166,2,'Sick','After a traumatic event, a life hangs in the balance. Complicating matters, the group must also deal with a potential threat to their new surroundings.','2012-10-21'),(2534,166,3,'Walk with Me','After witnessing an accident, Andrea and Michonne are introduced to a new community of survivors. As conflicts arise with their new acquaintances, a decision must be made.','2012-10-28'),(2535,166,4,'Killer Within','The group is severed and lives are put in jeopardy. In Woodbury, Merle has a request for the Governor.','2012-11-04'),(2536,166,5,'Say the Word','After another loss, Rick struggles. Michonne remains suspicious of the Governor as he throws a party with a unique twist for the people of Woodbury.','2012-11-11'),(2537,166,6,'Hounded','As Andrea grows closer to the Governor, Michonne makes a decision about Woodbury. Glenn and Maggie go on a run. Rick struggles.','2012-11-18'),(2538,166,7,'When the Dead Come Knocking','The Governor presses for information. A new guest arrives at the prison, forcing Rick\'s hand.','2012-11-25'),(2539,166,8,'Made to Suffer','Andrea steps up as the people of Woodbury are thrown into uncharted territory. At the prison, a new threat arises.','2012-12-02'),(2540,166,9,'The Suicide King','Rick tries to rescue a member of his group. Woodbury is in disarray after a recent attack. New guests raise concerns at the prison.','2013-02-10'),(2541,166,10,'Home','As the group debates their next course of action, Rick wanders after a lost friend. Daryl and Merle question their choices. The Governor restores order in Woodbury and makes plans to punish those responsible.','2013-02-17'),(2542,166,11,'I Ain\'t a Judas','Rick and the group must make a choice when security is threatened. With Woodbury in a police state, Andrea grows uneasy.','2013-02-24'),(2543,166,12,'Clear','Realizing they are heavily outgunned against the Governor\'s forces, Rick leads an expedition to get more weapons.','2013-03-03'),(2544,166,13,'Arrow on the Doorpost','In an effort to prevent any more deaths, Rick and the Governor meet to come up with a peace treaty.','2013-03-10'),(2545,166,14,'Prey','The Governor chases a dissenter who fled Woodbury. While the Governor is gone, a traitor tries to sabotage his upcoming plans.','2013-03-17'),(2546,166,15,'This Sorrowful Life','Rick and the group are faced with a serious problem. If they want a truce with the Governor, they will have to make a huge sacrifice.','2013-03-24'),(2547,166,16,'Welcome to the Tombs','Rick and the group have to seriously consider if the prison is worth defending as the Governor\'s impending attack looms over their heads.','2013-03-31'),(2548,167,1,'30 Days Without an Accident','Rick and the group are as close to an ideal life as possible at the prison. Will they be able to hold on to humanity in the face of a new evil?','2013-10-13'),(2549,167,2,'Infected','As the group faces a brand new enemy, Rick and the others must fight to protect the livelihood they worked so hard to create at the prison.','2013-10-20'),(2550,167,3,'Isolation','As one group leaves the prison in search for supplies at a local college, those who stay must deal with recent losses while preserving what remains.','2013-10-27'),(2551,167,4,'Indifference','While on a supplies mission to a local college, members of the group run into multiple hurdles. Things at the prison are getting worse.','2013-11-03'),(2552,167,5,'Internment','Multiple enemies put pressure on Rick and the group. Could this finally be the breaking point for the survivors and the prison?','2013-11-10'),(2553,167,6,'Live Bait','A familiar face returns as each member of the group struggles to find his or her humanity in a world of constant threats.','2013-11-17'),(2554,167,7,'Dead Weight','A new and scary chapter is unfolding at a camp outside the prison. Will peace be attainable with the addition of new members?','2013-11-24'),(2555,167,8,'Too Far Gone','Just when everything started to calm down at the prison, Rick and his group now face imminent danger and destruction. This time, they might not win.','2013-12-01'),(2556,167,9,'After','As Rick deals with old wounds, members of the prison have to come to terms with their new environment and ask themselves if survival alone is enough.','2014-02-09'),(2557,167,10,'Inmates','The group encounters many obstacles in their quest to find stability and safety, but sometimes all they have to guide them is hope.','2014-02-16'),(2558,167,11,'Claimed','Just when Rick thinks he\'s going to be able to relax, he\'s faced with multiple immediate threats. Other members of the group deal with their past.','2014-02-23'),(2559,167,12,'Still','Faced with the day-to-day survival of life outside shelter, a simple request by someone in the group leads to a bizarre but enlightening mission.','2014-03-02'),(2560,167,13,'Alone','As one group finds what may be an ideal shelter, another group comes to realize that the best protection comes from those around them.','2014-03-09'),(2561,167,14,'The Grove','After finding an idyllic place to establish a new shelter, the group starts to question whether it is possible to go back to the way things were.','2014-03-16'),(2562,167,15,'Us','However brutal some survivors believe they must be to stay alive, we get to see that faith can sometimes be the strongest survival tool.','2014-03-23'),(2563,167,16,'A','As multiple paths collide, Rick comes face to face with sheer brutality. Will he and the group have what it takes to survive?','2014-03-30'),(2564,168,1,'No Sanctuary','We learn the true motives of the Terminans as Rick and the group find themselves in a vulnerable situation. Will they be able to work together?','2014-10-12'),(2565,168,2,'Strangers','With supplies running low and not knowing whether to trust the people around them, Rick leads a mission where the risk might not be worth the reward.','2014-10-19'),(2566,168,3,'Four Walls and a Roof','Rick and the group find themselves pitted against some very nasty people, but our group might just have a plan to gain the upper hand.','2014-10-26'),(2567,168,4,'Slabtown','Beth gets to meet a whole group of other survivors, but what looks safe and nice on the outside has a bit of a dark side.','2014-11-02'),(2568,168,5,'Self Help','A new set of issues confront our group while on a mission. Will they be able to push through and survive these challenges? Or better yet, each other?','2014-11-09'),(2569,168,6,'Consumed','Cautiously, members of our group must venture into a familiar location on a heroic rescue mission. It\'s a huge stage, but so are the stakes.','2014-11-16'),(2570,168,7,'Crossed','Between holding down the church and going on a rescue mission, our group is spread pretty thin. Is this going to be the breaking point?','2014-11-23'),(2571,168,8,'Coda','Rules and morals have been tossed aside by new enemies. Rick will try to find a peaceful agreement, but they might prefer violence.','2014-11-30'),(2572,168,9,'What Happened and What\'s Going On','After all the recent trials the group has faced, a slight detour might prove to be the solution they\'ve been looking for.','2015-02-08'),(2573,168,10,'Them','Life on the road has left the group beaten and beleaguered. Will they be able to trudge along? Are they even the same people they once were?','2015-02-15'),(2574,168,11,'The Distance','Lasting through a spectacular storm, Rick and the group meet a seemingly friendly person. Can they be trusted or are they just manipulating Rick?','2015-02-22'),(2575,168,12,'Remember','Adjusting into a new lifestyle is proving difficult for the group. Has life on the road proven too treacherous to go back to who they once were?','2015-03-01'),(2576,168,13,'Forget','Rick and the group continue to acclimate to their new surroundings. Will they be able to go back to normalcy? Then again, what is normal now?','2015-03-08'),(2577,168,14,'Spend','While trying to secure their new home, Rick and his group face many challenges, some life threatening. Is this really the utopia it seems to be?','2015-03-15'),(2578,168,15,'Try','The group realizes that sheltered life might not be possible as life within the walls starts to mimic life outside. Will these setbacks break Rick?','2015-03-22'),(2579,168,16,'Conquer','Daryl experiences trouble on a run, while Rick and his group continue to feel like outsiders in Alexandria, where trouble is creeping into the gates.','2015-03-29'),(2580,169,1,'First Time Again','Rick and the group are still having trouble assimilating into Alexandria. Will a new threat bring them closer together or drive them further apart?','2015-10-11'),(2581,169,2,'JSS','Just when it looks like things can return to normal, or as normal as things can be in the apocalypse, a new problem arises for the Alexandrians.','2015-10-18'),(2582,169,3,'Thank You','A return home doesn\'t go as expected.','2015-10-25'),(2583,169,4,'Here\'s Not Here','A new face and setting are introduced. With all that\'s gone on in the apocalypse, can people be trusted?','2015-11-01'),(2584,169,5,'Now','Trouble is inside and outside the gate.','2015-11-08'),(2585,169,6,'Always Accountable','Daryl, Abraham and Sasha encounter many obstacles and a new threat while trying to return to Alexandria.','2015-11-15'),(2586,169,7,'Heads Up','Things in Alexandria are quiet, briefly.','2015-11-22'),(2587,169,8,'Start to Finish','Multiple problems crash together.','2015-11-29'),(2588,169,9,'No Way Out','While trying to escape Alexandria, Rick and his group meet trouble when sudden noise draws walkers towards them with what could be fatal consequences.','2016-02-14'),(2589,169,10,'The Next World','A simple scavenging run proves to be more tricky, when the survivors are not the only ones after a goldmine of supplies.','2016-02-21'),(2590,169,11,'Knots Untie','After Rick comes to the realization that Alexandria might not be as safe as he thought, decisions must be made about where to go from here.','2016-02-28'),(2591,169,12,'Not Tomorrow Yet','Rick and the group realize the only way to maintain the peace of Alexandria is to fight a new enemy. This time, though, our group might be outmatched.','2016-03-06'),(2592,169,13,'The Same Boat','With no hope of safety in Alexandria, Rick and his band of survivors soon discover a larger world with new dangers and new opportunities.','2016-03-13'),(2593,169,14,'Twice as Far','Two separate groups leave Alexandria for supplies, and while both worry over the future of the community, they will face immediate danger.','2016-03-20'),(2594,169,15,'East','When someone goes missing in Alexandria, the community goes on alert, and search parties venture out.','2016-03-27'),(2595,169,16,'Last Day on Earth','To save one of their own, Rick\'s group must venture outside the walls; their experience changes their lives forever.','2016-04-03'),(2596,170,1,'The Day Will Come When You Won\'t Be','Rick and his group kneel helplessly before Negan and the Saviors. What Negan does will haunt those who survive forever.','2016-10-23'),(2597,170,2,'The Well','For a number of familiar faces, a new, well-established community seems too good to be true.','2016-10-30'),(2598,170,3,'The Cell','A new group of survivors seem to have it all in their impressive community, however, there is a price.','2016-11-06'),(2599,170,4,'Service','Alexandria gets a sobering visit.','2016-11-13'),(2600,170,5,'Go Getters','Saddled with grief and surrounded by enemies, members of the group try to find safety at the Hilltop before it\'s too late.','2016-11-20'),(2601,170,6,'Swear','Someone stumbles upon a brand new society unlike anything seen before.','2016-11-27'),(2602,170,7,'Sing Me a Song','A deeper look at the Sanctuary and the world of the Saviors. Members of Alexandria look for supplies.','2016-12-04'),(2603,170,8,'Hearts Still Beating','Negan\'s unwelcome visit to Alexandria continues as other members scavenge for supplies and things quickly spin out of control.','2016-12-11'),(2604,170,9,'Rock in the Road','Rick and the group are led to a new community where they are introduced to its inhabitants and ruler. A familiar face resurfaces.','2017-02-12'),(2605,170,10,'New Best Friends','While searching for a missing Alexandrian, Rick and his group encounter a mysterious collective, its inhabitants unlike any they have come across.','2017-02-19'),(2606,170,11,'Hostiles and Calamities','An Alexandrian discovers that he must navigate the mysterious, confusing and horrifying world within the Saviors\' Sanctuary.','2017-02-26'),(2607,170,12,'Say Yes','The group scavenges for supplies; back in Alexandria, someone must make a morally challenging decision.','2017-03-05'),(2608,170,13,'Bury Me Here','Things do not go as planned when a group of Kingdommers deliver goods to the Saviors during a routine supply drop-off.','2017-03-12'),(2609,170,14,'The Other Side','The Saviors visit the Hilltop unexpectedly, surprising everyone, with plans of taking more than supplies.','2017-03-19'),(2610,170,15,'Something They Need','A group of Alexandrians embarks on a journey to the distant community; one member of the group must make a heartbreaking decision.','2017-03-26'),(2611,170,16,'The First Day of the Rest of Your Life','The stakes continue to grow higher as paths cross; the group enacts an intricate plan.','2017-04-02'),(2612,171,1,'Mercy','Rick and his group, along with the Kingdom and Hilltop, have banded together to bring the fight to Negan and the Saviors.','2017-10-22'),(2613,171,2,'The Damned','The plan involving Alexandrians, Kingdommers and Hilltoppers unfolds. As Rick continues to fight, he encounters a familiar face.','2017-10-29'),(2614,171,3,'Monsters','Conflict with the Saviors leads to unintended consequences for the Hilltop, the Kingdom, and Alexandria; morality proves tricky in wartime.','2017-11-05'),(2615,171,4,'Some Guy','A new weapon in the Savior arsenal proves to be a giant hurdle as fighting continues between Rick\'s forces and those of the Saviors.','2017-11-12'),(2616,171,5,'The Big Scary U','With war raging all around him, we get a close look at Negan and the lives of the Saviors during the conflict through a familiar set of eyes.','2017-11-19'),(2617,171,6,'The King, the Widow, and Rick','With things looking up for Rick and the group, an argument breaks out at the Hilltop; the consequences of the decision are life versus death.','2017-11-26'),(2618,171,7,'Time for After','Negan has to enlist the help of his lieutenants in solving a huge issue facing the Sanctuary; Rick and the group continue to enact the plan.','2017-12-03'),(2619,171,8,'How It\'s Gotta Be','Every story and battle comes crashing together.','2017-12-10'),(2620,171,9,'Honor','Rick faces new difficulties after a battle. Meanwhile, the fight continues in other communities as core members face hard decisions.','2018-02-25'),(2621,171,10,'The Lost and the Plunderers','Groups unite their forces and converge on the Hilltop. Meanwhile, Aaron and Enid search for allies. Simon takes matters into his own hands.','2018-03-04'),(2622,171,11,'Dead or Alive Or','Daryl finds himself in bad company as his group heads to the Hilltop; Maggie makes difficult decisions at the Hilltop; Gabriel\'s faith becomes tested.','2018-03-11'),(2623,171,12,'The Key','Hilltop\'s leadership faces a difficult dilemma after the arrival of unexpected visitors. Rick comes face to face with an adversary.','2018-03-18'),(2624,171,13,'Do Not Send Us Astray','Trouble arises when unexpected visitors arrive at the Hilltop and the community is thrust into action; heartbreaking discoveries are made.','2018-03-25'),(2625,171,14,'Still Gotta Mean Something','A Heaps prisoner makes a discovery; Carol searches for someone in the nearby forest; Rick and Morgan find themselves in the company of strangers.','2018-04-01'),(2626,171,15,'Worth','With the threat of the Saviors still looming, Aaron continues searching for allies. Daryl and Rosita take action and confront an old friend.','2018-04-08'),(2627,171,16,'Wrath','The communities join forces in the last stand against the Saviors as all-out war unfolds.','2018-04-15'),(2628,172,1,'A New Beginning','Rick and his group make a risky run into Washington, D.C. to search for artifacts they will need to build the civilization he and Carl envisioned.','2018-10-07'),(2629,172,2,'The Bridge','The communities join forces to restore a bridge that will facilitate communication and trade. Someone is gravely injured at the construction site.','2018-10-14'),(2630,172,3,'Warning Signs','Rick\'s vision for the future is threatened by a mysterious disappearance that divides the work camp where the communities are building a bridge.','2018-10-21'),(2631,172,4,'The Obliged','Rick\'s vision of a civilized future is threatened by a sudden reckoning with past sins that remain unavenged and unforgiven.','2018-10-28'),(2632,172,5,'What Comes After','Rick is forced to face the past as he struggles to maintain the safety of the communities and protect the future he and Carl envisioned.','2018-11-04'),(2633,172,6,'Who Are You Now?','The Survivors encounter unfamiliar faces outside the safety of their community\'s walls and must decide whether or not this new group can be trusted.','2018-11-11'),(2634,172,7,'Stradivarius','Carol seeks out an old friend living alone in a wilderness teeming with walkers; survivors make the perilous trek to a new home.','2018-11-18'),(2635,172,8,'Evolution','A small rescue mission braves a dangerous herd in their hunt for a missing comrade, only to discover a surprising threat that could doom them all.','2018-11-25'),(2636,172,9,'Adaptation','The group unmasks a disturbing and dangerous new threat. An escaped captive revisits his past.','2019-02-10'),(2637,172,10,'Omega','A captive or a refugee? A new arrival at the Hilltop opens up about the leader of a group of mask-wearing savages. A search party sets out on a daring mission to find two missing friends.','2019-02-17'),(2638,172,11,'Bounty','The savage group led by Alpha confronts the Hilltop in a harrowing attempt to retrieve her daughter; a supply run for the Kingdom turns into a dangerous quest.','2019-02-24'),(2639,172,12,'Guardians','While one community struggles to ease tensions that threaten to divide from within, the true nature of another group comes into focus; a mission to rescue a friend has deadly consequences.','2019-03-03'),(2640,172,13,'Chokepoint','Daryl\'s daring rescue mission forces Alpha to unleash a group of her own to retrieve what belongs to her, even if the price is paid in blood; the Kingdom\'s plans to reunite the communities are put in jeopardy.','2019-03-10'),(2641,172,14,'Scars','An outsider\'s arrival forces Alexandria to rehash devastating old wounds; eye-opening secrets from the past are revealed.','2019-03-17'),(2642,172,15,'The Calm Before','The fair at the Kingdom is underway, with all four communities coming together in celebration for the first time in years, while some pacts are renewed, other deals will come at a much steeper price.','2019-03-24'),(2643,172,16,'The Storm','In the aftermath of an overwhelming loss, the communities must brave a ferocious blizzard; as one group deals with an enemy from within, another is forced to make a life or death decision.','2019-03-31'),(2644,173,1,'Lines We Cross','We pick back up with the group in Oceanside continuing to train in case the Whisperers return. Tensions are high as our heroes struggle to hold onto their concept of civilization.','2019-10-06'),(2645,173,2,'We Are the End of the World','A flashback reveals the origins of Alpha and Beta. Alpha attempts to toughen up Lydia as they prepare to walk with the dead. Meanwhile, the Whisperers create their herds.','2019-10-13'),(2646,173,3,'Ghosts','The threat of the Whisperers return leads to paranoia sweeping over Alexandria; in the meantime, Carol battles with the need for revenge.','2019-10-20'),(2647,173,4,'Silence the Whisperers','Still paranoid Alexandrians get riled up over the Whisperers and take their fear out on Negan; back at Hilltop, the group deals with an unexpected safety issue.','2019-10-27'),(2648,173,5,'What It Always Is','Supplies go missing from Hilltop, Negan is idolized by an Alexandrian, and Ezekiel holds a secret.','2019-11-03'),(2649,173,6,'Bonds','Carol and Daryl go on a mission together while Siddiq struggles to solve a mystery.','2019-11-10'),(2650,173,7,'Open Your Eyes','Carol pushes boundaries that make Daryl uncomfortable. Alpha and Beta have reservations about someone.','2019-11-17'),(2651,173,8,'The World Before','A fight causes tensions in Oceanside while the Alexandrians set out on a high-stakes mission.','2019-11-24'),(2652,173,9,'Squeeze','Our group must figure out how to get out of a precarious situation.','2020-02-23'),(2653,173,10,'Stalker','Our group must defend Alexandria from a threatening outside force.','2020-03-01'),(2654,173,11,'Morning Star','The Whisperers are coming for Hilltop. After Daryl and Lydia\'s encounter with Alpha, the communities must decide whether to run or fight. Meanwhile, Eugene\'s communication with Stephanie gets complicated.','2020-03-08'),(2655,173,12,'Walk with Us','Alpha and the Whisperers attack Hilltop, with Negan\'s help.','2020-03-15'),(2656,173,13,'What We Become','Michonne takes Virgil back to his mysterious island to reunite with his family; in exchange, Virgil promises weapons that could change the tide of the Whisperer War.','2020-03-22'),(2657,173,14,'Look at the Flowers','Heroes and villains reckon with the aftermath of the Hilltop fire; Eugene takes a group on a journey to meet Stephanie, with the hopes of befriending another civilisation.','2020-03-29'),(2658,173,15,'The Tower','The communities prepare for the final battle of the Whisperers\' War. Meanwhile, Eugene\'s group encounters Princess.','2020-04-05'),(2659,173,16,'A Certain Doom','The final battle against Beta and his allies is at its peak. Aaron and Alden find themselves in a predicament.','2020-10-04'),(2660,173,17,'Home Sweet Home','Maggie has returned with a story she is not ready to share, even when her past catches up to her. Negan’s safety is at stake again. Daryl and Maggie fight an unseen and unknown threat.','2021-02-28'),(2661,173,18,'Find Me','An adventure for Daryl and Carol turns sideways when they come across an old cabin. It takes Daryl back to the years when he left the group after Rick disappeared as he relives a time that only the apocalypse could manifest.','2021-03-07'),(2662,173,19,'One More','Gabriel and Aaron search for food and supplies to bring back to Alexandria. Small tragedies lead to bigger tragedies as faith is broken and optimism is fragmented when they are put to the ultimate test.','2021-03-14'),(2663,173,20,'Splinter','Eugene, Ezekiel, Yumiko and Princess are captured and separated. Princess struggles with memories of her traumatic past and tries to escape one way or another with the help of Ezekiel.','2021-03-21'),(2664,173,21,'Diverged','Daryl and Carol come to a fork in the road and head their separate ways. Each going into their own type of survival mode, the easiest of challenges become much harder. Will their individual journeys be the tipping point needed to mend their friendship, or is the distance between them permanent?','2021-03-28'),(2665,173,22,'Here\'s Negan','Carol takes Negan on a journey, hoping to minimize the increasing tension. Negan reflects on the events that led him to this point and comes to a conclusion about his future.','2021-04-04'),(2666,174,1,'Acheron (1)','Daryl leads a mission team to scavenge the military base he discovered. Maggie tells her story, prompting a new mission for survival that only Negan can lead. Eugene and his group go through assessment by the Commonwealth\'s paramilitary police.','2021-08-22'),(2667,174,2,'Acheron (2)','Maggie\'s mission takes the team through a subway tunnel, challenged by lurking walkers and a recalcitrant Negan. With Eugene\'s group, Yumiko seeks answers about her brother and demands expedited processing into the Commonwealth.','2021-08-29'),(2668,174,3,'Hunted','Maggie\'s mission team gets separated and hunted by the Reapers. Carol, Rosita, Magna, and Kelly attempt to catch horses for Alexandria. Judith, R.J., Hershel, and Gracie cope with their parents going away.','2021-09-05'),(2669,174,4,'Rendition','Daryl and Dog get captured by the Reapers. Taken to the Meridian, they reconnect with a familiar figure from their past.','2021-09-12'),(2670,174,5,'Out of the Ashes','Aaron, Carol, Lydia, and Jerry go to the Hilltop ruins for blacksmith tools and nearby game; Eugene\'s group goes through orientation at the Commonwealth; Maggie and Negan trudge through the woods; Judith and the kids clash with teenagers.','2021-09-19'),(2671,174,6,'On the Inside','Escaping from walkers, Connie and Virgil hide in a house occupied by mysterious creatures. Pope tests Daryl\'s loyalty to the Reapers with a conflicting mission. Kelly leaves Alexandria in search of Connie.','2021-09-26'),(2672,174,7,'Promises Broken','Maggie and Elijah learn a new survival tactic from Negan. Eugene\'s group clears walkers to pay their fines. Yumiko interviews for an upper-class job. Daryl learns more about Leah and the Reapers. Gabriel encounters a man of God.','2021-10-03'),(2673,174,8,'For Blood','The Reapers defend Meridian from an incoming herd. Pope suspects Maggie is behind the attack, while Daryl treads carefully. Alexandrians scramble to protect themselves when a violent storm leaves them vulnerable to walkers.','2021-10-10'),(2674,174,9,'No Other Way','Daryl, Maggie, Gabriel, Negan, and Elijah battle the Reapers for food. Aaron and the Alexandrians must survive a storm.','2022-02-20'),(2675,174,10,'New Haunts','The heroes experience Halloween in the Commonwealth; Daryl and Rosita undergo military training led by Mercer; Carol investigates Ezekiel\'s medical condition.','2022-02-27'),(2676,174,11,'Rogue Element','Eugene looks for Stephanie after she mysteriously goes missing. Connie investigates a story on Trooper Davis. Carol helps Hornsby with a labor dispute at a drug farm.','2022-03-06'),(2677,174,12,'The Lucky Ones','Aaron and Maggie meet Governor Pamela Milton as she tours Alexandria, Oceanside and Hilltop. Ezekiel finds himself lucky during a routine checkup. Eugene processes Max\'s story.','2022-03-13'),(2678,174,13,'Warlords','Maggie, Lydia, and Elijah help a stranger from another community called Riverbend. They run into Aaron, who tells them about a mission he embarked on with Gabriel as emissaries for the Commonwealth.','2022-03-20'),(2679,174,14,'The Rotten Core','Maggie, Lydia, and Elijah help Aaron and Gabriel on a rescue mission. In the chaos, Negan finds himself watching over Hershel. Sebastian coerces Daryl and Rosita into pulling a heist.','2022-03-27'),(2680,174,15,'Trust','Hornsby marches Daryl and troops to confront Maggie at Hilltop. After a harrowing heist, Rosita gets Connie, Kelly, Eugene, and Max to investigate the Miltons. Ezekiel helps hospital patients in need.','2022-04-03'),(2681,174,16,'Acts of God','Maggie prepares to defend Hilltop and the people of Riverbend against Hornsby. Meanwhile, Hornsby hires Leah to kill her.','2022-04-10'),(2682,174,17,'Lockdown','Daryl and Negan rush to the Commonwealth to stop Hornsby from going after their families. Pamela deals with protestors demanding justice for Sebastian\'s crimes. Mercer needs Rosita\'s help to fight a swarm.','2022-10-02'),(2683,174,18,'A New Deal','Carol makes a deal with Pamela to wipe the slate clean on behalf of her friends. Aaron, Jerry, Lydia, and Elijah get on the road to Oceanside to fill them in on a plan. The Commonwealth celebrates Founders Day.','2022-10-09'),(2684,174,19,'Variant','Eugene goes on the run after the Founders Day incident. Pamela tasks Mercer to investigate his whereabouts, to Max and Princess\' dismay. Meanwhile, Aaron, Jerry, Lydia, and Elijah encounter an unusual complication at an abandoned Renaissance Faire.','2022-10-16'),(2685,174,20,'What\'s Been Lost','Daryl and Carol investigate the whereabouts of their friends after Pamela disappeared them from the Commonwealth. Unfortunately, their only lead is Hornsby. Meanwhile, Pamela asks Yumiko to prosecute Eugene on behalf of the Commonwealth.','2022-10-23'),(2686,174,21,'Outpost 22','Separated from their children, Maggie, Gabriel, and Rosita track a military convoy to a mysterious destination. Ezekiel, Kelly, Negan, and Annie find themselves at a work site. Daryl and Carol follow a train that has taken Connie aboard.','2022-10-30'),(2687,174,22,'Faith','Ezekiel and Negan team up to lead a clandestine labor revolt against the Warden. Aaron, Jerry, Lydia, and Elijah catch up with Luke and Jules fleeing Oceanside. Eugene stands trial with Yumiko as his defense attorney.','2022-11-06'),(2688,174,23,'Family','The Alexandrians and the prisoners head back to the Commonwealth to confront Pamela Milton. A swarm approaches the city.','2022-11-13'),(2689,174,24,'Rest in Peace','Daryl and Carol rush Judith to the hospital. Rosita, Eugene, and Gabriel search for Coco. Maggie and Negan take arms against Pamela. As the citizens of the Commonwealth deal with the herd, our heroes assemble for one last stand to save their future.','2022-11-20'),(2690,175,1,'1:23:45','April 26, 1986, Ukrainian SSR. Plant workers and firefighters put their lives on the line to control a catastrophic 1986 explosion at a Soviet nuclear power plant.','2019-05-06'),(2691,175,2,'Please Remain Calm','With untold millions at risk after the Chernobyl explosion, nuclear physicist Ulana Khomyuk makes a desperate attempt to reach Valery Legasov, a leading Soviet nuclear physicist, and warn him about the threat of second explosion that could devastate the continent.','2019-05-13'),(2692,175,3,'Open Wide, O Earth','Lyudmilla Ignatenko, a Pripyat resident, ignores warning about her firefighter husband\'s contamination. Valery Legasov lays out a decontamination plan, complete with human risks.','2019-05-20'),(2693,175,4,'The Happiness of All Mankind','Valery Legasov and Soviet Deputy Prime Minister Boris Shcherbina consider using lunar rovers to remove radioactive debris, while Ulana Khomyuk faces government hurdles in determining the truth about the cause of the explosion.','2019-05-27'),(2694,175,5,'Vichnaya Pamyat','Valery Legasov, Boris Shcherbina and Ulana Khomyuk risk their lives and reputations to expose the truth about Chernobyl.','2019-06-03'),(2695,176,1,'Six Minute Preview','','2013-08-11'),(2696,176,2,'Detective Skills with Hitchcock and Scully: Preparing for the Stakeout','Detectives Hitchcock and Scully give an inside look on how to prepare for a stakeout.','2015-08-30'),(2697,176,3,'Detective Skills with Hitchcock and Scully: How to Stay Awake During a Stakeout','Detectives Hitchcock and Scully demonstrate how they stay awake during stakeouts.','2015-09-06'),(2698,176,4,'Detective Skills with Hitchcock and Scully: Processing the Perp','Detectives Hitchcock and Scully breakdown the steps of the booking process.','2015-09-14'),(2699,176,5,'A Very Terry Christmas - Terry Crews\' Yule Log','Terry Crews relieves holiday stress by painting an original work of art in his living room, while soaking up the warmth of a Yule log.','2018-12-14'),(2700,176,6,'Comic-Con Panel 2019','The cast and the creators of the ever popular \"Brooklyn Nine-Nine\" took to San Diego Comic-Con to discuss the series and Season 7. The panel featured Luke Del Tredici (Executive Producer), Dan Goor (Executive Producer & Creator), and series stars Andy Samberg, Melissa Fumero, Terry Crews, Joe Lo Truglio, Dirk Blocker, and Joel McKinnon Miller.','2019-07-22'),(2701,176,7,'Nine-Nine Day: The Ultimate Fan Event','An epic 99-minute fan event featuring exclusive cast interviews and brand-new content like \"Every Slo-Mo Walk,\" \"Every Heist\" and much, much more!','2021-09-09'),(2702,176,8,'Get Your Cop On','','2021-08-12'),(2703,176,9,'The Squad','','2021-08-12'),(2704,177,1,'Pilot','When tightly wound Capt. Holt takes over the precinct, carefree Det. Jake Peralta and his dysfunctional coworkers\' lives get demanding.','2013-09-17'),(2705,177,2,'The Tagger','Jake is assigned a lowly graffiti case as punishment for being late to roll call.','2013-09-24'),(2706,177,3,'The Slump','Jake\'s unsolved cases pile up and the other detectives fear that his losing streak will rub off on them, while Amy must run an at-risk youth program.','2013-10-01'),(2707,177,4,'M.E. Time','The team turns on Jake for delaying an autopsy report by flirting with an attractive medical examiner, who turns out to be more than he bargained for.','2013-10-08'),(2708,177,5,'The Vulture','A Major Crimes detective known as \"The Vulture\" takes over Jake\'s nearly solved case and steals his thunder, prompting revenge.','2013-10-15'),(2709,177,6,'Halloween','Halloween-hating Amy is anything but festive when she has to don a costume and hit the streets with Charles on busy Halloween night.','2013-10-22'),(2710,177,7,'48 Hours','After making an arrest with too little proof, Jake has 48 hours to get evidence or the perp will go free, forcing the team to work over the weekend.','2013-11-05'),(2711,177,8,'Old School','Jake\'s dream day with his hero, a former crime reporter, turns nightmarish when his comments about Holt and the precinct go \"on the record.\"','2013-11-12'),(2712,177,9,'Sal\'s Pizza','When Jake\'s favorite pizzeria is burned down and the fire marshal suspects the owner, Jake steps outside his jurisdiction to catch the real arsonist.','2013-11-19'),(2713,177,10,'Thanksgiving','Amy hosts Thanksgiving dinner for the precinct in an effort to get Holt to be her mentor, but Holt and Jake leave early and the rest hate her cooking.','2013-11-26'),(2714,177,11,'Christmas','When Capt. Holt receives death threats, Jake is placed on his protective detail and revels in the chance to boss his boss around.','2013-12-03'),(2715,177,12,'Pontiac Bandit','Jake and Rosa hunt an infamous car thief, Holt tries to find a home for puppies and the rest of the precinct tries to accommodate a wounded Charles.','2014-01-07'),(2716,177,13,'The Bet','After Jake and Amy\'s bet about who can make more arrests is finally settled, the two go on a stakeout where Jake reevaluates their relationship.','2014-01-14'),(2717,177,14,'The Ebony Falcon','On his first task back in the field, Terry takes advice from Jake on controlling his emotions to infiltrate and bust a steroid trafficking ring.','2014-01-21'),(2718,177,15,'Operation: Broken Feather','While investigating a string of hotel robberies together, Jake discovers that Amy may transfer to the Major Crimes unit and work with \"The Vulture.\"','2014-02-02'),(2719,177,16,'The Party','At Capt. Holt\'s birthday party, Jake, Amy and the other officers try to make a good impression on Holt\'s husband but fail miserably.','2014-02-04'),(2720,177,17,'Full Boyle','To stop Detective Boyle from getting too clingy, or \"Full Boyle,\" with his new girlfriend, Jake goes on their date, but things don\'t go as planned.','2014-02-11'),(2721,177,18,'The Apartment','When Jake\'s building goes co-op and he must pay nearly a half million dollars to keep his apartment, he desperately seeks Gina\'s help.','2014-02-25'),(2722,177,19,'Tactical Village','At Tactical Village, where the precinct competes against other precincts in paintball exercises, Jake gets jealous when Amy runs into an old flame.','2014-03-04'),(2723,177,20,'Fancy Brudgom','When Charles makes Jake his best man, it means cake tasting, choosing flowers and convincing fiancée Vivian that Charles doesn\'t want to move.','2014-03-11'),(2724,177,21,'Unsolvable','On a solving streak, Jake decides to spend his weekend off with Sgt. Terry trying to crack a cold case that no one thinks can be solved.','2014-03-18'),(2725,177,22,'Charges and Specs','Jake risks suspension when the commissioner shuts down his investigation of a civic leader and he gets Amy and Holt to help him work the case anyway.','2014-03-25'),(2726,178,1,'Undercover','When Jake discovers that a mobster escaped his otherwise successful sting, he enlists Charles to help track him down, which worries Gina.','2014-09-28'),(2727,178,2,'Chocolate Milk','Holt\'s nemesis heads the precinct inspection, while Terry readies for his vasectomy and Charles needs a date for his ex-wife\'s engagement party.','2014-10-05'),(2728,178,3,'The Jimmy Jab Games','When a motorcade detail is delayed, it leads to a wacky competition, and Charles must get an incriminating videotape from Hitchcock.','2014-10-12'),(2729,178,4,'Halloween II','For their annual Halloween wager, Jake bets Holt that he can steal his watch before midnight, and Gina gets kicked off her dance squad, Floorgasm.','2014-10-19'),(2730,178,5,'The Mole','Holt and Jake search for a mole in the precinct, and Terry and Rosa visit a silent disco to find \"Giggle Pig\" dealers.','2014-11-02'),(2731,178,6,'Jake and Sophia','Jake is attracted to a woman he soon discovers is the attorney for a perp he\'s after, and Rosa gets Amy to run for union rep to replace Scully.','2014-11-09'),(2732,178,7,'Lockdown','When the precinct goes into lockdown on Thanksgiving night, it\'s up to Jake to keep morale high, even as things spiral out of control.','2014-11-16'),(2733,178,8,'USPIS','To catch a drug dealer, Jake and Charles must team up with an incompetent Postal Service investigator. Meanwhile, the team helps Amy quit smoking.','2014-11-23'),(2734,178,9,'The Road Trip','When Jake and Amy have to stay overnight at a hotel for a case, Jake invites Sophia and Amy\'s boyfriend Teddy over, but the move backfires.','2014-11-30'),(2735,178,10,'The Pontiac Bandit Returns','Jake and Rosa catch the Pontiac Bandit, who could lead them to the Giggle Pig kingpin. Charles and Gina worry about their parents getting close.','2014-12-07'),(2736,178,11,'Stakeout','Jake and Charles go on a stakeout that lasts way too long, and Terry writes a book for his daughters that angers Amy and Gina.','2014-12-14'),(2737,178,12,'Beach House','Jake ruins the precinct\'s annual beach house getaway when he\'s pressured into bringing Captain Holt. Gina wants to see \"six-drink Amy.\"','2015-01-04'),(2738,178,13,'Payback','Jake has to go to great lengths to keep a secret about Terry from the rest of the precinct, and Amy finally gets to partner up with Captain Holt.','2015-01-11'),(2739,178,14,'The Defense Rests','When his relationship with Sophia gets in the way of her work, Jake tries to help, Wuntch needs Holt\'s help, and Charles wants Gina\'s blessing.','2015-01-25'),(2740,178,15,'Windbreaker City','The Nine-Nine is invited to a terrorist training drill with Homeland Security, but the precinct\'s role as hostages doesn\'t go over so well.','2015-02-08'),(2741,178,16,'The Wednesday Incident','Jake is determined to prove that he\'s not to blame for Holt\'s bad mood, and when Charles catches a notorious bank robber, nobody believes him.','2015-02-15'),(2742,178,17,'Boyle-Linetti Wedding','It\'s wedding day for Charles and Gina\'s parents, and everyone in the squad is given duties; but Jake and Gina get distracted, and Terry has troubles.','2015-03-01'),(2743,178,18,'Captain Peralta','When Jake\'s absentee father visits, Charles suspects he\'s up to no good. Holt throws down a brain twister challenge.','2015-03-08'),(2744,178,19,'Sabotage','Holt makes Amy and Rosa investigate Jake\'s bad luck, but he also insults Gina. Charles partners with Hitchcock and Scully.','2015-03-15'),(2745,178,20,'AC/DC','Terry forces Jake to take time off after he\'s injured chasing a perp, and Holt and Rosa go on an awkward double date with their significant others.','2015-04-26'),(2746,178,21,'Det. Dave Majors','Jake gets jealous over another detective\'s romantic interest in Amy, and Terry is tempted to accept a job at a private security firm.','2015-05-03'),(2747,178,22,'The Chopper','Holt worries Jake is being set up to fail when Wuntch green lights his dream assignment, and Terry hosts a field trip for a magnet school.','2015-05-10'),(2748,178,23,'Johnny and Dora','Jake and Amy go undercover to catch an infamous identity thief, and the squad is rocked by an unexpected farewell.','2015-05-17'),(2749,179,1,'New Captain','The precinct\'s new captain makes an unforgettable first impression. Jake and Amy try to keep their budding romance under wraps.','2015-09-27'),(2750,179,2,'The Funeral','Another shakeup at the precinct spells trouble for Jake and Amy, while a string of disappointments sends Holt into a downward spiral.','2015-10-04'),(2751,179,3,'Boyle\'s Hunch','A smitten Boyle vows to get a fellow foodie out of prison by proving her innocence. Holt\'s bid to boost cops\' public image sparks a backlash.','2015-10-11'),(2752,179,4,'The Oolong Slayer','While Jake and Holt secretly team up to hunt for a serial killer, Amy and Rosa seek revenge for a sexist assignment.','2015-10-18'),(2753,179,5,'Halloween III','For their annual Halloween heist, Jake and Holt draft teams and compete to steal a crown. But Amy\'s divided loyalties leave her out in the cold.','2015-10-25'),(2754,179,6,'Into the Woods','Jake and Charles whisk Terry away for an ill-fated camping trip, while Holt helps Rosa with a dilemma, and Amy tries to cash in on an old invention.','2015-11-08'),(2755,179,7,'The Mattress','A lovers\' spat leads to trouble on the job as Jake and Amy chase down a new street drug. A parking mishap drives a wedge between Holt and Boyle.','2015-11-15'),(2756,179,8,'Ava','Jake jumps into action when Terry\'s wife goes into labor at the precinct. Meanwhile, an Internet outage forces the team to go old-school.','2015-11-22'),(2757,179,9,'The Swedes','Tensions flare as Jake and Rosa work a case with two peculiar Swedish cops. Neil deGrasse Tyson drops by to help Gina prepare for a big test.','2015-12-06'),(2758,179,10,'Yippie Kayak','A last-minute Christmas shopping trip lands Jake, Gina and Charles in the middle of a \"Die Hard\"-like hostage crisis.','2015-12-13'),(2759,179,11,'Hostage Situation','Boyle tries to recover some sensitive cargo held hostage by his ruthless ex-wife. Amy injures Terry at the worst possible moment.','2016-01-05'),(2760,179,12,'9 Days','An illness leaves Jake and Holt quarantined and delusional as they try to solve a cold case. Terry discovers running the precinct is messy work.','2016-01-19'),(2761,179,13,'The Cruise','Jake and Amy embark on a romantic cruise, only to find an old adversary aboard. Holt braces for a visit from his melodramatic sister.','2016-01-26'),(2762,179,14,'Karen Peralta','Amy gears up to meet Jake\'s mother on his birthday, but the celebration takes an unexpected turn. New body cameras prove embarrassing for Boyle.','2016-02-02'),(2763,179,15,'The 9-8','Sparks fly when a neighboring precinct moves in with the Nine-Nine. Jake\'s reunion with an old partner yields an unhappy surprise.','2016-02-09'),(2764,179,16,'House Mouses','Jake persuades Scully and Hitchcock to take over a drug bust so he can help out with a \"celebrity\" matter. But neither case is what the team expected.','2016-02-16'),(2765,179,17,'Adrian Pimento','A cop fresh off an undercover stint with the mob has trouble readjusting to precinct life. Boyle\'s culinary exploits trigger a janitorial standoff.','2016-02-23'),(2766,179,18,'Cheddar','Jake and Amy volunteer to house-sit for Holt, with disastrous results. The chemistry between Rosa and Pimento heats up.','2016-03-01'),(2767,179,19,'Terry Kitties','An adorable special delivery reminds Terry of an unsolved case that\'s haunted him for years. With Jake\'s help, he sets out to finally crack it.','2016-03-15'),(2768,179,20,'Paranoia','A whirlwind engagement sends the gang scrambling to throw twin bachelor and bachelorette parties. But the night of revelry takes an unexpected turn.','2016-03-29'),(2769,179,21,'Maximum Security','To root out the crooked FBI agent who targeted Pimento, the team stages an elaborate fake funeral and sends Amy on a risky undercover mission.','2016-04-05'),(2770,179,22,'Bureau','With help from an old friend of Holt\'s, the gang sneaks into the FBI to find dirt on the double agent. An inmate puts Charles in an awkward position.','2016-04-12'),(2771,179,23,'Greg and Larry','Jake and the team scour the hospital for a captive Captain Holt, while Amy and Charles book it back to New York to help their friends.','2016-04-19'),(2772,180,1,'Coral Palms (1)','Jake and Holt continue their new lives in Florida under the Witness Protection Program while Jimmy remains at large, but their identities may be revealed after a video of the pair goes viral.','2016-09-20'),(2773,180,2,'Coral Palms (2)','Jake and Holt end up on the other side of the interrogation table after being caught plotting an attack on Figgis. Meanwhile, a questionable new captain takes over at the precinct.','2016-09-27'),(2774,180,3,'Coral Palms (3)','The team makes a road trip to Florida to try to help Jake and Holt take down Figgis. With an unforeseen injury and yet another interruption by Sheriff Reynolds, the plan doesn’t follow through quite like they all had hoped. In the midst of the chaos, Jake and Amy share an awkward reunion.','2016-10-04'),(2775,180,4,'The Night Shift (I)','As Jake struggles with his first case back at the precinct, he encounters Jess Day, who is visiting New York, and enlists her to help him find his suspect. Meanwhile, Holt researches ways to increase office morale and Amy tries to figure out why Rosa keeps taking such long breaks.\n\nThe crossover continues on New Girl S06E04 Homecoming (II).','2016-10-11'),(2776,180,5,'Halloween IV','It’s Halloween in the Nine-Nine, which can only mean one thing: heist time. This year, the squad members pull out all the stops in their quest to win the new defending title of “Ultimate Detective Slash Genius.” Lines are drawn and plans are made, but there can only be one reigning champion.','2016-10-18'),(2777,180,6,'Monster in the Closet','Pimento and Rosa decide to pick up where they left off and get married, so the whole squad preps a perfect wedding under Amy’s careful direction. Pimento enlists Jake and Gina to hunt for his grandmother’s ruby earrings for Rosa to wear in the ceremony, but the universe has other plans for them.','2016-11-15'),(2778,180,7,'Mr. Santiago','At Amy\'s intricately planned Thanksgiving dinner, Jake goes \"full Santiago\" (binder and all) in order to impress her father, a former cop. With Jake and Amy\'s focus elsewhere, Charles is left on turkey duty and Holt helps Pimento cope after learning he can no longer work for the NYPD.','2016-11-22'),(2779,180,8,'Skyfire Cycle','When famous author DC Parlov receives death threats, Jake and Terry take the case, so that Terry can meet his lifelong hero. Back at the precinct, Gina forces her way into the Boyle clan of cousins in an attempt to choose the location of the annual Boyle family vacation. Meanwhile, Holt\'s anger peaks when Amy chooses Kevin\'s side in their argument about a math puzzle.','2016-11-29'),(2780,180,9,'The Overmining','Captain \"CJ\" is having major problems with a big case, and Jake and Holt find the motivation to help him out. Inside the precinct, war ensues when Terry enforces a green initiative and tells Gina to get rid of her precious space heater, while Rosa and Boyle take a break from the night shift to visit a foot massage parlor.','2016-12-06'),(2781,180,10,'Captain Latvia','Charles enlists Jake\'s help in tracking down his son\'s favorite toy for Christmas, and the two find themselves accidentally facing off against a Latvian criminal ring as a result. Back at the precinct, the team gears up for their annual Christmas carol competition against their sworn enemy: the MTA.','2016-12-13'),(2782,180,11,'The Fugitive (1)','When a prison-van escape sets nine convicts loose in the city, Jake and Amy compete to see who can bring in the most fugitives.','2017-01-01'),(2783,180,12,'The Fugitive (2)','The effort to capture prison escapees continues. Jake teams up with an unlikely ally who\'s related to one of the convicts.','2017-01-01'),(2784,180,13,'The Audit','Due to low crime rates, Brooklyn decides to close one of its precincts. The future of the Nine-Nine depends on an audit conducted by Amy’s boring ex.','2017-04-11'),(2785,180,14,'Serve & Protect','Jake and Rosa tackle a case of a missing laptop on the set of a long-running TV police procedural. Terry’s vengeful ex takes over the audit.','2017-04-18'),(2786,180,15,'The Last Ride','The squad learns it\'s dangerously close to being shut down. Jake and Charles go out on one last case that quickly escalates into a major drug bust.','2017-04-25'),(2787,180,16,'Moo Moo','After getting stopped and mistreated by an unfamiliar cop, Terry receives some disappointing advice from Holt about how to handle the profiling.','2017-05-02'),(2788,180,17,'Cop-Con','Eager to blow off steam, the squad tries to keep Holt in the dark as they throw a secret party during a police convention in upstate New York.','2017-05-09'),(2789,180,18,'Chasing Amy','Jake and Rosa go on a search mission after a stressed-out Amy disappears on the day of her sergeant\'s exam. Gina inherits a Boyle family heirloom.','2017-05-09'),(2790,180,19,'Your Honor','While looking into a break-in at Holt\'s mother\'s house, Jake discovers a secret she’s been keeping from her son. The squad remodels the break room.','2017-05-16'),(2791,180,20,'The Slaughterhouse','A drug case leads Jake and Rosa to an investigation conducted by their shared idol, Lt. Hawkins, who indicates she may have a job for one of them.','2017-05-16'),(2792,180,21,'The Bank Job','Jake and Rosa call for backup from Holt and Pimento after their search for bank robbers turns dangerous. Boyle disapproves of Gina\'s new boyfriend.','2017-05-23'),(2793,180,22,'Crime & Punishment','When Jake and Rosa find themselves framed for a crime they didn\'t commit, the squad must cook up an exceptionally creative solution.','2017-05-23'),(2794,181,1,'The Big House (1)','Stuck behind bars, Jake lands in trouble over some delicious contraband. Fellow inmate Rosa keeps Holt and Terry busy with a never-ending to-do list.','2017-09-26'),(2795,181,2,'The Big House (2)','As the squad looks for ways to implicate the corrupt Lt. Hawkins, Jake puts his detective skills to work with help from his affable cannibal cellmate.','2017-10-03'),(2796,181,3,'Kicks','Freed from prison and back on duty, Jake hunts for a sneaker thief under Holt\'s watchful eye. Meanwhile, Rosa suspects Pimento of infidelity.','2017-10-10'),(2797,181,4,'HalloVeen','Jake pulls off a major surprise during the squad\'s annual Halloween heist, a cutthroat competition to claim the coveted title of Amazing Human/Genius.','2017-10-17'),(2798,181,5,'Bad Beat','An undercover operation brings out Holt\'s inner gambler. Rosa tries to out-laze Hitchcock and Scully. Charles buys a food truck with an unsavory past.','2017-11-07'),(2799,181,6,'The Venue','Nemeses plague the squad, as Jake and Amy\'s big day gets derailed by the Vulture, and Charles must find his missing equine foe, Sgt. Peanut Butter.','2017-11-14'),(2800,181,7,'Two Turkeys','On Thanksgiving, alcohol provides a temporary fix to Jake and Amy\'s parental problems, and a pilfered pie awakens the ruthless interrogator in Holt.','2017-11-21'),(2801,181,8,'Return to Skyfire','Jake and Terry go undercover at a costume-packed fan convention when their favorite fantasy author reports his much-anticipated manuscript stolen.','2017-11-28'),(2802,181,9,'99','After missing their flight home from a funeral in LA, Jake and the squad scramble to get Holt back to New York in time for a big interview.','2017-12-05'),(2803,181,10,'Game Night','Intensely private Rosa shares personal news with the team but wants Jake\'s help to tell her parents. Cyber Crimes steals the Nine-Nine\'s bandwidth.','2017-12-12'),(2804,181,11,'The Favor','Crime boss Seamus Murphy resurfaces to claim his promised favor from Holt, so Jake and Charles befriend the Murphy family\'s Fredo to get information.','2017-12-12'),(2805,181,12,'Safe House','After a threat from Murphy, Holt stashes husband Kevin in a safe house with Jake. Rosa goes undercover at a salon. Scully reveals an actual skill.','2018-03-18'),(2806,181,13,'The Negotiation','Tapped to negotiate a hostage situation, Jake realizes the perp is someone he knows. Meanwhile, tensions flare inside Charles\'s meatball food truck.','2018-03-25'),(2807,181,14,'The Box','As Jake begins an intense interrogation of a wily dentist suspected of murder, an opera-bound Holt jumps in to assist. Sterling K. Brown guest-stars.','2018-04-01'),(2808,181,15,'The Puzzle Master','Jake brings Amy in on an arson case connected to her celebrity crush, a crossword puzzle author. The Nine-Nine gets a sweet new detective car.','2018-04-08'),(2809,181,16,'NutriBoom','After realizing they were suckered into a pyramid scheme, Jake and Charles try to take down the cultish group. Amy deals with an overeager officer.','2018-04-15'),(2810,181,17,'DFW','Jake\'s attempt to connect with his half sister goes off the rails. Terry tries and fails to show his flexibility. Gina sets Rosa up on a blind date.','2018-04-15'),(2811,181,18,'Gray Star Mutual','A familiar face pops up when disaster strikes Charles\'s food truck. Rosa offers to help Amy pick out a wedding gown. Holt sets up a Twitter account.','2018-04-22'),(2812,181,19,'Bachelor/ette Party','Charles\'s convoluted bachelor party plans frustrate Jake, Terry and Holt. At her bachelorette bash, Amy plays a revealing game of \"Never Have I Ever.\"','2018-04-29'),(2813,181,20,'Show Me Going','An anxious Nine-Nine awaits news on Rosa after she enters an active shooter situation. Amy and Gina distract themselves by taking on a plumbing issue.','2018-05-06'),(2814,181,21,'White Whale','As Rosa and Amy hunt a criminal who escaped their clutches years ago, Jake takes over wedding prep. Holt faces off with his rival for commissioner.','2018-05-13'),(2815,181,22,'Jake & Amy','When Jake and Amy suffer a wedding day crisis, the Nine-Nine attempts to salvage the nuptials. Holt receives news on his bid for the commissioner job.','2018-05-20'),(2816,182,1,'Honeymoon','An unexpected third wheel puts a damper on Jake and Amy\'s tropical honeymoon. Back at the Nine-Nine, Terry experiences a crisis of confidence.','2019-01-10'),(2817,182,2,'Hitchcock & Scully','Jake and Charles investigate a case of Hitchcock and Scully\'s from the 1980s. Meanwhile, Amy\'s uniformed officers and Terry\'s detectives fight over limited resources.','2019-01-17'),(2818,182,3,'The Tattler','Jake and Gina attend their 20th high school reunion. Back at the Nine-Nine, Charles helps Rosa with her love life.','2019-01-24'),(2819,182,4,'Four Movements','After Gina makes a life-changing decision, she bestows a series of gifts on the squad. But first, an interpretive dance ...','2019-01-31'),(2820,182,5,'A Tale of Two Bandits','Jake investigates a series of car thefts that point to an old frenemy. Meanwhile, the squad defends their favorite bar from interlopers.','2019-02-07'),(2821,182,6,'The Crime Scene','A promise made to a grieving mother sends Jake spiraling into obsession as he and Rosa comb the scene of a baffling murder for clues.','2019-02-14'),(2822,182,7,'The Honeypot','Holt and Jake become suspicious of a new Nine-Nine employee. Amy goes full-on Marie Kondo to declutter the bullpen.','2019-02-21'),(2823,182,8,'He Said, She Said','Amy and Jake hear conflicting stories as they investigate a sexual assault accusation. Holt refuses to believe an old nemesis is really dead.','2019-02-28'),(2824,182,9,'The Golden Child','Jake helps Amy navigate the complicated relationship she has with her brother, David. Charles introduces some drama into an undercover mission involving Terry and Holt.','2019-03-07'),(2825,182,10,'Gintars','A visitor from Latvia causes Charles and Jake to investigate Nikolaj\'s family. Holt and Amy bring in famed forensic scientist Dr. Yee to help close a case for Rosa.','2019-03-14'),(2826,182,11,'The Therapist','A missing person case forces Jake to confront his issues with therapy. Holt invites Rosa and her new girlfriend to dinner. Terry overcompensates.','2019-03-21'),(2827,182,12,'Casecation','While celebrating their first anniversary, Jake and Amy realize they\'ve had a communication breakdown over a major life decision.','2019-04-11'),(2828,182,13,'The Bimbo','A burglary investigation at Kevin\'s university reveals Holt\'s hidden insecurity. Amy and Terry\'s efforts to raise morale turn deliciously cutthroat.','2019-04-18'),(2829,182,14,'Ticking Clocks','As Hitchcock and Scully microwave a lasagna for exactly 21 minutes and 30 seconds, the squad races against the clock to catch a hacker.','2019-04-25'),(2830,182,15,'Return of the King','Gina invites Jake and Terry over to her new place. Holt takes an interest in Nikolaj\'s education. Rosa rejects Amy\'s offer of a helping hand.','2019-05-02'),(2831,182,16,'Cinco de Mayo','Mayhem and double-crossing overtake the squad as they try to distract Terry from his lieutenant\'s exam by kicking off the Halloween Heist on a new day.','2019-05-09'),(2832,182,17,'Sicko (1)','Jake and Boyle hunt for a serial killer under the watchful eye of Commissioner Kelly. Terry learns that more money does indeed bring more problems.','2019-05-16'),(2833,182,18,'Suicide Squad (2)','To right a wrong, the Nine-Nine teams up with the worst of the worst of the NYPD. Terry sinks into deep denial about his future.','2019-05-16'),(2834,183,1,'Manhunter','Jake finds his authority tested and thunder stolen by a beat-walking Holt amid a manhunt. Amy turns to Rosa for support during a personal crisis.','2020-02-06'),(2835,183,2,'Captain Kim','When an interim captain arrives at the Nine-Nine, Jake sets out to prove she\'s way too good to be true. Boyle rebrands his image.','2020-02-06'),(2836,183,3,'Pimemento','Adrian Pimento resurfaces with a \"Finding Dory\"-esque memory problem. Jake tries to keep a secret from Boyle. The squad attends a mandatory HR seminar.','2020-02-13'),(2837,183,4,'The Jimmy Jab Games II','Jake revives the Jimmy Jab Games, with Boyle going full-on P.T. Barnum as host of the competition and Holt\'s timid new partner reluctantly joining in.','2020-02-20'),(2838,183,5,'Debbie','The squad suspects an inside job when guns and cocaine connected to a notorious crime boss go missing from the Nine-Nine.','2020-02-27'),(2839,183,6,'Trying','Time flies as Jake and Amy focus on their family plans. Holt bristles over his tedious new job. A tooth-wielding Hitchcock searches for his Cinderella.','2020-03-05'),(2840,183,7,'Ding Dong','Holt risks his career by refusing to let his greatest nemesis have the last word. Boyle and Terry compete for Jake\'s tickets to an exclusive kid event.','2020-03-12'),(2841,183,8,'The Takeback','The reappearance of Doug Judy lands Jake in hot water. Terry scrambles to replace Holt\'s treasured keepsake. The Nine-Nine gets a new vending machine.','2020-03-19'),(2842,183,9,'Dillman','When an apparent prank destroys a key piece of evidence, Holt taps the best detective he knows to interrogate the squad and bring the culprit to justice.','2020-03-26'),(2843,183,10,'Admiral Peralta','Jake doubles down on his daddy issues during a tense family reunion. Holt turns into a musical taskmaster over Terry\'s audition with the NYPD band.','2020-04-02'),(2844,183,11,'Valloweaster','A pudgy pooch, handcuffs and various other disasters delay the crowning of the squad\'s newest Amazing Human/Genius in the annual Halloween Heist.','2020-04-09'),(2845,183,12,'Ransom','Holt turns to Jake for help after a family member goes missing. Rosa battles Amy\'s ex for a coveted prize. Boyle and Terry team up on a business scheme.','2020-04-16'),(2846,183,13,'Lights Out','Amy takes charge of the Nine-Nine during a citywide blackout, while Jake hits one snag after another as he races to her side.','2020-04-23'),(2847,184,1,'The Good Ones','Amy returns from maternity leave. Jake and Rosa work a difficult case.','2021-08-12'),(2848,184,2,'The Lake House','The squad takes up Holt on an offer for a weekend getaway.','2021-08-12'),(2849,184,3,'Blue Flu','Captain Holt and Amy manage an understaffed precinct. Jake and Charles investigate.','2021-08-19'),(2850,184,4,'Balancing','Jake and Amy create a system to balance work and childcare and Rosa gets a new houseguest.','2021-08-19'),(2851,184,5,'PB&J','Jake takes an old friend for a ride.','2021-08-26'),(2852,184,6,'The Set Up','When the FBI takes over a high-profile case, Jake keeps digging. Amy and Rosa negotiate with O\'Sullivan and the police union.','2021-08-26'),(2853,184,7,'Game of Boyles','Jake and Terry accompany Charles to the funeral of his Great Uncle Pappy — and uncover a family secret. Rosa nudges Holt back into the dating pool.','2021-09-02'),(2854,184,8,'Renewal','Amid planning for a vow renewal ceremony, Holt makes a big announcement — one that he asks Jake not to share with Amy. Plus, Cheddar wears a bow tie!','2021-09-02'),(2855,184,9,'The Last Day','The squad takes stock of its eight years together and looks toward the future.','2021-09-16'),(2856,185,1,'Episode 1','In 1977, frustrated FBI hostage negotiator Holden Ford finds an unlikely ally in veteran agent Bill Tench and begins studying a new class of murderer.','2017-10-13'),(2857,185,2,'Episode 2','Holden interviews the eerily articulate murderer Ed Kemper, but his research provokes negative feedback at the Bureau.','2017-10-13'),(2858,185,3,'Episode 3','Dr. Wendy Carr joins Holden and Tench in their first success, when their insights lead to an arrest.','2017-10-13'),(2859,185,4,'Episode 4','Bill and Holden consult with Dr. Wendy Carr to begin classifying their subjects. They receive surprising news.','2017-10-13'),(2860,185,5,'Episode 5','Holden and Bill return to a perplexing case in Pennsylvania where a set of clues leading in multiple directions leaves no shortage of suspects.','2017-10-13'),(2861,185,6,'Episode 6','Wendy considers an offer. Holden and Bill struggle to communicate the meaning of their findings to the judicial system in the baffling Altoona case.','2017-10-13'),(2862,185,7,'Episode 7','Wendy takes a career risk to relocate and join the team full time. Holden and Bill find it harder to keep the emotional intensity of work at bay.','2017-10-13'),(2863,185,8,'Episode 8','Bill and Wendy interview candidates for a fourth member of the team. Holden is intrigued by complaints about a school principal\'s odd habit.','2017-10-13'),(2864,185,9,'Episode 9','Holden\'s methods during a disturbing interview with mass murderer Richard Speck create dissension among the team and kick off an internal FBI probe.','2017-10-13'),(2865,185,10,'Episode 10','The team cracks under pressure from an in-house review. Holden\'s bold style elicits a confession but puts his career, relationships and health at risk.','2017-10-13'),(2866,186,1,'Episode 1','Amid sweeping changes at the BSU, Holden deals with severe repercussions from his close encounter with Ed Kemper.','2019-08-16'),(2867,186,2,'Episode 2','To glean insight into the elusive BTK killer, Bill and Holden interview the Son of Sam, who makes a startling admission.','2019-08-16'),(2868,186,3,'Episode 3','Bill gets drawn into a horrifying crime that hits close to home. Holden receives an intriguing offer while in Atlanta to interview a pair of killers.','2019-08-16'),(2869,186,4,'Episode 4','Holden develops a controversial profile in the Atlanta slayings. Wendy conducts her first interview and finds being on the front lines suits her well.','2019-08-16'),(2870,186,5,'Episode 5','Bill\'s devastating family situation spills over during his interview with Holden\'s holy-grail subject: Charles Manson. Wendy\'s new romance heats up.','2019-08-16'),(2871,186,6,'Episode 6','The FBI officially sends the BSU to Atlanta to investigate the missing and murdered children. Wendy second-guesses her interview methods.','2019-08-16'),(2872,186,7,'Episode 7','Hitting a dead end, Holden suggests a bold plan to draw the killer out. Bill\'s family faces more scrutiny. Wendy chafes as her job begins to shift.','2019-08-16'),(2873,186,8,'Episode 8','Red tape hinders Holden\'s plan to narrow his suspect pool. A weary and heartsick Bill tries to connect with his son. Wendy rethinks her relationship.','2019-08-16'),(2874,186,9,'Episode 9','The investigation zeroes in on a prime suspect who proves surprisingly adept at manipulating a volatile situation to his advantage.','2019-08-16'),(2875,187,1,'PRESENTING ATOM EVE SPECIAL EPISODE','In this special prequel episode, Samantha ‘Atom Eve’ Wilkins discovers her superpowers as a young girl - and must come to terms with her own sinister origins as she discovers a family she never knew she had.','2023-07-21'),(2876,188,1,'IT\'S ABOUT TIME','When Mark Grayson finally inherits powers from his superhero father, it’s a dream come true. But there’s more to being a hero than just choosing a name and costume.','2021-03-25'),(2877,188,2,'HERE GOES NOTHING','With his father out of action, Mark struggles to defend the city against an interdimensional invasion, joining forces with a team of teenage superheroes.','2021-03-25'),(2878,188,3,'WHO YOU CALLING UGLY?','Mark has to cut a study date short to help save Mount Rushmore from a crazed scientist. Robot deals with Action - Comic as he assembles a new team of world-saving superheroes.','2021-03-25'),(2879,188,4,'NEIL ARMSTRONG, EAT YOUR HEART OUT','It\'s two firsts for Mark: a first date and a first trip to another planet. At the same time, Nolan and Debbie revisit their own first vacation together.','2021-04-01'),(2880,188,5,'THAT ACTUALLY HURT','Feeling confident in his new abilities, Mark risks a team-up with a local villain to take down a crime lord, while simultaneously juggling school and a new relationship.','2021-04-08'),(2881,188,6,'YOU LOOK KINDA DEAD','Mark joins William and Amber on a campus visit to Upstate University, hoping to discover a new future for himself. Debbie makes her own disturbing discovery.','2021-04-15'),(2882,188,7,'WE NEED TO TALK','Feeling lost and confused, Mark looks for advice from Eve. At the same time, everyone\'s looking for him.','2021-04-22'),(2883,188,8,'WHERE I REALLY COME FROM','Mark must prove he\'s become the hero he\'s always wanted to be by stopping an unstoppable force.','2021-04-29'),(2884,189,1,'A LESSON FOR YOUR NEXT LIFE','In the aftermath of his father\'s betrayal, Mark struggles with his responsibilities as Invincible and encounters an unexpected enemy.','2023-11-02'),(2885,189,2,'IN ABOUT SIX HOURS I LOSE MY VIRGINITY TO A FISH','It\'s summer break for Mark and his friends, but supervillains don\'t take a vacation. Mark is forced to face the consequences of Omni-Man\'s double life.','2023-11-09'),(2886,189,3,'THIS MISSIVE, THIS MACHINATION!','Mark starts his college career, Debbie struggles with personal trauma, and Allen the Alien returns home to find a new threat facing the Coalition of Planets.','2023-11-16'),(2887,189,4,'IT\'S BEEN A WHILE','Mark answers the call to save an alien species, but the mission has unexpected personal consequences.','2023-11-23'),(2888,189,5,'THIS MUST COME AS A SHOCK','The Grayson household is upended when Mark returns to Earth with surprising new responsibilities. The Guardians of the Globe face dangers both at home and away.','2024-03-14'),(2889,189,6,'IT\'S NOT THAT SIMPLE','After two challenging missions, the Guardians of the Globe struggle to work as a team. Meanwhile, Mark tries to balance his hero duties, personal relationships, and his future as a college student.','2024-03-21'),(2890,189,7,'I\'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE','As Mark attempts to salvage his personal life, a new villain arrives, presenting Invincible with his greatest challenge yet. Donald grapples with his past.','2024-03-28'),(2891,189,8,'I THOUGHT YOU WERE STRONGER','An old enemy threatens everything Mark holds dear.','2024-04-04'),(2892,190,1,'YOU\'RE NOT LAUGHING NOW','Mark Grayson is back and stronger than ever – with new enemies out for blood and old villains out for revenge.','2025-02-06'),(2893,190,2,'A DEAL WITH THE DEVIL','Mark takes a stand, unaware of the ramifications for his family, the GDA, and even the Guardians. Cecil remembers his past and Eve makes an important decision.','2025-02-06'),(2894,190,3,'YOU WANT A REAL COSTUME, RIGHT?','Mark struggles to teach Oliver what it means to be a superhero. Debbie explores a new relationship and a changed family dynamic.','2025-02-06'),(2895,190,4,'YOU WERE MY HERO','Two strangers ask Mark for help with a mysterious villain. Elsewhere in the galaxy, Nolan grapples with his identity and Allen finds a surprising new ally.','2025-02-13'),(2896,190,5,'THIS WAS SUPPOSED TO BE EASY','Mark and Eve start a business and encounter a familiar face. Debbie worries that Oliver\'s growing up too quickly.','2025-02-20'),(2897,190,6,'ALL I CAN SAY IS I\'M SORRY','A powerful new figure challenges Mark\'s idea of what\'s right and what\'s wrong. Rae approaches Rex with a big life decision.','2025-02-27'),(2898,190,7,'WHAT HAVE I DONE?','Earth\'s greatest heroes join forces to fight an unimaginable threat.','2025-03-06'),(2899,190,8,'I THOUGHT YOU\'D NEVER SHUT UP','With the world still reeling, a dangerous stranger arrives - testing Mark to his limits and beyond.','2025-03-13'),(2900,193,1,'Making the World Safe for Violence: Peacemaker\'s Team','','2022-11-22'),(2901,193,2,'Bad Daddy Issues: Peacemaker\'s Search for Inner Peace','','2022-11-22'),(2902,193,3,'Gag Reel','','2022-11-22'),(2903,194,1,'A Whole New Whirled','After making a miraculous recovery, Peacemaker returns home–only to discover that his freedom comes at a price.','2022-01-13'),(2904,194,2,'Best Friends, For Never','After Peacemaker’s hazardous escape, tension and mistrust build within the team. Later, as Peacemaker grapples with his new assignment, he receives a surprise visitor.','2022-01-13'),(2905,194,3,'Better Goff Dead','On their first official mission to assassinate suspected “butterflies,” Economos and Murn bond, and Peacemaker and Harcourt reach an understanding. But the whole job goes sideways with the arrival of Judomaster.','2022-01-13'),(2906,194,4,'The Choad Less Traveled','Following a somewhat successful mission, Murn recruits Vigilante. Meanwhile, after learning that the team helped land his father in prison, Peacemaker confronts his complicated past.','2022-01-20'),(2907,194,5,'Monkey Dory','The team scouts the apparent hub for the aliens’ food supply, only to come face-to-face with a full-fledged invasion. Meanwhile, Auggie’s attempt to sell out his son to the police is complicated by Murn’s mysterious contact.','2022-01-27'),(2908,194,6,'Murn After Reading','Murn reveals his deepest secret. Auggie is set free. The botched arrest of Peacemaker sends alien Goff into an unexpected new host.','2022-02-03'),(2909,194,7,'Stop Dragon My Heart Around','Harcourt, Murn, and Adebayo find themselves surrounded by an alien force, while Peacemaker squares off against his father with help from Vigilante and Economos.','2022-02-10'),(2910,194,8,'It\'s Cow or Never','With Peacemaker and Adebayo at odds, can the team kill the cow once and for all – or will their fracture give the aliens the opening they need to complete its teleportation?','2022-02-17'),(2911,195,1,'The Ties That Grind','While Peacemaker attempts to join the Justice Gang, Harcourt struggles to find work, and Economos takes on a challenging new assignment.','2025-08-21'),(2912,195,2,'A Man Is Only As Good As His Bird','As Economos clashes with his new handler, Peacemaker must deal with the consequences of his actions in the alternate dimension.','2025-08-28'),(2913,195,3,'Another Rick Up My Sleeve','Economos pays for the team\'s bungled mission, while Peacemaker explores the depths of his relationship with Harcourt in the other dimension.','2025-09-04'),(2914,195,4,'Need I Say Door','As A.R.G.U.S. ramps up efforts to find the QUC, Harcourt receives a tempting offer from Flag – which comes at a steep cost to Peacemaker.','2025-09-11'),(2915,195,5,'Back to the Suture','After a catastrophic showdown with Flag, Peacemaker makes a shocking decision, while his friends scramble to keep the 11th Street Kids together.','2025-09-18'),(2916,195,6,'Ignorance Is Chris','As the 11th Street Kids fight to bring their missing member home, Flag doubles down on his efforts to hold Peacemaker accountable.','2025-09-25'),(2917,195,7,'Like a Keith in the Night','As Flag and A.R.G.U.S. close in, the 11th Street Kids attempt to keep the ever-increasing dangers of the alternate world around them at bay.','2025-10-02'),(2918,195,8,'Full Nelson','As Flag puts everyone around him in increasing danger, the 11th Street Kids must convince Peacemaker that he\'s one of them.','2025-10-09'),(2919,196,1,'The Missing Christmas Mustache','Ted and the crew search for a lost item that ultimately leads him to realize the meaning of the holiday season.','2021-12-15'),(2920,197,1,'Pilot','American football coach Ted Lasso is hired by a wealthy divorcée to coach the English soccer team AFC Richmond.','2020-08-14'),(2921,197,2,'Biscuits','It\'s Ted\'s first day of coaching, and fans aren\'t happy. He makes little headway but remains undeterred as the team plays its first match.','2020-08-14'),(2922,197,3,'Trent Crimm: The Independent','To arrange an in-depth exposé, Rebecca pairs cynical journalist Trent Crimm with Ted for a day. Ted and Roy venture into the community.','2020-08-14'),(2923,197,4,'For the Children','Rebecca hosts the team\'s annual charity benefit, where Ted stages a reconciliation between Roy and Jamie.','2020-08-21'),(2924,197,5,'Tan Lines','With his wife and son visiting from America, Ted makes drastic changes to the lineup during a critical match.','2020-08-28'),(2925,197,6,'Two Aces','When Jamie refuses to train, Ted turns to talented new signing Dani Rojas—and the team is struck by an age-old curse.','2020-09-04'),(2926,197,7,'Make Rebecca Great Again','Rebecca celebrates her first anniversary as a divorcée as the team plays a match in Liverpool.','2020-09-11'),(2927,197,8,'The Diamond Dogs','Ted and Roy are both having relationship problems. Ted consults the Diamond Dogs while Roy has a talk with Keeley.','2020-09-18'),(2928,197,9,'All Apologies','After a series of mistakes on the pitch, pressure mounts to bench Roy. Rebecca drops a bombshell.','2020-09-25'),(2929,197,10,'The Hope That Kills You','Richmond plays a climactic match that will determine the fates of Ted and his club.','2020-10-02'),(2930,198,1,'Goodbye Earl','AFC Richmond brings in a sports psychologist to help the team overcome their unprecedented seven game tie-streak.','2021-07-23'),(2931,198,2,'Lavender','Ted is surprised by the reappearance of a familiar face. Roy tries out a new gig.','2021-07-30'),(2932,198,3,'Do the Right-est Thing','Rebecca has a special visitor shadow her at work. A player\'s return is not welcomed by the team.','2021-08-06'),(2933,198,4,'Carol of the Bells','It\'s Christmas in Richmond. Rebecca enlists Ted for a secret mission, Roy and Keeley search for a miracle, and the Higginses open up their home.','2021-08-13'),(2934,198,5,'Rainbow','Nate learns how to be assertive from Keeley and Rebecca. Ted asks Roy for a favor.','2021-08-20'),(2935,198,6,'The Signal','Ted is fired up that the new team dynamic seems to be working. But will they have a chance in the quarterfinal?','2021-08-27'),(2936,198,7,'Headspace','With things turning around for Richmond, it\'s time for everyone to work on their issues—like Ted\'s discomfort, Nate\'s confidence, and Roy\'s attention.','2021-09-03'),(2937,198,8,'Man City','Ted and Dr. Sharon realize they might have to meet each other halfway. Tensions are high as the team prepares for the semifinal.','2021-09-10'),(2938,198,9,'Beard After Hours','After the semifinal, Beard sets out on an all-night odyssey through London in an effort to collect his thoughts.','2021-09-17'),(2939,198,10,'No Weddings and a Funeral','Rebecca is stunned by a sudden loss. The team rallies to show their support, but Ted finds himself grappling with a piece of his past.','2021-09-24'),(2940,198,11,'Midnight Train to Royston','A billionaire football enthusiast from Ghana makes Sam an unbelievable offer. Ted plans something special for Dr. Sharon\'s last day with the team.','2021-10-01'),(2941,198,12,'Inverting the Pyramid of Success','Richmond gets their final chance to win promotion as Ted deals with the fallout of Trent Crimm\'s painfully honest exposé.','2021-10-08'),(2942,199,1,'Smells Like Mean Spirit','The newly promoted AFC Richmond face mockery as pundits predict they\'ll finish dead last this season.','2023-03-14'),(2943,199,2,'(I Don\'t Want to Go to) Chelsea','News of a top player looking to move to London sends the English clubs into a frenzy. Richmond play their first game back in the Premier League.','2023-03-21'),(2944,199,3,'4-5-1','Richmond adjust to an exciting change, but Jamie has reservations. Ted learns there\'s something new going on back in Kansas as well.','2023-03-28'),(2945,199,4,'Big Week','Everyone\'s feeling the pressure as Richmond gear up to play West Ham. Ted is reunited with an old friend.','2023-04-04'),(2946,199,5,'Signs','With their season in a tailspin, Richmond try to right the ship against mighty Manchester City. Off the pitch, everyone faces their own setbacks.','2023-04-11'),(2947,199,6,'Sunflowers','A friendly match takes the team to Amsterdam, where one night out unlocks truths for many.','2023-04-18'),(2948,199,7,'The Strings That Bind Us','The Greyhounds try a new strategy that has everyone thinking outside the box. Sam prepares to host a VIP guest at Ola\'s.','2023-04-25'),(2949,199,8,'We\'ll Never Have Paris','While watching Henry, Ted fights the urge to spiral when Michelle and Dr. Jacob go on a romantic trip. An online leak has massive implications for Keeley.','2023-05-02'),(2950,199,9,'La Locker Room Aux Folles','Colin and Isaac\'s friendship is tested. Roy is asked to do a press conference.','2023-05-09'),(2951,199,10,'International Break','While some of the Greyhounds head home to play for their countries in international matches, Edwin Akufo brings a business proposal to Rebecca.','2023-05-16'),(2952,199,11,'Mom City','An unexpected guest has Ted on edge. When Richmond travel to Manchester for a big match, Roy and Keeley become concerned about Jamie.','2023-05-23'),(2953,199,12,'So Long, Farewell','AFC Richmond play their final game of the season.','2023-05-30'),(2954,201,1,'Welcome to Margrave','Reacher is wrongly accused of murder while visiting the small town of Margrave, GA.','2022-02-03'),(2955,201,2,'First Dance','When more victims are discovered, Reacher attempts to get answers but is set up. Roscoe receives a threatening message.','2022-02-03'),(2956,201,3,'Spoonful','Reacher and Finlay’s investigation into the missing Spivey leads them into a confrontation with Kliner Sr. Roscoe learns unsettling news about Reacher.','2022-02-03'),(2957,201,4,'In a Tree','As the danger increases, Reacher and Roscoe grow closer and they make plans to meet with their contact from Homeland Security.','2022-02-03'),(2958,201,5,'No Apologies','As the mystery deepens, Reacher teams up with an old colleague and Finlay makes a shocking discovery.','2022-02-03'),(2959,201,6,'Papier','As the town is rocked by another murder, Reacher heads to New York and learns the truth about the illegal business in Margrave while Roscoe faces danger in the woods.','2022-02-03'),(2960,201,7,'Reacher Said Nothing','Reacher springs a trap and then gets trapped himself.','2022-02-03'),(2961,201,8,'Pie','Reacher leads a rescue mission at the warehouse that ends in a showdown.','2022-02-03'),(2962,202,1,'ATM','Reacher and Neagley investigate the murder of a member of 110th, a group of Special investigators assembled by Reacher, only to realize the whole unit may be at risk.','2023-12-14'),(2963,202,2,'What Happens in Atlantic City','The investigation into Franz\'s murder takes Reacher and the surviving members of his former Army unit to Atlantic City where the mystery deepens, danger awaits, and an old flame is rekindled.','2023-12-14'),(2964,202,3,'Picture Says a Thousand Words','After more of his friends fall victim, Reacher forges an uneasy alliance with a dogged detective, and their only clue in the case leads the 110th to a troubling discovery.','2023-12-14'),(2965,202,4,'A Night at the Symphony','Reacher and his team head to Boston to track down a political aide with insider knowledge of a top secret military-defense contract that may be the reason behind their friends\' deaths.','2023-12-21'),(2966,202,5,'Burial','Neagley and Dixon discover shocking information about an old friend in Denver while Reacher and O\'Donnell learn more about the nefarious and mysterious A.M..','2023-12-28'),(2967,202,6,'New York\'s Finest','As the mystery continues to unfold, Reacher and his team set a trap to even the score.','2024-01-04'),(2968,202,7,'The Man Goes Through','As the team close in on Langston, two members of the 110th face danger, compelling Reacher to devise a dangerous plan to rescue them.','2024-01-11'),(2969,202,8,'Fly Boy','Reacher and Neagley make a final desperate attempt to save O’Donnell and Dixon, stop A.M. and avenge their friends’ murder.','2024-01-18'),(2970,203,1,'Persuader','Reacher’s attempt to thwart a kidnapping brings him into contact with mysterious businessman Zachary Beck.','2025-02-20'),(2971,203,2,'Truckin\'','Tasked with transporting cargo for his new employer Zachary Beck, Reacher must juggle the involvement of the DEA and a nosy new associate.','2025-02-20'),(2972,203,3,'Number 2 with a Bullet','As a rising body count threatens his undercover position, Reacher makes a dangerous play to secure Beck’s trust.','2025-02-20'),(2973,203,4,'Dominique','Reacher reunites with Duffy and Villanueva and finally shares the painful details of his history with Xavier Quinn.','2025-02-27'),(2974,203,5,'Smackdown','When a DEA tragedy puts the entire mission at risk, Reacher, Duffy, and Villanueva improvise a drastic plan to save their cover.','2025-03-06'),(2975,203,6,'Smoke on the Water','Reacher is torn between his desire to kill Quinn and his promise to Duffy to save Teresa.','2025-03-13'),(2976,203,7,'L.A. Story','After Reacher and Duffy travel to Los Angeles to arrange a deal, Neagley arrives in Maine to help Reacher get answers.','2025-03-20'),(2977,203,8,'Unfinished Business','Reacher finally faces off with both Paulie and Quinn.','2025-03-27');
